NK102(ne)001:1: // gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches mdzad
NK102(ne)001:2: pa'i sgom gyi gnad gsal bar phye ba bsam gtan
NK102(ne)001:3: mig sgron zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK102(ne)001:4: gdod man ngag 'di yang rtsis mgo las /
NK102(ne)001:5: nas lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang //
NK102(ne)001:6: rang bzhin ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK102(ne)001:7: ma mthong rang bzhin gnyis su snang //
NK102(ne)001:8: de nyid ngang gyur bdag nyid chen po /
NK102(ne)001:10: de la kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems lhun gyis
NK102(ne)001:11: rdzogs pa chen po gtan la dbab pa'i man ngag
NK102(ne)001:12: gi rgyal po / rnal 'byor pa'i mig ces bya
NK102(ne)001:13: ba'i bsam gtan 'di'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs mtshan gyi
NK102(ne)001:14: che ba'i rnam grangs gtan tshigs dang bcas pa /
NK102(ne)001:15: ni 'khor ba'i chu bo bzhi las sgrol ba'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:17: pa chen po'i gru'i bsam gtan zhes bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:19: chen po thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas /
NK102(ne)001:20: rin po che'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:22: pa'i don thams cad 'dir 'dus pas don bsdus pa'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:25: zhe phugs kyi bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:28: pa ka nas 'dag par byed pas sgron ma chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:30: chags kyi ljan ljin thams cad 'dag par byed pas chu bo chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:32: bdun chen po ma btsal grub par byed pas /
NK102(ne)001:33: ded dpon chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:35: gtan gyi gral rim par bkod nas mchog tu bstan pas /
NK102(ne)001:36: khyad par chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:37: 'khor ba dang rtsol ba'i dgra dgu pa /
NK102(ne)001:38: dpung chen po ril gyis klan ka mi rnyed pas /
NK102(ne)001:39: rdzong chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:41: ba dang zhen rtsol gyi bsam pa ril bcom pas dmag dpung chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:43: rnams ma bgrod cig car non pas mgyogs pa chen po cang shes kyi bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:46: ma sgrubs lhun gyis rdzogs pas /
NK102(ne)001:47: grub pa chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:49: pa med par mthar phyin par byed pas /
NK102(ne)001:50: thar lam chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:52: 'phrul gyi mngon rtogs thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pas /
NK102(ne)001:53: ya mtshan chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:55: ba gang yang ma spangs blang du med pas /
NK102(ne)001:56: spyod pa chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:59: phyad pa chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:61: dang yang ma bral bas snying rje chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:63: du bya ba gang yang med pas /
NK102(ne)001:64: nyal ba chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:66: dpe ba'i gcong snying chen po 'byin pas /
NK102(ne)001:67: bdud rtsi sman chen po 'byin pa'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:69: la'ang nyam nga ba dang bag tsha ba med pas /
NK102(ne)001:70: khyung chen lding ba'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:72: zab cing gting dpag dka' la g.yo ba med pas /
NK102(ne)001:73: rgya mtsho chen po'i bsam gtan zhes kyang bya ste /
NK102(ne)001:74: dper na rdul phra rab dang chu'i thig pa bgrang zhing shes par mi rung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:75: 'di'i mtshan gyi mtha' ni shes par mi rung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:77: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mtshan gyi bdag nyid pa'i phyir ro //
NK102(ne)001:78: 'o na rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan zhes kho nar gdags pa ci ste zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:80: de dag don chen po ma mthong bar med pa'i yon tan gyi khyad par gyi phyir ro //
NK102(ne)001:81: de lta bu'i don chen po ni rigs khungs su brgyud pa'i dbang dang rim pa ni rdzogs /
NK102(ne)001:82: gang la bslab pa'i bya ba ni mthar phyung /
NK102(ne)001:83: 'khor ba'i spyod pa la don med par ni rig cing khong du chud pas /
NK102(ne)001:84: bya ba thams cad mchil ma'i thal ba bzhin du bor te /
NK102(ne)001:85: thar pa chen po'i go 'phang thob par 'dod pas /
NK102(ne)001:87: de la gnas kyi ngo bo ji ltar btsal zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:88: rgyu'i theg pa chen po'i lugs kyis kyang /
NK102(ne)001:89: sngon ston pas zhabs kyis bcags pa'i rdo rje'i gnas byin che ba /
NK102(ne)001:91: bya grub pa thob pa'i gnas bkra shis pa /
NK102(ne)001:93: li yul lcang ra smug po la sogs pa bkra
NK102(ne)001:94: shis pa'i gnas dag bya ba grub par byed pas
NK102(ne)001:95: btsal lo // zhes gzhung du ma las 'byung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:96: rnal 'byor nang pa'i theg pa'i gzhung gis kyang /
NK102(ne)001:97: gzhung dang rgyud kyi ldan pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:99: gzhung dang ldan pa ni phyogs mtshams kyi sgros legs pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:102: ri'i dbyibs dang bar snang gi dbyibs de bzhin gshegs pa'i phyag rgya rin po che dang /
NK102(ne)001:105: 'khor lo la sogs pa spangs pa phun sum tshogs pa'i gzugs 'dra ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:107: snyan pa'i sgra ldan yid 'ong btsal bar rgyud gzhung du ma las bka' stsal to //
NK102(ne)001:108: yang las dang po pas re zhig nye ring spangs pa /
NK102(ne)001:109: snang yal ran pa btsal lo //
NK102(ne)001:110: de yang mched po pad+ma'i man ngag las /
NK102(ne)001:111: khams la mi gnod nye ring spangs /
NK102(ne)001:112: zhes 'byung ba dang mthun par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:113: lo rgyus shis pa yang sngar smos pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:114: rgya bod kyi mkhas pa pho mo mang po grub pa thob pa'i gnas bgrangs kyis mi tshugs so //
NK102(ne)001:115: dur khrod ru dra bsgral ba'i yan lag lnga khog pa stod smad nang khrol lo //
NK102(ne)001:118: he ru ka'i gnas bcu dang /
NK102(ne)001:119: a su ra'i rdo rje gdan gyi gnas /
NK102(ne)001:121: bod kyi grub pa thob pa'i gnas /
NK102(ne)001:123: stag dang seng ge lung dang /
NK102(ne)001:124: lho brag mkhar chu'i brag dang /
NK102(ne)001:126: gangs ti se ma pham gyi 'gram dang /
NK102(ne)001:128: lung la sogs pa de lta bu la bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:129: 'o na de lta bu dag tu bya ba la yon tan ci yod ce na /
NK102(ne)001:130: de dag tu byas na 'dug bsran che ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:131: nyams dga' zhing thag nye ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:133: rang bzhin gyi nus pa dang ldan pa'i phyir ro //
NK102(ne)001:136: mtshams med pa la mtshams gcod pa //
NK102(ne)001:138: shes bya nang gi chos nyid la //
NK102(ne)001:141: bar du gcod pa bsal ba'i phyir //
NK102(ne)001:142: phyi dang nang gi sa mtshams su //
NK102(ne)001:148: rnam par mi rtog don tshol na //
NK102(ne)001:149: gcig pu dben pa'i sa bzung ste //
NK102(ne)001:150: zhes gsungs pa g.yeng sgrib sel ba'i phyir ro //
NK102(ne)001:151: theg pa chen po nang pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:152: shin tu rnal 'byor gyi lugs kyis /
NK102(ne)001:153: ril kyang rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid mtha' thams
NK102(ne)001:154: cad dang bral ba yum gyi mkha' klong chen po
NK102(ne)001:155: dang / rang byung gi ye shes kyi ngo bo mtha' ma spang bral ba la /
NK102(ne)001:156: stong gsum nyid yang dag pa'i gnas su bka' stsal to //
NK102(ne)001:158: phyogs bcu stong khams ye nas dben //
NK102(ne)001:161: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams 'di dag nga nyid kyi yul lo //
NK102(ne)001:165: ched du dben pa tshol ba don las mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:167: de nyid kyang spang bya min pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:168: re zhig rkyen nyung ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:169: 'og gi yon tan rnams dang ldan pas btsal gyi /
NK102(ne)001:170: de kho na la chags par bya ba yang ma gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:171: 'o na dgon pa la chags pa skyon nam zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:172: de ni gang la yang spang blangs med pa'i don
NK102(ne)001:173: chen po mthong du mi ster ba'i nad chen po
NK102(ne)001:174: yin te / bi ma la'i klong 'grel las /
NK102(ne)001:175: gnas su sems nyid dgon pa /
NK102(ne)001:177: ting 'dzin ye shes mchog gi gnas //
NK102(ne)001:178: dgon pa'i dben pa bdag mi tshol //
NK102(ne)001:179: gnas kyi rtogs pas bcings par mchi //
NK102(ne)001:182: sems la dben par ma rtogs na //
NK102(ne)001:183: dgon pa'i dben par sus phyin kyang //
NK102(ne)001:184: sems ni rmu rgod stong khams nyul //
NK102(ne)001:185: lus po nyal khang gnas stong bsrung //
NK102(ne)001:186: spang phug phyi ba nyal ba 'dra //
NK102(ne)001:188: 'o na gnas de skyon brtag pa ji lta bu zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:189: sa tsha grang ma snyoms pas nad 'jug pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:190: klu gdug pa gnas pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:191: yul lha nag po gnas pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:192: lha 'dre'i rgyu srang du babs pas srog gi bar chad dang /
NK102(ne)001:193: yo byad shin tu btsal dka' ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:194: mchog tu nyams mi dga' ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:195: mun gyis chod na khams 'khrug go //
NK102(ne)001:196: ha cang snang yal ches pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:198: skye bo grol nyan pa dang skye ba dang rgyu 'grul khe tshol byed /
NK102(ne)001:200: chu sgra gnas pa na sems 'phros so //
NK102(ne)001:201: yul de na theg pa chung ngu'i gang zag gnas pa ni ya ga dang 'tshangs 'dogs so //
NK102(ne)001:202: rgyal po gdug pa can dang /
NK102(ne)001:203: blon po gdug pa can gnas na bar chad 'ong ngo //
NK102(ne)001:204: nye na gnyen gyi cha mchus gnod par 'gyur te g.yeng ngo //
NK102(ne)001:205: ring na dgra'i 'tshe ba 'ong bas de dag dang ldan pa ni skyon no //
NK102(ne)001:206: dgos pa ni de dag med par bya ba ste /
NK102(ne)001:207: de sgrub thabs nges pa rgyan las /
NK102(ne)001:209: bdag dbang bar chad med pa'i gnas //
NK102(ne)001:210: rnyed nas de na gnas par bya //
NK102(ne)001:212: 'o na dar las ci bya zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:213: de dag rang rig pas rang gi mtshan nyid la
NK102(ne)001:214: lta ba med pa'i tshul gyis blta ste 'dris goms
NK102(ne)001:215: su bya'o // byang chub sems kyi man ngag las /
NK102(ne)001:216: don nyid nyams su myong 'dod pas //
NK102(ne)001:217: gcig pu seng ge bzhin 'dug nas //
NK102(ne)001:218: g.yeng ba'i yul rnams thag bcad de //
NK102(ne)001:219: 'brel sngon du bya ba'i las su yang bshad de mi 'gal lo //
NK102(ne)001:220: yul dpag tshad du mas bshug /
NK102(ne)001:221: de nas yid kyi me long blta //
NK102(ne)001:225: gdung tshab kyi skyes bu su zhig /
NK102(ne)001:228: khyim thabs ni wa'i brtul zhugs kyis spangs nas dgon par don chen po 'tshol ba'i mi chen pos /
NK102(ne)001:230: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho chen po ni shin tu zad pa med de thar dka' la 'gying skyen 'gyur /
NK102(ne)001:231: pas 'di dag las thar pa'i dus med pa ni
NK102(ne)001:232: snying re rje zhes sems can thams cad bu dang
NK102(ne)001:234: de dag las thar bar bya ba'ang /
NK102(ne)001:235: bdag gang zag sa sems can yin pas /
NK102(ne)001:237: rang bzhin dag kyang thabs chen po dang mi ldan
NK102(ne)001:238: pa'i phyir bskal pa rgya mtshor 'gro don mdzad pa'i
NK102(ne)001:239: rjes su don las dang po pas /
NK102(ne)001:242: chen po mchog bsgrubs thabs rgya mtsho dang sangs rgyas kyis /
NK102(ne)001:243: 'dra ba sprin phung gi don byas te /
NK102(ne)001:244: thams cad bsgral lo bar bsam pa ni mdo sngags thun mong du byas pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:247: dang por rab tu dam bca' ste //
NK102(ne)001:248: bdag ni mi rtag sdug bsngal las //
NK102(ne)001:249: thar nas gzhan don bsgrub pa yang //
NK102(ne)001:250: gang zag sa pa nus zhan pas //
NK102(ne)001:251: rgyal ba'i go 'phang rab bsgrubs te //
NK102(ne)001:252: kun 'dren sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan /
NK102(ne)001:254: kun kyang byang chub sar bkod la //
NK102(ne)001:255: bde ba thob bya snyam du yang //
NK102(ne)001:256: bsams te snying rje bskyed par bya //
NK102(ne)001:258: de la lta ba dang sbyar na /
NK102(ne)001:259: theg pa bzhi car du yang bcad du ton /
NK102(ne)001:263: sems can ni don byed pa'i rtog pa mig la mi 'gal dam bca' ba la rtsod pa /
NK102(ne)001:265: re zhig gtso bo'i dbang du rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs 'dir /
NK102(ne)001:266: bya ba thams cad bral lo zhe 'dir dam bca' ba mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:268: 'dir dam bca' ba med pa'i don rtogs na dngos
NK102(ne)001:269: po gang la'ang spang blangs med pa'i skyon gyis mi
NK102(ne)001:270: gos pa dper na nam mkha' dang 'dra ba'i phyir
NK102(ne)001:272: dam du bca' ba'i yul rang gdod nas med //
NK102(ne)001:273: dam du bca' ba'i yul med don rtogs na //
NK102(ne)001:274: dam du bcas kyang skyon med nam mkha' 'dra //
NK102(ne)001:275: zhes pas dam du bca' ba'ang 'gal ba ma yin no //
NK102(ne)001:276: de nas bdag gzhan gyi don du gnas der las brtsam pa'ang theg pa so so'i spyir bstan /
NK102(ne)001:277: mi rtog pa'i gzhung bzhi legs par khong du chud pas /
NK102(ne)001:278: sgo gsum bcos slad med par sems kyis chos lta ba dang rjes su mthun pa'i spyod pa'ang /
NK102(ne)001:279: bya ba med bya ba mi 'gog ma chags par spyod do //
NK102(ne)001:281: nyams dga' ba'i gnas su brtson pa yis //
NK102(ne)001:285: spyod pas ci la chags med spyod //
NK102(ne)001:286: des ni don bzhin mthar phyin 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:288: sngon du 'gro ba'i las brtsam pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:289: dang po kho nar mnyan pa la 'bad par bya ste /
NK102(ne)001:291: mnyan pa'i shes rab thos pa ma bskyed na //
NK102(ne)001:292: mun khungs gser la sgron me med dang 'dra //
NK102(ne)001:294: thog mar mun pa'i gser tshol ba na sgron me la brten pa 'dra bar /
NK102(ne)001:295: don chen po sems las btsal ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:297: tshig dang yi ge'i sgron ma la brten dgos pas /
NK102(ne)001:298: mdo sde dag las mang du yang gsungs /
NK102(ne)001:301: t+r+aam gsang lta ba la rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK102(ne)001:302: ba gsang chen gsang mchog gang //
NK102(ne)001:303: gsang ba kun la mnyan par bya //
NK102(ne)001:304: zhes pa la sogs pa rgya cher gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:307: mig tshig sgron mas don gyi gser mtshon pa //
NK102(ne)001:308: tshig gi rnam grangs gsung gi 'khor lo can //
NK102(ne)001:309: zhes gsungs pas don btsal te 'bad do //
NK102(ne)001:310: de yang mdor don go ba ni thos pa'i mchog yin pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:312: tshig tshogs rgya mtsho thos pa min //
NK102(ne)001:313: tshig gcig go ba thos pa'i mchog /
NK102(ne)001:315: lang kar gshegs pa'i mdo las /
NK102(ne)001:316: mang du thos pa zhes bya ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:317: don la mkhas pa yin gyi /
NK102(ne)001:318: tshig la mkhas pa ni ma yin no //
NK102(ne)001:319: zhes gsungs pas go bar bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:320: de ltar mnyan pa phal cher tshig zin kyang /
NK102(ne)001:321: ma bsams na don dang 'brel ba med do //
NK102(ne)001:322: bsam pa'i shes rab ni shin tu ma dpyad na /
NK102(ne)001:323: snyan smra don dang 'brel med snyan tshig smra /
NK102(ne)001:327: ji ltar cang shes gyi ling dag /
NK102(ne)001:328: sdom byed sgrog gis bcings gyur pa //
NK102(ne)001:329: bkrol nas bde blag btang gyur na //
NK102(ne)001:330: ci la'ang thogs med 'gro ba ltar //
NK102(ne)001:331: sems kyi dbang po cang shes 'di //
NK102(ne)001:332: mi shes bcings pas bcings gyur pa //
NK102(ne)001:333: rnam grol thos pa'i sgo mo yis //
NK102(ne)001:334: shes rgyud kun grol thogs med 'gro //
NK102(ne)001:337: rgyu 'bras theg pa kun mthun yang //
NK102(ne)001:338: don lta sgom spyod pa 'bras bu /
NK102(ne)001:339: mthun pa ni ma yin no //
NK102(ne)001:341: khyad par du gdams ngag rna bar brgyud pa'i man ngag thob par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:342: de la rgyu'i theg pa bcom ldan 'das sku mya
NK102(ne)001:343: ngan las 'da' kar 'od srungs la gdams ngag phog
NK102(ne)001:344: / de nas dar m+ao d+h+aa ra la sogs pa nas /
NK102(ne)001:345: rgya nag por bdun brgyud tha ma ha shang ma h+aa ya na la thug /
NK102(ne)001:346: de nas bod yul du btsan po dang dge slong
NK102(ne)001:347: rnams la yod pa ni nub glang dar ma'i ring
NK102(ne)001:348: la btsun pa ye shes dbang po bar chad du
NK102(ne)001:349: gyur pas mtshan nyid kyi slob dpon brgyud pa nub
NK102(ne)001:350: / de dag gi 'dod gzhung gi yi ge dag yod pa de dag dang /
NK102(ne)001:351: ka m+aa la shi las rim par bslab pa la sogs pa dag the tshom chod par byas te /
NK102(ne)001:352: phyis slob dpon la mi snyeg par bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:353: sngags nang pa la ma h+aa /
NK102(ne)001:354: thabs 'dod chags chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyi man ngag dang /
NK102(ne)001:355: gdams ngag thig le la sogs te /
NK102(ne)001:356: steng 'og gi sgo'i man ngag dang /
NK102(ne)001:357: lhag 'bro lha bu rin chen nas bka' ma chad par bzhugs pa /
NK102(ne)001:360: ci la yang bya ba med pa'i man ngag snyan khung brgyud pa thob par bya ba ste /
NK102(ne)001:364: spyod lam bya thabs la sogs pa'i the tshom bcad pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:369: mchod rten dang gtsug lag khang bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:370: rab tu byung ba'i sde ba chen po bca' ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:371: mdo sde rgya chen po bklag pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:372: chos kyi 'khor lo chen po bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:373: sdug bsngal can gyi grogs bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:374: nye ring med pa'i nad pa gso ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:375: sbyin pa rgya chen po la sogs pa rlabs ci cher 'bad do //
NK102(ne)001:376: theg pa chen po sngags la ni khyad par du yang /
NK102(ne)001:377: dbang gi rim pa mang po nod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:378: sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor mang du zhal phye ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:379: sbyin bsreg rgya chen po bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:380: rab tu byung ba'i sde ba yang mchod gnas su bkur ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:381: snying rje khung ba'i zhing du bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:382: sgoom grwa gzugs pa la sogs pa la 'bad par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:383: gzhan yang zas nor zang zing gi 'brel chags bsal ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:384: gros 'dun gyi thag bcad pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:385: dgos pa'i rkyen rnams gong du tshang bar bsags pa la sogs pa bya ste /
NK102(ne)001:386: byang chub sems kyi man ngag las /
NK102(ne)001:387: zab mor 'jug pa'i sngon log gsungs //
NK102(ne)001:388: the tshom 'phyar mo thag bcad de //
NK102(ne)001:389: sdig sbyang byang chub sems bskyed nas //
NK102(ne)001:390: rnal 'byor tshogs kyi bsod nams dpung //
NK102(ne)001:391: rnam grangs ji snyed bstan pa kun //
NK102(ne)001:392: tshul bzhin lcog tshad bya ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:393: 'phral gyi bya ba ma lus kun //
NK102(ne)001:394: phyi nas 'gyod pa med par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:397: bsgom pa'i gnas nas lam btsal mi dgos pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:401: phyis mi g.yeng bar 'gyur bas 'bad do //
NK102(ne)001:402: de nas zang zing gi nor dag spang ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:403: zas nor gyi rang bzhin rnam rtog gi gzugs brnyan snang ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:408: 'ching ba'i rgyu byed pa nyid de /
NK102(ne)001:410: bdag la dbyig gi bang mdzod dang /
NK102(ne)001:411: rta glang la sogs pa ci yod mi chags par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:413: snga rabs shi ba'i mi rnams kun gyis kyang //
NK102(ne)001:414: rtag tu re zhing zas dang nor bsags kyang //
NK102(ne)001:415: sdig pa'i rnam smin rmongs pa bdag nyid khur //
NK102(ne)001:416: zas nor phyir lus bdag la spyad dbang med //
NK102(ne)001:417: bzang rgu gon zhing zhim rgu ltor zos kyang //
NK102(ne)001:418: sgom pa'i don la 'gyang na byol song ste //
NK102(ne)001:419: gcan gzan gra bzang rmon glang lto skyid 'dra //
NK102(ne)001:420: de bzhin mi gtsang phyi sa bzhin du bor //
NK102(ne)001:422: gzhan yang mi gnyen dang yid chags spangs te /
NK102(ne)001:429: yul mi la sogs pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:430: 'jig rten 'di'i mgron po gnas gcig tu 'dug pa 'dra ste /
NK102(ne)001:431: nam yang 'gyes pa'i chos can te /
NK102(ne)001:432: 'dir 'phral phyid dang dga' ba'i chags pas bsten kyang /
NK102(ne)001:434: de dag gi dbang kar mi btang /
NK102(ne)001:435: wa yis gzhan mthong na sar bas bros pa bzhin mi chags par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:436: tshe 'dir gcig pa'i las mthun gnyen gzhi rnams //
NK102(ne)001:437: mgron po gnas mthun tsam ste so sor 'gro //
NK102(ne)001:438: pha ma la sogs grogs bshes gnyen gdung gis //
NK102(ne)001:439: sdug bsngal grogs byed 'khor ba'i gros bskyil nas //
NK102(ne)001:440: 'phral phyid phugs su phung bar byed pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:441: de la nyan cing sems gtod smyos sam ci //
NK102(ne)001:442: de bas rang gi lus kyang 'gyel chos can //
NK102(ne)001:443: de phyir wa yi shugs slongs la //
NK102(ne)001:444: dgon pa'i gnas su gcig pur gshegs //
NK102(ne)001:446: slob mkhan pos bshad pa bsgom pa'i tshe mi ni su yang bsnyen par mi rigs /
NK102(ne)001:448: kun kyang mi rgod kyi sems dang chas shing khe
NK102(ne)001:449: g.yogs ci thob tu tshol ba yin pas chos lam
NK102(ne)001:450: bsgom pa la gnod de nan gyis mi gnyen pa
NK102(ne)001:451: la gnyen mi mdza' ba la mdza' zhes zer zhing
NK102(ne)001:452: 'gro zhing gar ci thob par glags lta zhing 'gro
NK102(ne)001:453: ba'i phyir ro // dpon dar mo ta ra'i rgya lung chen po las kyang /
NK102(ne)001:454: 'khor ba'i gdung mtshams dang mi bshes par gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:455: de dag las kyang chung 'dod chags zhe sdang gti
NK102(ne)001:456: mug dri dang 'grogs pa'i phyir chung ma zhes bya'o
NK102(ne)001:457: // mi zad srin mo chags pa klu mo 'bag nor 'dzom pa dang dgra /
NK102(ne)001:458: ma dngos po gang rung ba dang 'brel ba phra
NK102(ne)001:459: mo la chags nas mi sgom pa yang spang ngo
NK102(ne)001:461: rgyal srid 'jig rten pha rol nas //
NK102(ne)001:462: bsnams te mi rtag pa'i dpe /
NK102(ne)001:468: bsod nams rgyu las grub pa'i phyir //
NK102(ne)001:469: de yang yud tsam zhig tu bas //
NK102(ne)001:470: de ltar longs spyod kun kyang 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:471: brel ba gal chen gsal la bya zhe phyis bsgom pa /
NK102(ne)001:473: chu gnyer 'dra ste mtha' med pas //
NK102(ne)001:474: ma 'das bar du brel ba mi zin na //
NK102(ne)001:475: shi nas ro de dal bas bsgom bya'am //
NK102(ne)001:476: de bas longs spyod mchil ma bzhin du bskyur //
NK102(ne)001:478: spyir dang bo las can gyis de bzhin du bsam
NK102(ne)001:479: pa'ang dor ba ni ma yin sna ba gnyen 'dun
NK102(ne)001:480: la sogs pa dgra bzhin yang ma yin te ma
NK102(ne)001:482: lugs chen po'i chos lam spyod pas ni /
NK102(ne)001:483: de dag ril gyis brtags na med /
NK102(ne)001:485: snang ba nyid dang mi snang ba'ang glo bur gyi btags pa tsam las /
NK102(ne)001:486: ngo bos cir yang btags bsams byar med pa gang la su zhig chags te /
NK102(ne)001:487: chags par bya ba rdul tsam yang med par shes par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:488: shes par bya ba nyid kyang re zhig go //
NK102(ne)001:489: de ltar thams cad la ma chags pa'i yid kyis dgon par yun bsrings te don dpyad do //
NK102(ne)001:490: gal te dgon par yun ring pas dgon pas skyo na 'di ltar bsams te /
NK102(ne)001:491: grong dang 'du 'dzi'i mtshan nyid ni chung ngu na /
NK102(ne)001:499: nyon mongs pa'i ru ma slong zhing sogs pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:501: rgyud rab tu ma zhi ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:502: yongs su brtag mi bzod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:504: myur du 'byung ba'i chos can dang /
NK102(ne)001:505: yongs su skyo ba'i chos can dang /
NK102(ne)001:506: byang chub shin tu thag ring ba la sogs par bsam so so mkhyen pa 'dul ba /
NK102(ne)001:509: snga ma'i skyon bzlog pa nyid kyang yon tan no //
NK102(ne)001:510: mdo sde ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyal po las dgon pa'i yon tan gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:511: gzhan yang mdo sngags kyi bka' du ma las /
NK102(ne)001:512: dgon pa ni sdig pa mi dge ba'i chos rnams las dben pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:513: rgyud shin tu zhi bar 'gyur ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:515: nyon mongs mi bsog mi slong ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:518: mngon par shes pa 'char ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:520: bla na med par 'tshang rgya ba la sogs pa gsungs pa dran par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:521: gang zhig grong gi dbus su 'dug nas su //
NK102(ne)001:522: byang chub sangs rgyas dam pa thob pa ni //
NK102(ne)001:523: de 'dra'i sangs rgyas gang yang sngon ma byon //
NK102(ne)001:524: ma byon pa dang da ltar bzhugs la'ang med //
NK102(ne)001:525: ces gsungs pa de dag dran par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:526: cher na so so'i rang bzhin dben pa'i don bsam par bya ste /
NK102(ne)001:527: mdo sde pas kun rdzob rten cing rkyen bzhi 'dus kyi dngos po /
NK102(ne)001:528: 'brel 'dus pa bsngo ba'i ngo bo tsam zhig /
NK102(ne)001:530: rta bzhin snang ba yang sgyu ma tsam ste /
NK102(ne)001:531: don dam par de la ngo bo med pa /
NK102(ne)001:534: rgyu rkyen bral ba ste spros mtha' brgyad dang gsum las dben par shes par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:535: sngags nang pa bas bden pa gnyis dbyer med pa'i de bzhin nyid /
NK102(ne)001:536: rang rig pa'i ye shes ni mtha' gang gis kyang ma rig pa'i don gyis /
NK102(ne)001:537: dben thams cad par dran par nges sangs bar du 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:539: lhag pa'i rnal 'byor ni lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i chos nyid /
NK102(ne)001:540: gzhi bzhag rang lugs ni bsal bas dben pa ma yin gyi ye nas dben pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:541: dben pa'i tha snyad nyid dang yang bral ba /
NK102(ne)001:542: de dran pa med pas dran na su zhig gang la skyo /
NK102(ne)001:544: don des skyo ma bsal bar sangs par 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:545: zhib tu so so lta gzhung du 'og nas ston no //
NK102(ne)001:546: rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan zhes bya rgya cher 'grel pa chen po las /
NK102(ne)001:551: skyo ba bsang ba'i don bstan te le'u dang po'o////de ltar bya ba'i las thams cad zin nas /
NK102(ne)001:553: rgyu'i theg pa'i lugs kyis kyang dbang po rno rtul gyi bye brag gi gnyis te /
NK102(ne)001:556: de la rim gyis pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:557: rgya dkar po'i slob dpon ka m+aa la shi la'i 'dod gzhung ste /
NK102(ne)001:558: drang ba don gyi mdo sde yongs su ma rdzogs pa'i gzhung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:561: slob dpon d+har mo ra las brgyud pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:562: bod der dar mo t+aa ra ni shar phyogs nas rgya mtsho brgal nas 'ongs te /
NK102(ne)001:563: rgya yul leng kug tu phyin pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:566: mkhan pos rgya rje 'u ni don dam pa go ba ma yin par shes nas /
NK102(ne)001:567: mkhar lag chur byon pas dge sbyong kha shi dang /
NK102(ne)001:569: kwa na hong la sogs pas phrag dog byas te /
NK102(ne)001:570: li cis mkhan po la dug lan snga phyi drug blud pas ma tshugs so //
NK102(ne)001:571: gzhug chos gtad pa'i sa rnyed nas rgya yul du sku 'das tshul bstan nas /
NK102(ne)001:574: rgya yul nas stod phyogs su tshong pa 'un zhes bya bas phyin pas /
NK102(ne)001:575: ra ma ting gi la ka slob dpon bod de dar mo t+aa ra dang mjal te /
NK102(ne)001:576: phyag na lham ya yang gcig kyang thogs nas 'dug go //
NK102(ne)001:577: der bka' mchid zhib tu smra pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:578: slar log nas rgya yul tu gtam zhib tu bsnyad pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:579: dur kha phye ste bltas na /
NK102(ne)001:580: lham ya gcig las mi 'dug ste /
NK102(ne)001:581: kun na re 'phags pa yin no zer ro //
NK102(ne)001:582: des brgyud pa'i tha ma ha shang ma h+aa ya na gyi gzhung cig car 'jug pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:583: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mdo sde'i gzhung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:584: gzhan yang sngags nang pa rnal 'byor chen po dang /
NK102(ne)001:585: shin tu rnal 'byor la 'jug pa'i dus su'ang man ngag thob par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:586: de yang re zhig phye nas gsol te /
NK102(ne)001:587: tsen min ni thabs zhi gnas rgyud brtags pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:589: par sla ba'i zhi gnas la sogs pa dag thob par byed do //
NK102(ne)001:590: ston mun ni thog ma nyid nas don dam pa
NK102(ne)001:591: ma skyes pa nyon mongs gang dang gang che ba'i
NK102(ne)001:592: gnyen por byams pa la sogs /
NK102(ne)001:594: goms pa'i thabs rnams thob par byed kyang /
NK102(ne)001:595: thabs ni yin gyi de la thabs chen po zhes mi bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:596: thabs chen po gang zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:599: bya ba med pa'i thabs so //
NK102(ne)001:600: de la rten pa'i rnal 'byor chen po'i thabs ni
NK102(ne)001:601: dper na dug nyid dpyad pas sman gyi mchog tu
NK102(ne)001:602: gyur pa ste / de'ang phyi dang nang ngo //
NK102(ne)001:603: phyi ni thos bsam gyi lam nas blo gzhug pa'i
NK102(ne)001:604: thabs khyad par can mang po spyod yul dang bral
NK102(ne)001:605: bas rtogs pa ngang gis mi skye bar /
NK102(ne)001:607: yi ge la brten pas mi dmigs par bya ba rnams so //
NK102(ne)001:608: de dag gi gzhung yang shes par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:609: nang gi la yang gnyis te /
NK102(ne)001:610: ting nge 'dzin gyi gdams ngag rtsa dang /
NK102(ne)001:612: thig le la brten pa ni gsang snying gar /
NK102(ne)001:613: ba'i gnas su rtsa brgyad la bsgom pa'i thabs chos 'khor la sogs pa /
NK102(ne)001:615: sku dang 'od kyi 'da' daka'i man ngag la sogs pa mang po yod pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:616: de dag rim par rdzogs slob dpon la /
NK102(ne)001:617: shing mnyes pa mchog tu byas la mtshams drag tu bcad la zhu ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:620: zla ba dang nyi mar ldan pa'i mi mo mtshan nyid tshang ba btsal te /
NK102(ne)001:621: rnyed nas phyi'i rim pa rdzogs /
NK102(ne)001:623: gsang ba'i dbang nod de gong gi steng sgo'i /
NK102(ne)001:625: de brten phra ba'i las la 'jug cing brtag go //
NK102(ne)001:626: de brten nas bde ba chen po la 'jug go //
NK102(ne)001:627: de la las kyi phyag rgya'i bde ba /
NK102(ne)001:628: rjes su 'jug pa'i rnal 'byor thob nas /
NK102(ne)001:629: gzhi'i mu tra bral kyang nyams pa med de /
NK102(ne)001:630: bsgom pa la'ang 'bad mi dgos de /
NK102(ne)001:631: btang snyoms chen po'i brtson 'grus bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:632: thabs de gnyis ka la 'jig rten pa'i chags pa'i /
NK102(ne)001:634: mya ngan las 'das pa'i bde stong dbyer med pa /
NK102(ne)001:635: ro yod pas shin tu nyams gang yin /
NK102(ne)001:637: thos bsam gyi don dang sbyar zhing bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:638: de ni zla gsang thig le las /
NK102(ne)001:639: 'dod chags med par byang chub med //
NK102(ne)001:640: byang chub med par 'dod chags med //
NK102(ne)001:641: yang dag sbyor bas thams cad 'grub //
NK102(ne)001:642: sbyor dang mi ldan dngos grub med //
NK102(ne)001:644: ya nga'i rgyu la gzhus spyad pas //
NK102(ne)001:645: thar pa chen po rang las 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:647: thabs chen theg pa theg pa'i mchog /
NK102(ne)001:649: de ni nam mkha' che las kyang //
NK102(ne)001:650: che ba'i ye shes rnyed dka' ba //
NK102(ne)001:651: shes rab thabs la brten pas 'grub //
NK102(ne)001:654: +aa li k+aa li zab tu bstan //
NK102(ne)001:655: de ni a dang mdzes pa'i ta //
NK102(ne)001:656: pa dang yan lag spros pa bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:657: 'jig rten yongs kyi spyod yul la //
NK102(ne)001:658: sangs rgyas gsung gi zab mo 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:660: 'o na rdzogs chen nang pa'i thabs la brten nam zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:661: rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhung gi dgongs pa min na'ang /
NK102(ne)001:662: re zhig de dag nas brgyud pas rtogs pa mi 'gog pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:663: bdud rtsi chen po'i rgyud las /
NK102(ne)001:664: rgyud dang lung dang man ngag kyang //
NK102(ne)001:665: dmangs dang rje'u dang rgyal po'i tshul //
NK102(ne)001:666: gcig la gcig brten gcig gi ngang //
NK102(ne)001:667: gcig ste rnam pa yongs kyis med //
NK102(ne)001:669: lhag pa'i rnal 'byor gyi lugs nyid ni /
NK102(ne)001:670: rna brgyud bstan pas thugs brtol te //
NK102(ne)001:672: snyan khungs brgyud pa'i man ngag gser dang g.yus kha smra shes tsam du byas /
NK102(ne)001:673: lag par za 'og theg tshad khyer /
NK102(ne)001:675: gnas dben par lha 'dres kyang ma tshor par zhu'o //
NK102(ne)001:677: rten med kyi thabs ni 'dod chags zhe sdang la sogs pa'i rgyu re las /
NK102(ne)001:678: ye shes skyes pa lta bu ni thabs kyi mchog ma yin te /
NK102(ne)001:679: 'dir tha snyad thams cad rang byung gi ye shes la /
NK102(ne)001:680: til 'bru gcig gi mtha' brtags kyang ye shes klong la mtha' mi rnyed de /
NK102(ne)001:681: ye shes chen pos snum khyabs che chung med pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:682: phyogs la mi brten pas thams cad kyang lam ste /
NK102(ne)001:683: mthong thos myong tshor reg pa ci byas kyang //
NK102(ne)001:684: rang byung ba'i ye shes klong du wal wal rang gsal lo //
NK102(ne)001:685: de ni gong gi nam mkha' che'i bka' lung dang /
NK102(ne)001:687: chos rnams sna tshogs ji snyed snang ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:688: tha snyad thams cad byang chub mchog gi lam //
NK102(ne)001:691: nyon mongs lnga dang mtshams med lnga po yi //
NK102(ne)001:692: rnam dag lam der zhugs na mnyam pa'i rgyal po thob //
NK102(ne)001:695: dmyal ba'i gnas nyid bla med lam //
NK102(ne)001:696: zhes pa la sogs pa rgya cher gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:698: gsang sngags mthong bar 'dod pa'i rkyen me long du ni thams cad 'gyur te /
NK102(ne)001:699: ji lta ji ltar sangs rgyas nas srog chags ldem bu dang /
NK102(ne)001:700: nam mkha' las rdul phra rab yan chad kyis /
NK102(ne)001:701: lhan ne lhang nge lhag ger gsal bar byed pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:702: the tshom gcod par byed pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:704: glegs bam chen por gyur pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:706: yongs su go bar sgrog pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:708: 'dir nyon mongs pa la rten pa ni ma yin te /
NK102(ne)001:709: de nyid ye shes chen po'i klong las lam gzhan nas btsal du med de /
NK102(ne)001:710: sngon du de dag thos par byas te /
NK102(ne)001:712: tshom bcad pa'i skabs su bstan pa dang 'dra'o //
NK102(ne)001:713: de la mthun pa bsten 'di la mdo chus las /
NK102(ne)001:715: nyams dang mdor gnyis med spyod pa'i rgyu /
NK102(ne)001:716: ldan pa'i grogs bsten pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:717: nang pas mtshan dang ldan pa'i phyag rgya bsten pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:718: bsam pa dang mthun pa'i dar ma bsten pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:719: yid du 'ong ba'i g.yog bsten pa dang bzhi'o //
NK102(ne)001:720: de la nyams dang man ngag gi /
NK102(ne)001:721: ldan de'i khungs su bzhi las dang po rgyu dam pa /
NK102(ne)001:723: mkhan po dpal dbyangs kyis kyang /
NK102(ne)001:725: ldan ma nor don bzhin bcos pa shin tu gces //
NK102(ne)001:727: slob dpon dgongs pa'i nyams dang ldan pa /
NK102(ne)001:728: khungs kyi dbang dang man ngag thob pa /
NK102(ne)001:729: mchog tu dgongs pa don dang 'brel bas slob bu nyams drod zin pa /
NK102(ne)001:730: sems 'chos pa la mkhas pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:732: gser la nag tshur gtong ba'i slob dpon rin chen de //
NK102(ne)001:733: rin thang dpag tu med pa'i lon gyis bslu bar 'os //
NK102(ne)001:735: yang rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung las /
NK102(ne)001:736: rdo rje slob dpon bla ma de //
NK102(ne)001:737: lam ston sa mkhan bshes gnyen mgon //
NK102(ne)001:738: mun sel sgron ma rin po che //
NK102(ne)001:739: mthong mig dbang po yid rnam shes //
NK102(ne)001:740: chu bo rabs med sgrol ba'i gru //
NK102(ne)001:741: 'jigs pa'i rdzong chen brten pa'i mkhar //
NK102(ne)001:743: mtsho gling rin chen len byed pa'i //
NK102(ne)001:744: ded dpon dam pa'i bla ma de //
NK102(ne)001:745: sngon du nges pa shes par bya //
NK102(ne)001:747: yon tan de lta bus bdag la phan 'dogs pas gdags par bya /
NK102(ne)001:749: bla ma dam pa'i rang bzhin yang //
NK102(ne)001:750: yid brtan sems dwangs dul ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:751: tshad med yangs pa'i blo gros dang //
NK102(ne)001:752: rkyen thub bzod ldan kun tu drang //
NK102(ne)001:753: gsong por spyod la gya gyu med //
NK102(ne)001:754: sems can nyen can thams cad la //
NK102(ne)001:755: thabs kyis mi 'jigs sna tshogs sbyin //
NK102(ne)001:756: dpa' bo mthu ldan brtson 'grus che //
NK102(ne)001:757: shes bya'i yul ni thams cad la //
NK102(ne)001:759: srid pas zhus kyang zad mi shes //
NK102(ne)001:760: brtags shing yon tan phyi phyir 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:761: bden par smra zhing tshig mi 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:762: ji skad smras pa bzhin du byed //
NK102(ne)001:763: nyes dang legs pa'i las rnams las //
NK102(ne)001:764: dga' dang mi dga' rtog 'dzin med //
NK102(ne)001:765: ri dwags rgyal po seng ge ltar //
NK102(ne)001:766: gzi ldan brjid che yul mi 'jug /'du 'dzi dman pa'i las rnams spang //
NK102(ne)001:767: 'phyong dang g.yang bral gang na rtag /
NK102(ne)001:768: seng ge spu ltar gcig pu gnas //
NK102(ne)001:769: dgon pa'i rgyud dang dben lam dben //
NK102(ne)001:771: zhes bstan pa'i bla ma'i yon tan de dag dang ldan pa btsal lo //
NK102(ne)001:772: de kun dang ma ldan yang /
NK102(ne)001:773: rang bzhin bzang la dgongs pa zab pa btsal na /
NK102(ne)001:774: thar lam la nor sa med do //
NK102(ne)001:775: de lta bu'i bla ma ma rnyed na /
NK102(ne)001:777: nor bas ngan pa'i tshig la bros pa gong gi
NK102(ne)001:778: yon tan las bzlog pa'i skyon can gyi mi slob
NK102(ne)001:780: mtho phyir bsten na gcal lo //
NK102(ne)001:781: slob dpon tshad mar ma phyin spre'u'i lung //
NK102(ne)001:782: brten dang lam nor rtogs pas zin ta re //
NK102(ne)001:785: phyag rgya ma bsten pa yang /
NK102(ne)001:786: rgyud gzhung du ma las 'byung ba'i yon tan dang
NK102(ne)001:787: ldan pa'i rigs dbye rdo rje'i rigs sogs gang yin
NK102(ne)001:793: yul la gtogs 'dod chung zhing bzhin lus yid du 'ong ba /
NK102(ne)001:795: ngag rdzun dang phra ma dang khro gtum spangs pa /
NK102(ne)001:796: tshad pa bzlas pas mi skyo ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:798: shes rab rno la nyon mongs chung ba /
NK102(ne)001:801: chags pa mchog tu che ba /
NK102(ne)001:803: sbyor thabs kyi bye brag la mkhas pa bsten no //
NK102(ne)001:806: ka m+aa la shi la dang /
NK102(ne)001:807: ma h+aa ya na'i bsam gtan dang /
NK102(ne)001:808: rnal 'byor nang pa'i zab pa'i phyogs rnams dang /
NK102(ne)001:811: bzhi phrugs gi la ba 'grel te ka don lta bu /
NK102(ne)001:813: de kho na nyid kyi rgyud drug dang /
NK102(ne)001:814: sems phran nyi shu'am bco brgyad la sogs pa bsten no //
NK102(ne)001:817: gnas thag ring thung dang sbyar te /
NK102(ne)001:818: ring na nad kyi bar chad 'byung srid pas zung du yang rung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:821: kho brdib nogs thub pa sran che /
NK102(ne)001:822: brtse gdung ldan la smra ba nyung //
NK102(ne)001:823: gsong des zhi la bya ba bzo //
NK102(ne)001:824: brtson ldan kha ska shin tu'ang gces //
NK102(ne)001:825: srang chung 'phyo dga' gtam mang dang //
NK102(ne)001:826: brtson med 'gabs lci nogs chung dang //
NK102(ne)001:827: sdar ma snying ring kha sla can //
NK102(ne)001:828: bsten na bar chad 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK102(ne)001:829: ldum ra'i dug bzhin rtsa nas dbyung //
NK102(ne)001:830: zhes bal po'i rgyal po ba su d+h+aa ra gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:832: bdud rtsi chen po'i rgyud bzhin /
NK102(ne)001:833: dgra bgegs bzlog pa'i phur bu dang /
NK102(ne)001:835: yungs kar la sogs pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:836: nad bzlog pa'i sman mang po dang /
NK102(ne)001:840: nad gzhil ba'i rig sngags khyad par can btsal zhing tshags bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:841: bar chad kyi sho gam pa bzlog pa'i go mtshon yang tshags bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:843: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor rnams lus bsrung ba'i phyir mtshon cha bsrel bar ni gnang gis /
NK102(ne)001:844: brdeg par mi bya'o zhes gsungs te /
NK102(ne)001:845: 'dir yang yod las dgra yis 'tshe bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:846: dus deng sang gi mi ni shin tu spyod pa yang bas /
NK102(ne)001:847: lam bsgom pas kyang tshags byas te /
NK102(ne)001:848: nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis bsnun par mi bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:850: 'tsho ba'i kha zas dang ras kyi pi bar stan 'bol po /
NK102(ne)001:852: spyir ni chog shes pas chags par mi bya'ang /
NK102(ne)001:854: lus la rgyan du mi bya nang nub kha zas gzab /
NK102(ne)001:856: bcud dang ldan pa bsten no //
NK102(ne)001:857: de dag la dgos pa ci yod zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:858: lus kyi gru gzug pa'i phyir te /
NK102(ne)001:859: dper na chu bo rgal ba'i dus su /
NK102(ne)001:860: lus rten pa'i gru chen pos pha mthar skyel ba bzhin /
NK102(ne)001:861: dal 'byor khong ldan gyi mi lus la brten nas /
NK102(ne)001:862: thar pa'i go 'phang la gzeg pas /
NK102(ne)001:863: lus gru dang 'dra bar bsam mo //
NK102(ne)001:864: dba' dpal dbyangs kyi zhal snga nas /
NK102(ne)001:865: lus la gru'i blo bzhag ste /
NK102(ne)001:866: pha mthar bde blag skyel ba bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:867: thar pa'i go 'phang gzegs par bya //
NK102(ne)001:868: zhes gsungs pa de bzhin du bsam mo //
NK102(ne)001:870: de la rtag par khrus byed pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:871: bag med pas tsha grang mi snyoms pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:872: mi bde bar mi 'dug pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:875: ngal spyod cha mnyam pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:876: bcag ran gyi phyin par bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:877: kha zas thang lhag dang mi mthun pa mi btang ba la sogs rkyen bzlog pa rnams so //
NK102(ne)001:879: de lta bu'i lus kyi bkur ba'ang re zhig tsam
NK102(ne)001:880: las lta ba'i don dran pas de la ma chags
NK102(ne)001:881: par bya'o // de la ma bsgoms pa'i skyon ni /
NK102(ne)001:884: rgya mtsho mchings kyi pha bong ltar //
NK102(ne)001:885: dpag tu med pa'i sgo spyad kyang //
NK102(ne)001:886: don med snying po skams pa yin //
NK102(ne)001:888: sdong po brgyan pa'i mdo las /
NK102(ne)001:889: la la stobs med chu klung gis //
NK102(ne)001:890: nan gyis khyer bar gyur pa dag /
NK102(ne)001:891: skams shing shi bar gyur pa bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:892: ma sgom chos kyang de dang 'dra //
NK102(ne)001:893: ji ltar 'gro ba mang po la //
NK102(ne)001:894: zas dang skom dag byin byas kyang //
NK102(ne)001:895: bdag nyid bkres nas shi ba ltar //
NK102(ne)001:896: de 'drar chos la ma sgom pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:897: ji ltar sman pa la la zhig /
NK102(ne)001:898: sman rnams thams cad gtong bzhin du //
NK102(ne)001:899: lto yis nad kyis shi ba ltar //
NK102(ne)001:900: chos la ma sgom de dang 'dra'o //
NK102(ne)001:901: ji ltar dbyig gi mdzod dag tu //
NK102(ne)001:902: rin chen mang po bgrangs byed kyang //
NK102(ne)001:903: ba zhad tsam yang mi thob bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:904: chos la ma sgom de dang 'dra'o //
NK102(ne)001:905: ji ltar bde ba kun ldan pa'i //
NK102(ne)001:906: rgyal po pho brang 'khor skyes kyang //
NK102(ne)001:907: zas dag skom dag mi bdog bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:908: de bzhin ma sgom de dang 'dra //
NK102(ne)001:909: ji ltar 'on pa'i rol mo yis //
NK102(ne)001:910: sil snyan glu dag mkhas pa bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:911: gzhan dag de yis dga' byed pa //
NK102(ne)001:912: de bzhin ma sgom de dang 'dra //
NK102(ne)001:913: ji ltar dmus long ri mo mkhan //
NK102(ne)001:915: bdag nyid kyis ni ma mthong ba //
NK102(ne)001:916: de bzhin ma sgom de dang 'dra //
NK102(ne)001:917: ji ltar mtsho chen mnyan pa zhig /
NK102(ne)001:918: skye bo mang po sgrol byed kyang //
NK102(ne)001:919: bdag nyid chu ru shi ba ltar //
NK102(ne)001:920: chos la ma sgom de dang 'dra //
NK102(ne)001:921: lam gyi gzhi mdor mang po la //
NK102(ne)001:922: phun sum tshogs pa kun brjod kyang //
NK102(ne)001:923: bdag gis de ma dmigs pa bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:924: chos la ma sgom de dang 'dra //
NK102(ne)001:927: rtse gcig bsgoms pa'i shes rab mig med par //
NK102(ne)001:928: ma bgrod dmus long dge ba ci spyod kyang //
NK102(ne)001:929: spyan bzang lam long ba bsti sangs /
NK102(ne)001:930: thub gnas su phyin mi srid //
NK102(ne)001:931: ji ltar seng ge lcags gzeb ma bkrol ba //
NK102(ne)001:932: seng skad 'byin yang mchong dang rgyug mi dgos //
NK102(ne)001:933: de bzhin rtse gcig bsgoms pas ma bkrol na //
NK102(ne)001:934: tshig la 'chel bas thar pa thob mi srid //
NK102(ne)001:935: drod chen ma phebs lo tog skye mi srid //
NK102(ne)001:936: de bzhin rtse gcig sgom pa'i drod med na //
NK102(ne)001:937: tshig gi thang skam dgon dung smras pa la //
NK102(ne)001:938: sku dang ye shes lo tog skye mi srid //
NK102(ne)001:939: dper na tshong pa 'ba' zhig byes bgrod kyang //
NK102(ne)001:940: zong med nor mi rnyed na spang ba ltar //
NK102(ne)001:941: ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i zong dang nor med na //
NK102(ne)001:942: lus ngag dge ba'i nor de 'khor bar dkor 'dun chen po /
NK102(ne)001:946: dper na mi la la zhig zhing gi so nam gyi bya ba la shang thang bar 'bad nas /
NK102(ne)001:947: btsas ma yal bar 'dor ba ltar /
NK102(ne)001:948: rnal 'byor pa mnyan bshad nas mi bsgom pa yang de dang 'dra'o //
NK102(ne)001:949: dper na nad pa gang zhig gis nad la sman pa'i sman dka' bas btsal nas sbyar te /
NK102(ne)001:951: sman pa'i ngag mi nyan cing sman ma zos na 'chi ba ltar /
NK102(ne)001:952: rnal 'byor pa bsgom pa'i thabs mnyan btsal nas /
NK102(ne)001:953: mi bsgom pa'ang de bzhin te 'khor bar 'achi'o //
NK102(ne)001:954: dper na mi la la zhig rgya mtsho'i dbus su
NK102(ne)001:955: skoms nas shi ba ltar thos nas ma sgom pa'i
NK102(ne)001:957: dper na nong po kha g.yos mkhan gyis /
NK102(ne)001:958: g.yos kyi kha skyid mang po btang yang /
NK102(ne)001:959: 'grangs pa la mi phan pa bzhin /
NK102(ne)001:960: nyan pa dang bshad mkhan gyis sgom pa'i yon tan
NK102(ne)001:961: brjod kyang ma sgom na 'bras bu med pa'ang de
NK102(ne)001:962: bzhin no // dper na rin po che gter len
NK102(ne)001:963: pa'i lam rgyus mkhan gyis lam rgyus bshad kyang ma
NK102(ne)001:964: phyin na dbul ba sel mi nus so //
NK102(ne)001:965: de bzhin du tshig la zhen pas sgrub pa'i thabs smras kyang ma bsgom na /
NK102(ne)001:966: chos kyi dbul ba sel bar mi nus so //
NK102(ne)001:967: dper na gla mi la la zhig gis jo bo'i mdzod kyi nor bgrangs kyang /
NK102(ne)001:968: rang la spyod pa'i thabs med pa bzhin du /
NK102(ne)001:969: 'chad mkhan dang nyan pa pos byang chub bsgrub pa'i thabs dang yon tan bskal par smras kyang /
NK102(ne)001:970: ma sgom na byang chub kyi 'bras bu med do //
NK102(ne)001:971: zhes pa la sogs pa bka' du ma las rgya cher gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:972: de ltar skyon shes nas sgom pa'i yon tan ni /
NK102(ne)001:974: 'khor los dbang bsgyur ji bzhin du //
NK102(ne)001:975: chos kun dbang bsgyur bsam gtan yin //
NK102(ne)001:976: des na dam pa'i bsam gtan bya //
NK102(ne)001:978: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las /
NK102(ne)001:979: mun las snang byung ji bzhin du //
NK102(ne)001:981: rtogs pa'i dbang bsgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK102(ne)001:982: gso dang bsad dang pham dang rgyal //
NK102(ne)001:983: dgug dang btang dang bcing dang grol //
NK102(ne)001:987: dngos grub thams cad ting 'dzin gyis 'grub par gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:990: theg chen don la bsgom pa'i gang zag gis //
NK102(ne)001:991: da ltar 'bras bu mngon du mi snang yang //
NK102(ne)001:992: lus ngan sdug bsngal d+r+wa ba bral ma thag /
NK102(ne)001:993: thar pa'i 'bras bu rim gyis thob par 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:994: dper na khyung dang seng ge'i phru gu yang //
NK102(ne)001:995: da ltar mthong ba snang ba'i gzugs med kyang //
NK102(ne)001:996: mngal dang sgo nga'i sbubs dang bral ma thag /
NK102(ne)001:997: khyung dang seng ge mngon par snang bar 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:998: rgyal po'i btsun mo'am bran mo ma la'ang rung //
NK102(ne)001:999: rgyal po'i sa bon chags nas gzugs 'dod pa //
NK102(ne)001:1000: mngal gyis bsgribs pa'i mod la mi snang yang //
NK102(ne)001:1001: mngal dang bral nas rgyal por snang bar 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:1002: de bzhin theg chen bsgoms pa'i gang zag kyang //
NK102(ne)001:1003: rnam smin lus ngan d+r+wa bas bsgribs pa yis //
NK102(ne)001:1004: da ltar rtags mtshan gsal bar mi snang yang //
NK102(ne)001:1005: lus ngan bral nas 'bras bu rim par 'grub //
NK102(ne)001:1006: rgyal po bran mo ngan dang nyal na yang //
NK102(ne)001:1007: mngal du byung ba nur nur chags pa la //
NK102(ne)001:1008: lha rnams de la re ba'i mthu skye zhing //
NK102(ne)001:1009: mngal dang bral nas rgyal po'i lus mthong la //
NK102(ne)001:1010: skyes nas kun gyi rgyab dang dpung nus ltar //
NK102(ne)001:1011: theg chen bsgoms pa'i gang zag da lta ru //
NK102(ne)001:1012: rtags mtshan med kyang lus dang bral ma thag /'bras bu snang zhing kun gyi mgon skyabs 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:1013: dper na ka la ping ka'i phru gu yang //
NK102(ne)001:1014: sgo nas bsgribs pas mngon par mi snang yang //
NK102(ne)001:1015: sgo nga'i nang nas zab mo'i sgra sgrogs shing //
NK102(ne)001:1016: sgong shun bral nas mngon du snang bar 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:1017: de bzhin theg chen bsgoms pa'i gang zag kyang //
NK102(ne)001:1018: tshe 'dir rtags mtshan mngon du mi snang yang //
NK102(ne)001:1019: theg chen tshig smra bsgom pa rtse gcig pas //
NK102(ne)001:1020: lus ngag bral nas 'bras bu thob par 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:1021: sgo nga phyi rol gzugs su 'dra ba la //
NK102(ne)001:1022: ma chag bar du khyad par mi snang yang //
NK102(ne)001:1023: ma gnong pa la chag kyang bye phrug med //
NK102(ne)001:1024: gnongs nas chag nas bye phrug snang ba ltar //
NK102(ne)001:1025: mi lus ma shi bar du khyad med kyang //
NK102(ne)001:1026: ma bsgom pa la shi nas byang chub med //
NK102(ne)001:1027: bsgoms nas shi na byang chub rim par 'grub //
NK102(ne)001:1028: de phyir bsam zhing bsgom la 'bad par bya //
NK102(ne)001:1029: gzhan yang gal te gang g+aa'i bye snyed kyi //
NK102(ne)001:1030: sems can ma lus kun la rin chen nor //
NK102(ne)001:1031: phung po du mar sbyin pa byin byas pas //
NK102(ne)001:1032: ting 'dzin phung po'i bsod nams char mi phod //
NK102(ne)001:1033: khams gsum gang ba'i 'gro mang ji snyed pa //
NK102(ne)001:1034: de dag ji snyed ma lus thams cad kyi //
NK102(ne)001:1035: 'pho ba'i srog bton bsod nams bsdoms pas ni //
NK102(ne)001:1036: rtse gcig bsgoms pa bsod nams khyad par 'phags //
NK102(ne)001:1037: de bzhin stong gi 'jig rten khams rnams su //
NK102(ne)001:1038: gser dngul shel dang beed+aur+ya sogs pa'i //
NK102(ne)001:1039: rin chen sna bdun mchod rten bkangs pa bas //
NK102(ne)001:1040: ting 'dzin rgyal po 'bum gyi char mi phod //
NK102(ne)001:1041: gal te gang g+aa'i ji snyed kyi //
NK102(ne)001:1042: sems can de la lus 'byin pa'i //
NK102(ne)001:1043: bsod nams rgya chen gang yin pas //
NK102(ne)001:1044: ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i 'bum gyi char mi nye //
NK102(ne)001:1045: de bzhin bskal par dge bsags pa'i //
NK102(ne)001:1046: bsod nams phung po ji snyed pa //
NK102(ne)001:1047: ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i dge ba yi //
NK102(ne)001:1048: bye ba'i char yang mi reg go //
NK102(ne)001:1050: zag pa med pa'i dge ba ni bdud kyis kyang mi 'phrog pas /
NK102(ne)001:1051: zla med par khong du chud par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:1052: de ni shin tu'ang gces pas /
NK102(ne)001:1053: rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung dag las /
NK102(ne)001:1054: dper na rgya mtsho'i nor len mis //
NK102(ne)001:1055: sbrul dang chu srin sbrang ma la sogs pa'i //
NK102(ne)001:1056: stug pa'i sdug bsngal sna tshogs can //
NK102(ne)001:1057: dka' bas nyams su blang na 'grub //
NK102(ne)001:1059: rnam rtog bying rmug 'phyar g.yeng dgra //
NK102(ne)001:1060: gzhom par dka' ba'i las 'di dag /
NK102(ne)001:1061: nyams su blangs na bde thob rnyed //
NK102(ne)001:1062: ting 'dzin nyams su blangs pa yi //
NK102(ne)001:1063: 'drir goms bya bar rab tu gces //
NK102(ne)001:1065: bka' du ma las rgya cher 'byung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:1066: 'di dag ni bsgom pa la bskul bar gsol te /
NK102(ne)001:1067: dus phyi ma la rnal 'byor rjes su spyod pa rnams kyi thugs la bzhag par gsol to //
NK102(ne)001:1068: de la sgom pa'i dus su sprin nag po a cang yang ches /
NK102(ne)001:1069: dkar po yang nyi ma la sgrib pa 'dra bar /
NK102(ne)001:1070: rnam par dkar ba'i las chos spyod nyid kyang sgrib pas /
NK102(ne)001:1071: dkar phyogs btang snyoms su bzhag par bya ste /
NK102(ne)001:1072: mdo dag las rgya cher gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:1073: nang pa'i theg pa yang re zhig blo chung ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:1074: blo che yang sngar bsgoms pa la ma sbyangs pa dag /
NK102(ne)001:1075: phyi rol gyi g.yeng bar 'gyur bas /
NK102(ne)001:1076: spyod pas bsgom pa gcig pu la dril lo //
NK102(ne)001:1078: mchod rten lha khang la sogs pa //
NK102(ne)001:1079: 'dus byas dge rtsa mnyam snyoms bzhag /
NK102(ne)001:1082: bya ba med pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK102(ne)001:1083: mchod rten dag gi las mi bya //
NK102(ne)001:1084: glegs bam bklag par mi bya zhing //
NK102(ne)001:1085: gzugs brnyan brtsam pa'i las mi bya //
NK102(ne)001:1086: lag gi phyag rgya mi bya zhing //
NK102(ne)001:1087: ngag gi bzlas pa de la sgrib //
NK102(ne)001:1088: rnal 'byor lus kyis phyag mi bya //
NK102(ne)001:1089: rnyed dang bkur sti lta ma yin //
NK102(ne)001:1090: khe phyir ma yin grags phyir min //
NK102(ne)001:1091: ci phyir phyi rol g.yeng ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:1092: shin tu g.yeng ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:1093: de la nye ba ma yin pas //
NK102(ne)001:1094: lus 'di rnam par gnas par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:1095: zhes pa la sogs pa du ma gsungs pa rnams
NK102(ne)001:1096: skabs la lar skyon du bsdams pa skad zer na
NK102(ne)001:1097: / 'dir skyon yang nan gyis mi 'gag ste /
NK102(ne)001:1098: btang snyoms su bzhag pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1099: cher na don chen po dang ma bral bas /
NK102(ne)001:1100: spyod pa la ma 'gags sbyang rgyu med de mi dmigs pas spyad do //
NK102(ne)001:1101: rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan zhes bya ba rgya cher 'grel ba las /
NK102(ne)001:1102: thabs thob rgyu la man ngag /
NK102(ne)001:1105: skyon yon bstan pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o////de la don lta bas thag chod par bya ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:1109: don ma mthong bar bsgom pa'i skyon no //
NK102(ne)001:1111: la thabs ni rang gzhung 'chad pa'i skabs su ston no //
NK102(ne)001:1112: yon tan ni rtogs gnyis te /
NK102(ne)001:1113: pa rang gi ngo lta ba /
NK102(ne)001:1115: rtogs nas bsgoms pa'i yon tan no //
NK102(ne)001:1116: de la rtogs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK102(ne)001:1117: re zhig so so nas brjod de /
NK102(ne)001:1118: mdo sde pa'i lugs kyis rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:1120: mu bzhi skye 'gogs la sogs rdo rje gzegs ma mngon sum rjes dpag /
NK102(ne)001:1122: don dam pa'i 'dzin pa ma skyes pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1123: kun rdzob sgyu mar mthong ba'i lhag mthong gi shes pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1124: ston mun ril chos ma skyes pa'i klong la gzhal du yang med pas rtogs par smra ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:1125: de la mi shes pa nyid shes pa yang dag pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1126: cir yang ma rig pa nyid rig pa yang dag pa /
NK102(ne)001:1127: ci yang ma mthong ba nyid mthong ba yang dag pa /
NK102(ne)001:1128: ci yang mi reg pa nyid reg pa chen por rtogs pa'i lhag mthong ste /
NK102(ne)001:1129: tshul de ltar gnyis rtogs bden gnyis /
NK102(ne)001:1130: ni chos la mkhas par bshad /
NK102(ne)001:1131: deng ril 'dus par yang bshad do //
NK102(ne)001:1133: 'di las bsal bya gang yang med //
NK102(ne)001:1134: bzhag par bya ba ci yang med //
NK102(ne)001:1135: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK102(ne)001:1136: yang dag mthong bas rnam par grol //
NK102(ne)001:1138: ston mun gyi bsgom pa'i don yang yin no //
NK102(ne)001:1139: lta ba rtogs nas tshul khrims bsrung mi dgos par byang chub 'grub par gsungs te /
NK102(ne)001:1140: 'phags pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i mdo las /
NK102(ne)001:1141: tshul khrims las ni nyams sla yi //
NK102(ne)001:1144: tshul khrims bsrungs pas mtho ris skye //
NK102(ne)001:1147: chos 'byung ba med pa'i mdo las /
NK102(ne)001:1150: khrims med par sus shes shing //
NK102(ne)001:1151: tshul khrims 'chal dang tshul khrims tshul gcig don rtogs na /
NK102(ne)001:1153: tshul khrims rang bzhin de ltar sus shes pa //
NK102(ne)001:1154: tshul khrims 'chal ba de la nam yang med //
NK102(ne)001:1155: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:1156: zla ba sgron ma'i mdo las /
NK102(ne)001:1157: gang zhig chos gcig dang nyams su ldan na /
NK102(ne)001:1158: yon tan gyi chos thams cad rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:1159: chos kyi rgyal po'i mdo las /
NK102(ne)001:1160: chos gcig shes par nus na chos gcig kyang mi shes pa med do //
NK102(ne)001:1162: zla ba mar me'i mdo las /
NK102(ne)001:1163: chos gcig goms par byed pas na //
NK102(ne)001:1164: de dag thams cad goms byed 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:1166: ting nge 'dzin gyi yon tan gang yang yin no //
NK102(ne)001:1167: de dag las rgya cher gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:1168: rtogs nas bsgom pa'i yon tan ni /
NK102(ne)001:1169: don mthong nas bsgoms na thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang la sbyor nus te /
NK102(ne)001:1170: ting nge 'dzin rgyal po'i mdo las /
NK102(ne)001:1171: gal te chos la bdag med so sor rtog /
NK102(ne)001:1172: so sor de brtags gal te bsgoms pa ni //
NK102(ne)001:1173: de nyid mya ngan 'das thob 'bras bu'i rgyu //
NK102(ne)001:1174: rgyu gzhan gang gis sangs mi rgya /
NK102(ne)001:1177: yang ma rtog par sgom pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1178: rkyal ma sbyangs par chur 'jug pa'am /
NK102(ne)001:1179: long ba lam du zhugs pa dang 'dra ba'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:1181: bsam gyis mi khyab ye shes par //
NK102(ne)001:1182: bsam du med par gang 'jog pa //
NK102(ne)001:1183: byis pa de ni blun pa ste //
NK102(ne)001:1184: mun pa'i skye mched nyid du 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:1186: yon tan yang de nyid las /
NK102(ne)001:1187: bsam gyis mi khyab don shes nas //
NK102(ne)001:1188: bsam du med par 'jog pa gang //
NK102(ne)001:1189: de nyid thams cad mkhyen pa ste //
NK102(ne)001:1190: yon tan dpag tu med par 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:1191: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:1194: shin tu rnal 'byor gyi skabs na'ang /
NK102(ne)001:1195: rtogs pa gcig pu'i yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK102(ne)001:1196: rdo rje sems dpa'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las /
NK102(ne)001:1197: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'di //
NK102(ne)001:1198: dang por don rtogs mthar mi gtong //
NK102(ne)001:1201: lung dang man ngag rig pa gsum gyis rtogs par bya ste /
NK102(ne)001:1202: zhib tu gzhung phyi nas ston to //
NK102(ne)001:1204: tshad ma gsum dang ldan pa'i blos //
NK102(ne)001:1205: rnam par rtog pa'i rjes bcad pa //
NK102(ne)001:1207: mkhan po dpal dbyangs kyi bsgom lung las /
NK102(ne)001:1208: lung dang man ngag rig pas thag bcad de //
NK102(ne)001:1209: chos kyi rang bzhin yang dag yid ches bya //
NK102(ne)001:1212: de bzhin nyid las gang 'dir ji ltar lta //
NK102(ne)001:1213: de nyid snang ba yin nam mi snang ba //
NK102(ne)001:1214: 'on te sangs rgyas yin nam sangs rgyas min //
NK102(ne)001:1215: de las gzhan na sangs rgyas yod dam med //
NK102(ne)001:1216: 'di ltar cir bzhag gros kyis chod par bya //
NK102(ne)001:1218: sngags kyi du ma las rgya cher 'byung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:1222: go ba'i yul na bde ba che //
NK102(ne)001:1223: de nyid rnam dag 'jig rten yin //
NK102(ne)001:1224: zhes pas spyod yul re la ye shes chen por gsal ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:1226: mnyam par shes pa sangs rgyas kun gyi rje //
NK102(ne)001:1229: de bzhin nyid du thag chod na //
NK102(ne)001:1230: 'jig rten gnas kyang chos kyi sku //
NK102(ne)001:1231: dam par nges kyang 'jig rten 'jug /'khor ba'i mtha' la skyo ba med //
NK102(ne)001:1232: mu matha'i las kyang gcig tu rdzogs //
NK102(ne)001:1233: bdud kyi khams las nyams mi nga //
NK102(ne)001:1234: mi bzad khams la bag mi tsha //
NK102(ne)001:1235: 'dod pa'i dngos po dbyings su sbyor //
NK102(ne)001:1236: cig car nges pa'i don mthong na //
NK102(ne)001:1239: yang dag dgongs pa'i don dam pa gcig bslab pas /
NK102(ne)001:1240: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos thams cad bslab pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1241: de bzhin gcig la mkhas na /
NK102(ne)001:1242: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos thams cad la mkhas pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1243: de kho na nyid kyi don la goms na /
NK102(ne)001:1244: ting nge 'dzin 'bum phrag la goms par byed pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1245: de kho na nyid kyi don las ma 'das na /
NK102(ne)001:1246: dam tshig thams cad bsrungs pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1247: ma nor ba'i don la blo zhugs na /
NK102(ne)001:1248: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos kyi sgor zhugs pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1249: de kho na nyid ma nor ba'i don bstan na /
NK102(ne)001:1250: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos thams cad bstan pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1251: de nyid phyin ci ma log par rna ba'i dbang po la brten nas thos na /
NK102(ne)001:1252: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos thos pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1253: de kho na nyid mngon du mthong na rgyal ba thams cad kyi zhal mthong ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:1254: zhes pa la sogs pa rgya cher gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:1256: kun tu bzang po che ba la rang gnas pa las /
NK102(ne)001:1257: bsgom pa mi gtso rtogs pa gtso //
NK102(ne)001:1258: rtogs pa gdeng du ma tshud na //
NK102(ne)001:1259: bsgom pa mtshan ma'i ngang la bsgom //
NK102(ne)001:1260: rtsol ba nyon mongs zhen pas rtsol //
NK102(ne)001:1263: rtogs pa'i klung du don spyod dang //
NK102(ne)001:1264: rang byung ye shes de las 'char //
NK102(ne)001:1267: rtogs pa klung du su 'dris pa //
NK102(ne)001:1268: mi zhes bya ba sangs rgyas yin //
NK102(ne)001:1273: rnam shes brgyad ye shes su /
NK102(ne)001:1275: rang rig rgyal po goms pa yis //
NK102(ne)001:1278: rtogs nas bsgom pa kho nar gsungs te /
NK102(ne)001:1279: ting nge 'dzin dang thabs dang rna brgyud ma mnyan par bsgom pa yang bzhugs so //
NK102(ne)001:1280: des gnas su gcig pu 'dug pa'i dpe ni /
NK102(ne)001:1281: gcan gzan rgyal po ji bzhin gnas te /
NK102(ne)001:1282: seng ge ni 'jigs pa dang bral bas zla spangs te /
NK102(ne)001:1283: de bzhin du yang rnal 'byor pa g.yeng ba'i grogs spangs te /
NK102(ne)001:1287: sngags pa seng ge bzhin du rgyu //
NK102(ne)001:1289: 'dir rnam par mi rtog pa dang bral dgod pa ci ste /
NK102(ne)001:1290: don bsam pa yang g.yang shes phyir ces pa /
NK102(ne)001:1291: dngos po la ltung du med kyang ltung ba'i gol
NK102(ne)001:1292: sa shes par bya ba'i phyir ston tsan gnyis pa
NK102(ne)001:1293: ma h+aa a ti'i mi rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1295: de la phyir mi rtog pa la gsum ste /
NK102(ne)001:1296: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i bla ma'i rtog pa dang
NK102(ne)001:1297: ngo shes par byas pas mi rtog pa ngos bzung
NK102(ne)001:1298: sla'o // de yang rtog pa dbral ba'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:1299: dang po la rtog pa bshad de /
NK102(ne)001:1300: snang la rtog pa dang mi snang la rtog med pa la med par 'dzin pa /
NK102(ne)001:1302: snang la rtog pa la gsum ngo bo la rtog pa /
NK102(ne)001:1304: ngo bo dang mtshan ma dbyer med pa la rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1306: ngo bor snang la rtog pa ni bzhi ste /
NK102(ne)001:1307: dngos po'i rang bzhin la rtog pa yod med snang stong ji ltar du 'dug ces /
NK102(ne)001:1309: gnyen nyon mongs pa la sogs pa spang ba'o /
NK102(ne)001:1312: de kho na nyid la rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1315: mtshan ma la rtog pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1316: kun rdzob tu rtog pa'i lta ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:1317: ngo bo dang mtshan ma med par dbyer med /
NK102(ne)001:1318: snang ba la rtog pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1319: don dam pa la rtog pa'i lta ba so sor rtog pa'i shes rab bo //
NK102(ne)001:1320: gzhan yang zhar la bshad pa /
NK102(ne)001:1321: ngo bo nyid kyi rtog pa cir yang shar bas /
NK102(ne)001:1326: nges par 'jog pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1329: de dag re re la mi rtog pa re re rtog pa kho na'i phyogs zhi tshe /
NK102(ne)001:1330: mi rtog pa phyogs re re yod /
NK102(ne)001:1332: mi rtog pa ni 'jig rten pa'i mi rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1333: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i mi rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1335: de la 'jig rten pa'i mi rtog pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1339: 'jig rten las 'das pa ni nyan thos 'gog pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1340: rang rgyal zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK102(ne)001:1341: de ni byis pa nyer spyod kyi bsam gtan zhes kyang bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:1342: bla ma'i mi rtog pa ni theg pa chen po ste /
NK102(ne)001:1343: de la don rab 'byed pa'i bsam gtan lhag mthong ste /
NK102(ne)001:1344: so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab kyi rgyu las byung ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:1345: de bzhin nyid dmigs kyi bsam gtan ni mtshan ma med pa'i zhi gnas so //
NK102(ne)001:1346: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bsam gtan ni zhi gnas lhag mthong zung du 'brel ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:1347: de dag la'ang mos dang po /
NK102(ne)001:1348: pa las byung ba'i mi dmigs pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1349: shin tu mi dmigs pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1350: rjes su mi dmigs par bshad de go sla bas ma sbyar ro //
NK102(ne)001:1352: snang la mi rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1353: mi snang ba la mi rtog pa gnyis las /
NK102(ne)001:1354: snang la mi rtog pa ni gnyis te /
NK102(ne)001:1355: mtshan mar snang la mi rtog pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1356: gzhan dang po ngo bor snang la mi rtog pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1357: mig sogs kyi dbang po yul la rten 'brel /
NK102(ne)001:1358: dbang la dmigs pa'i shes pa rtog la med kyi 'dzin pa /
NK102(ne)001:1359: pa dang bral ba rnams so //
NK102(ne)001:1360: ngo bor snang la mi rtog pa yang gsum ste /
NK102(ne)001:1361: yod pa'i ngo bor snang la mi rtog pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1362: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i gzhan gyi dbang rten 'brel las
NK102(ne)001:1363: byung ba sgyu ma tsam pas rang rgyud pa'i rtog
NK102(ne)001:1364: pa med / dbang yid la byed pa'i shes pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1365: mu stegs can dag gi bdag tu yid la byed
NK102(ne)001:1366: pa'i shes gzhan med par yid kyang de la dmigs
NK102(ne)001:1368: stong pa'i ngo bor snang la mi rtog pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1369: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i yongs su grub pa bsgom pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1370: dbu ma'i lam sgom pa'i shes pa lhag mthong ste /
NK102(ne)001:1371: de la gong gi mi dmigs pa tshang ngo //
NK102(ne)001:1372: de las khyad du gnyis su med pa'i mi rtog pa ma h+aa yo ga'o //
NK102(ne)001:1373: lhun gyis grub pa'i mi rtog pa chen po a ti yo ga'o //
NK102(ne)001:1374: de dag ni gol sa ngos bzung ba'i phyir rim par bkod pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1375: de la tsen men rim gyis 'jug pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1376: rang bzhin la rtogs pa'i mtshan ma la sogs pa dang gnyen po rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1377: de kho na nyid la rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1378: thob pa la rtog pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1380: mi rtog pa la 'jug pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:1381: de yang mi rtog pa'i gzungs las /
NK102(ne)001:1382: yid bzhin nor bu rin po che 'dod pa'i mis
NK102(ne)001:1383: brag shin tu sra zhing mkhregs pa'i 'og na yid
NK102(ne)001:1384: kyis rkos shig / rin po che 'di lta ste /
NK102(ne)001:1389: de dag la rin po che'i brag gsum /
NK102(ne)001:1390: brag shin tu sra ba dang bzhi'i 'og nas /
NK102(ne)001:1392: yid bzhin nor bu bdag dang gzhan don thams cad rdzogs par 'byung ba 'thob pa de bzhin du /
NK102(ne)001:1393: rnam par mi rtog pa 'dod pas /
NK102(ne)001:1394: rang bzhin la rtog pa'i mtshan ma dang /
NK102(ne)001:1395: gnyen po la rtog pa'i mtshan ma dang /
NK102(ne)001:1396: de kho na nyid la rtog pa'i mtshan ma dang /
NK102(ne)001:1397: thob pa la rtog pa'i mtshan ma de bzhi dang bral bar byas nas /
NK102(ne)001:1398: mtshan ma gsum po la de kho na yis yod la ma byas par bsgom na 'grub bo //
NK102(ne)001:1403: smon pa med pa'i sgo gsum rim par bsgom pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1404: zhi gnas lhag mthong la sogs pa bsgom pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1405: ston mun ni cig car 'jug pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:1406: dang po nas re mos pa med par don dam
NK102(ne)001:1407: pa ma skyes pa nyid la cig car slob ste
NK102(ne)001:1408: / shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i mdo las /
NK102(ne)001:1409: dang po sems bskyed pa nas rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa nyid yid la bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:1412: las dang po pas sems dang po bskyed pa nas nye bar brtsams te /
NK102(ne)001:1413: chos thams cad dmigs su med pa la bslab par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:1416: dang por skye 'gag med pa'i sems bskyed na /
NK102(ne)001:1417: tha ma skye 'gag med pa'i 'bras bu thob par 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:1418: zhes pa la sogs pa phyi nas kyang ston no //
NK102(ne)001:1419: cig car 'jug pa'i sgo slob dpon so so'i bzhed kyang /
NK102(ne)001:1421: po chen po bo d+he dar mo ta ras bshad pa las /
NK102(ne)001:1422: yang dag pa la phyogs shing rtogs pa spangs te /
NK102(ne)001:1424: bdag kyang med gzhan yang med /
NK102(ne)001:1425: ma rabs dang 'phags pa mnyam zhing gcig ste /
NK102(ne)001:1426: mi 'gyur bar brtan par gnas na /
NK102(ne)001:1427: de phan chad yi ge dang bstan pa'i rjes su mi 'brang ngo //
NK102(ne)001:1428: 'di ni yang dag pa'i don gyi rnal du phab pa rnam par rtog pa med pa /
NK102(ne)001:1429: zhi zhing bya ba med pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:1430: de ni don la mi 'jug pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1431: bsam gtan gyi mkhan po 'dug pas bshad pa /
NK102(ne)001:1433: mi dran pa ni ting nge 'dzin /
NK102(ne)001:1434: sgyu ma'i sems mi 'byung ba ni shes rab bo //
NK102(ne)001:1435: bsam gtan gyi mkhan po bdud 'dul snying pos bshad pa las /
NK102(ne)001:1436: ci yang mi dran pa ni sangs rgyas dran pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1437: 'di nyid la bltas te sems snyoms na /
NK102(ne)001:1438: de bzhin gshegs pa yang dag pa'i sku nyid yin no //
NK102(ne)001:1439: bsam gtan gyi mkhan po a d+ha na her gyis bshad pa las /
NK102(ne)001:1440: sems ji bzhin du mnyam pa ni rnal 'byor nges pa'i lam mo //
NK102(ne)001:1441: mkhan po ma h+aa ya na gyis bshad pa las /
NK102(ne)001:1442: chos nyid bsam du med la mi rtog par bzhag go //
NK102(ne)001:1444: bsgom pa po'i rig pa nyid ma skyes pas ma
NK102(ne)001:1445: skyes pa'i don ched du dran par byar yang med
NK102(ne)001:1447: de la las dang po sngar ma sbyangs pa rnams kyis /
NK102(ne)001:1448: 'jug tu gtub pa'i lung dang rigs pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1452: yul gzugs dkar na rnam shes dkar po skye ba dang 'dra ste /
NK102(ne)001:1453: yul bya ba sam med pas shes pa yang bya bsam med par gsal lo //
NK102(ne)001:1454: nang pa'i mi rtog pa de bzhin nyid ni /
NK102(ne)001:1455: ma h+aa yo ga'i gzhung gis /
NK102(ne)001:1456: chos thams cad ni rang rig par gsal ba nyid bden pa gnyis med pa /
NK102(ne)001:1457: byed pa pos ma byas pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1459: dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:1461: dngos po bsgom pa med pa'i dngos //
NK102(ne)001:1462: bsgom par bya ba bsgom pa med //
NK102(ne)001:1463: de ltar dngos po dngos med pas //
NK102(ne)001:1464: bsgom pa dmigs su med pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1466: gnyis su med pa'i de bzhin nyid ni log nas mi gnyer /
NK102(ne)001:1467: ye shes ni dbyings la dmigs par mi byed pa de la rnam pa'i chos la spangs bral te /
NK102(ne)001:1469: de la sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las /
NK102(ne)001:1470: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i rang rig nyid //
NK102(ne)001:1471: dmigs med tshul du rang snang ngo //
NK102(ne)001:1473: a ti yo ga'i lhag pa'i rnal 'byor gyi lhun rdzogs de bzhiin nyid ni /
NK102(ne)001:1474: snang srid kyi chos so cog rang byung gi ye
NK102(ne)001:1475: shes rnam par dag pa'i klong du sel med par
NK102(ne)001:1476: ye nas rang gsal ba la /
NK102(ne)001:1477: rgyu dang 'bras bu ril ma btsal bar lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1479: de la g.yo rdul ming yang med pas /
NK102(ne)001:1480: rang rig pa ma bzhag ma g.yos ma bslad ma
NK102(ne)001:1481: zhugs par lhan ne lhang nge ye gsal bar ci
NK102(ne)001:1482: zhig bsgom / ci zhig dran par byar yod de med /
NK102(ne)001:1483: med pa'i don de nyid kho na yod /
NK102(ne)001:1484: de dang du len pa su zhig ste /
NK102(ne)001:1485: ye mi rtog pa chen po la /
NK102(ne)001:1486: snang ba bkag pa yang med la /
NK102(ne)001:1487: de la rtogs pa med de /
NK102(ne)001:1488: mi rtog pa nyid kyang bla dwags so //
NK102(ne)001:1490: snang ba rgya mtsho chen po bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:1491: mi rtog nam mkha'i mkha' ltar yangs //
NK102(ne)001:1493: de dag gi khyad par skad kyi gdang bu bzhin te /
NK102(ne)001:1494: dper na skad gdang la mtho dman yod par dang 'dra ste /
NK102(ne)001:1495: mi rtog pa 'di bzhi yang khyad par ston tsen ma h+aa a ti /
NK102(ne)001:1497: tsen man rim gyis 'jug pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1498: sngar bshad pa ltar dmigs pa la sha thang bar 'bad nas ma dmigs pa skye ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:1499: dngos po gtan tshigs kyis gzhal nas /
NK102(ne)001:1500: dbu ma'i don dang du len to //
NK102(ne)001:1501: ston mun ni bdag gzhan chos so cog ye nas ma skyes pa la /
NK102(ne)001:1502: des skyes pa don du gnyer ba ni sems bslad pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:1503: des nam yang don chen po mi mthong ste /
NK102(ne)001:1504: dper na bya gag gi rtsal gyis rgya mtsho mi 'khrugs pa dang 'dra'o //
NK102(ne)001:1505: 'on tang cir yang ma bsams na chos nyid la zhugs par 'dod de /
NK102(ne)001:1506: de yang ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo las /
NK102(ne)001:1507: rgyu rkyen rten 'brel bstan pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:1508: rim par 'jug ste zhes pa yang //
NK102(ne)001:1509: rmongs pa rnams la thabs kyis gsungs //
NK102(ne)001:1510: lhun gyis grub pa'i chos 'di la //
NK102(ne)001:1511: rim gyis sbyangs pa ci zhig yod //
NK102(ne)001:1512: mtha' las 'das pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK102(ne)001:1513: gong bur 'du shes ji ltar lta //
NK102(ne)001:1514: cung zad tsam yang khas blang med //
NK102(ne)001:1515: de tshe sems ni nam mkha' ste //
NK102(ne)001:1516: sangs rgyas dang yang spyod yul gcig /
NK102(ne)001:1518: dbang po tha shal gyi don du rim 'jug bstan te /
NK102(ne)001:1519: sbur bu'i bros kyis ri rab kha la mi phyin pa ltar /
NK102(ne)001:1520: dmigs pa can gyi mi rtog par bshad do //
NK102(ne)001:1521: de lta bu'i ston mun bya ba dang bral bar gsol ba yang /
NK102(ne)001:1526: ril don dam pa'i bden pa stong pa ma skyes par lta ba der gcig par 'dod de /
NK102(ne)001:1527: 'on tang res 'jog skye med ni bden pa /
NK102(ne)001:1528: skye med ni mi bden pa'o /
NK102(ne)001:1529: can des rnal 'byor chen po'i rang bzhin bden par dbyer med pa mi mthong ste /
NK102(ne)001:1530: rang gi lta bas bsgribs so //
NK102(ne)001:1533: 'bras thu bas sa gzhi mi mthong ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:1534: khab mig 'jug pa gyen du lta yang nam mkha' mi mthong ba dang 'dra'o //
NK102(ne)001:1535: de yang rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung las /
NK102(ne)001:1536: rang bzhin skye 'gag med pa nam mkha' bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:1537: des ni kun 'dus kun kun gyi dngos gzhi ris med /
NK102(ne)001:1539: ci yang mi snang ba nyid skyon med do //
NK102(ne)001:1541: ni 'khrul pa yin phyir gtub pa min //
NK102(ne)001:1543: stong pa ni ci yang snang mi nus pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1545: bzhin nyid ni 'gro ba'i don dbugs 'byin pa'i dkyil
NK102(ne)001:1546: 'khor zhi khro la sogs pa cir yang bsgyur du
NK102(ne)001:1547: rung ba'i don nyid kyis gsol lo //
NK102(ne)001:1548: rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo ga gnyis su med par gsol bas /
NK102(ne)001:1550: lhun gyis grub pa chen po ni ma rtogs so //
NK102(ne)001:1552: ma h+aa yo ga pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:1554: thabs mang pos de bzhin nyid goms par byed /
NK102(ne)001:1555: 'gro don du sprul pa spro ba yod pa nyid kyis /
NK102(ne)001:1556: bya ba med pa'i don bdag lhun gyis rdzogs pa nyid pas /
NK102(ne)001:1557: mngon du yang mi byed mi slob /
NK102(ne)001:1558: sprul pa ril gyi 'byung gnas 'gro don rgyun mi
NK102(ne)001:1559: 'chad pa kho na ye shes chen po yin pas
NK102(ne)001:1560: / de kho na bdag gi mdzad spyod yin pas
NK102(ne)001:1561: don ma mthong ba snga ma dang 'dra dbu ma
NK102(ne)001:1563: dper na gnya' shing ri bo /
NK102(ne)001:1564: 'dzin gyi kha nas lhun po'i ri bo mchog rab /
NK102(ne)001:1567: gser ri 'dzin gyi rgyal po gnya' shing 'dzin //
NK102(ne)001:1568: thog tu phyin yang lhun po'i rtse ma mthong //
NK102(ne)001:1569: thams cad gnyis med gsol ba'i rnal 'byor ma h+aa pa /
NK102(ne)001:1571: rtsol mtha' rang sgribs ngang chen mthong ba med //
NK102(ne)001:1574: byang chub yan lag kun gyi sgo //
NK102(ne)001:1575: cha lugs bsgom pas chu zla bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:1577: bsgom pas byis pa'i spyod yul bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:1578: dkyil 'khor khro gnyer cha lugs kyis //
NK102(ne)001:1579: khro bdag chen po'i yul bzung nas //
NK102(ne)001:1580: yi ge mngon du gyur na yang //
NK102(ne)001:1581: zhi ba de nyid mthong ba min //
NK102(ne)001:1583: rnal 'byor chen po nang pas mtshan yig 'bru dang mtshan ma'i phyag mtshan la sogs pa /
NK102(ne)001:1584: ma'i ting nge 'dzin las su rung nas rtags thon yang /
NK102(ne)001:1585: lhun grub la dmigs pa yod pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:1587: dper na nyi ma'i snying por bltas na /
NK102(ne)001:1588: slar mi mthong gi mig ljir 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK102(ne)001:1589: de ni lta ba'i khyad par tsam ste zhib tu 'og nas ston to //
NK102(ne)001:1590: rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan zhes bya ba rgya
NK102(ne)001:1591: cher 'grel pa las 'jug thabs dgos ched kyi khyad
NK102(ne)001:1592: par bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o////'dir lhun gyis rdzogs
NK102(ne)001:1593: pa'i theg pa'i gol sa shes par bya ba'i phyir
NK102(ne)001:1594: / gzhung bzhi bkod pa'i dang po mdo sde stong
NK102(ne)001:1595: par bsgom pa la ci'i phyir rim 'jug ces bya
NK102(ne)001:1596: shing tog ma li ka dang 'dra bar rim gyis
NK102(ne)001:1601: ri bo che la 'dzeg pa'ang gom gcig gom gnyis phyin pas rdol ba dang 'dra bar /
NK102(ne)001:1602: rgyal ba'i chos kyi sku bsgrub pa yang /
NK102(ne)001:1604: zhi gnas lhag mthong la sngar rim par sbyangs nas /
NK102(ne)001:1605: je je la sa non par 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:1606: de yang stug po bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK102(ne)001:1607: rnam shes bdun dang bcas pa yang //
NK102(ne)001:1608: de bzhin kun gzhi rnam par shes /
NK102(ne)001:1609: ting nge 'dzin gyi yongs sbyangs pas //
NK102(ne)001:1610: rnal 'byor can gyis rtag tu mthong //
NK102(ne)001:1611: de ltar shin tu bzang po'i gser //
NK102(ne)001:1612: gser gyi dbyibs na mi snang bzang po'i ngo bor /
NK102(ne)001:1614: gsal bas shin tu zhib btags na //
NK102(ne)001:1615: yongs su sbyangs na snang bar 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:1617: de la lta bas thag bcad de /
NK102(ne)001:1618: dang por lta bas so sor rtogs pa'i shes rab
NK102(ne)001:1619: la brten pas rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i gtan
NK102(ne)001:1620: tshigs kyis dngos po mi rang rgyud du /
NK102(ne)001:1622: dper na shing rta'i rtsibs shing dang sgyogs bu chung
NK102(ne)001:1623: dang 'khor lo la sogs pa'i rnam pa shing rtar
NK102(ne)001:1625: shing rta'i ngo bo rtsibs shing la yang med /
NK102(ne)001:1626: de bzhin du sgyogs bu chung la sogs pa gang la yang med pa ltar /
NK102(ne)001:1627: dngos po ka ba bum pa la sogs pa rgyu
NK102(ne)001:1628: rkyen rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba tshogs bdo ba
NK102(ne)001:1629: tsam zhig tu snang yang don dam par rgyu rkyen
NK102(ne)001:1630: gang la yang dngos po sgyu ma'i chos grub pa
NK102(ne)001:1631: med de / rnam pa med pa /
NK102(ne)001:1635: de'i mtshan nyid stong pa bco brgyad pa la sogs pa'i ngo bor 'dod pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1636: de lta bu la sogs pa'i gtan tshigs rgya che bas thag bcad nas bsgom pa'ang /
NK102(ne)001:1637: dang po tshad med pa bzhi la rim gyis bsgom ste /
NK102(ne)001:1638: dang po la snying rje bsgom ste /
NK102(ne)001:1639: sems can rnams don dam pa ma skyes pa'i don
NK102(ne)001:1640: de ni mthong shin tu sdug bsngal ba e ma
NK102(ne)001:1641: hohzhesa shin tu gdung bar bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:1642: de yang skye dka' na dang por pha ma dang phu nu slob lugs /
NK102(ne)001:1644: de nas las su rung nas mchi ma dran pa tsam gyis 'ong tsam na /
NK102(ne)001:1645: sems can bar ma la bsgom /
NK102(ne)001:1646: de las su rung na dgra la bsgom /
NK102(ne)001:1647: de brtan nas sems can yongs la bsgom /
NK102(ne)001:1648: de yang snying rje gangs ltar 'tshor ba yi //
NK102(ne)001:1649: gzhan gyi sdug bsngal nyid tshogs la //
NK102(ne)001:1650: gdung zhing snying la bzhu ba bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:1651: kha mig gnyis nas mchi ma 'dzag /
NK102(ne)001:1652: ces gsungs pas de bzhin bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:1653: de nas byams pa kun la dbye ba med par
NK102(ne)001:1654: bu gcig pa la ma byams pa ltar sems can
NK102(ne)001:1655: rnams bdag gi bur bsam pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1656: dga' bas 'gyod pa med par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:1657: btang snyoms kyi yal bar mi dor ro //
NK102(ne)001:1662: gtod pa med pa ni bslab pa'i lam mo //
NK102(ne)001:1663: chen po ni de tshad med chen po de dang po la med /
NK102(ne)001:1664: bzhin gshegs pa la mnga' ste thob 'bras bu'i skabs na bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:1667: dbu ma'i bsgom rim rnam gsum las 'byung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:1668: bden pa gnyis bsgom pa yang /
NK102(ne)001:1669: dang po kun rdzob kyi bden pa yang gnyis te /
NK102(ne)001:1670: de la yang dag pa dang log pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1671: de la yang dag pa'i kun rdzob kyi rnam grangs
NK102(ne)001:1672: phung po lnga la sogs pa'i rang bzhin brdzun pa
NK102(ne)001:1673: tsam pa / de'i mtshan nyid brtags pas dben pa don byed mi nus pa /
NK102(ne)001:1678: dga' skyes shing snang ba la /
NK102(ne)001:1687: ma brtags na nyams dga' ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:1688: de dag drang ba don gyi mdo sde pa ra gsungs pa /
NK102(ne)001:1691: skar ma rab rib de kho na nyid la sgrib /
NK102(ne)001:1692: mar me mar me snum dang ras la brten /
NK102(ne)001:1695: sgyu ma zil pa chu bur log nor bar snang /
NK102(ne)001:1698: rmi yul dang longs spyod dus gsum 'das pa med /
NK102(ne)001:1701: lam glog dang sprin lta bu //
NK102(ne)001:1702: 'dus byas chos kyang 'dra zhes pas don gyis /
NK102(ne)001:1703: chos thams cad skar ma dang 'dra ba nyin mo med nub mo yod /
NK102(ne)001:1704: dar sar yod na ma rig pa med /
NK102(ne)001:1705: la sogs pa sgyu ma tsam mo //
NK102(ne)001:1706: de rtogs kun rdzob ngo bo /
NK102(ne)001:1707: pa'i lta ba ni ji bzhin pa shes 'di yang lhag mthong /
NK102(ne)001:1709: de bsgom pa shes pa'i rang bzhin gtsor shes rab
NK102(ne)001:1710: dang ting nge 'dzin mtshungs par ldan pa'i phung po
NK102(ne)001:1714: rtse gcig pa dang 'byed so sor /
NK102(ne)001:1716: de bsgom pa'i yon tan ni bka' de bas gsungs pa'i /
NK102(ne)001:1717: la mi rmongs pa la sogs pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1719: yang dag pa ma yin pa'i kun rdzob ni //
NK102(ne)001:1720: snang la chu zla me long nang gi 'od lta bu /
NK102(ne)001:1721: don byed mi nus pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:1722: mi mo gsham gyi bu sogs /
NK102(ne)001:1723: snang la brtags pas bsus pa dang med par dgags pa rnams dang yid gzugs la sogs pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1724: don byed mi nus mi snang /
NK102(ne)001:1726: de'i rang bzhin ni gzhan chu dang zla ba'i rkyen la sogs pa /
NK102(ne)001:1728: brtags pa'i mtshan nyid go rim bzhin no //
NK102(ne)001:1730: spyi shes pa ma 'khrul pa'i mthun snang la /
NK102(ne)001:1735: bye brag ni mthun snang la don byed mi nus pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1738: 'dus byas kyi mtshan skye rga na 'chi bzhi /
NK102(ne)001:1740: gnyis mi snang ba don byed mi nus pa /
NK102(ne)001:1741: pa ni gong ma las bzlog snang ba rtag tu sogs pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:1743: de yang rang gi ngo bo mu stegs rtag pa ngo bos med pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:1747: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob nyid kyang sgyu mar bltas te 'dog pa ci nyes zhe na /
