NK102(ne)001:10673: rnam par thams cad du phyin pa /
NK102(ne)001:10675: dmigs pa med pas byang chub bo //
NK102(ne)001:10676: rnam pa sna tshogs rang rig cir yang /
NK102(ne)001:10679: mkhas pas shes rab ril gsal bas /
NK102(ne)001:10681: thams cad gsal bas ting 'dzin no //
NK102(ne)001:10686: med pas rab nyid chos sku /
NK102(ne)001:10688: ngo sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bo /
NK102(ne)001:10690: de dngos po kun la khyad par du /
NK102(ne)001:10691: rnam par 'phags pas phul nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:10692: de bzhin nyid du thob par bya med de'i /
NK102(ne)001:10694: yod pas bla na med pa nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:10697: dpag tu med pas na gsang ba nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:10698: 'phra bas mi gsal ba ngo bo bzung dka' ba'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:10701: thams cad 'byung 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das /
NK102(ne)001:10703: ngo bo mtha' gang du yang /
NK102(ne)001:10704: mi 'gyur bas de kho na nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:10705: go bsgrub bya chos sku gnyis med phyir /
NK102(ne)001:10706: 'phang nyid pas byang chub pa la /
NK102(ne)001:10710: song khyab pas ril la snums /
NK102(ne)001:10713: gyur pas rtsa ba nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:10714: thams cad rgyal ba ril dang lam chos /
NK102(ne)001:10716: de la byung bas yab rgyal ba ril bzhi /
NK102(ne)001:10718: gdung brgyud 'dzin pas dus gsum du mi nub pa'i rgyal ba'i sras nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:10719: rang byung bas dbang bdag sus kyang ma byas te rag ma lus pa /
NK102(ne)001:10721: de bzhin nyid pas gdung rgyud chad pa med phyir rang par gyi /
NK102(ne)001:10723: 'da' de kho na nyid la 'brel log spyi tshugs gar 'dres kyang 'da' ba med /
NK102(ne)001:10724: bar dka' bas thugs dam chen po nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:10725: rnam de kho na nyid dpe ril gzung /
NK102(ne)001:10727: zad mi shes yon tan thams cad du /
NK102(ne)001:10728: pas gter chen po nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:10732: bya ba med pas dran pa nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:10733: rnam par brjid pas lta bas mi ngoms mi 'gyur /
NK102(ne)001:10735: smra brjod pa ril lhun gyis grub /
NK102(ne)001:10737: thams cad mkhyen pas thugs spyod yul med par rang gsal /
NK102(ne)001:10739: 'dod rgu 'byung bas gdul bya la bsam pa dang mthun par /
NK102(ne)001:10741: bya ba byed pas phrin las mdzad par ma gyur pa med pas /
NK102(ne)001:10743: yul la 'gro bas yul gyi chos ril la son te gnyis med /
NK102(ne)001:10746: nyid la spyod pas longs spyod chen spyod yul med par bdag nyid du /
NK102(ne)001:10748: rgyur gyur pas thams cad kyi /
NK102(ne)001:10750: dgos pa tshang bas tshogs chen po'o //
NK102(ne)001:10753: med pas don thams cad 'grub pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:10754: sna cir yang bltas pa ltar shar /
NK102(ne)001:10757: mar byung bas phyag rgya ji snyed du /
NK102(ne)001:10759: gang yang ma rdzogs pa med do //
NK102(ne)001:10760: gzhan nas mi tshol lam pa'i 'bras bu /
NK102(ne)001:10762: rang las byung bas nye ba'i bsnyen pa nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:10763: snying po nyid pas bsgrub pa nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:10764: 'bras bu nyid pas bsgrub pa chen po'o //
NK102(ne)001:10765: zhes gsungs pa'i don gyis snying po byang chub ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid ni /
NK102(ne)001:10769: thams cad du yang rang shar la cir yang gnas med par bstan to //
NK102(ne)001:10771: de nyid mi g.yo nam mkha' la //
NK102(ne)001:10772: g.yo rdul tha snyad ji snyed pa //
NK102(ne)001:10773: mi rtag ye shes rgya mtsho che //
NK102(ne)001:10774: gcig las rnam pa yongs kyis med //
NK102(ne)001:10775: rang byung lhun grub dkyil 'khor che //
NK102(ne)001:10777: snang srid 'khor ba'i kha brgyud kyang //
NK102(ne)001:10778: snying po dbyings la gar ma phyin //
NK102(ne)001:10779: mtha' thug med pa'i zhing bgrod kyang //
NK102(ne)001:10780: snying po de las g.yos pa med //
NK102(ne)001:10781: dpag med rgyal ba'i sku bskrun kyang //
NK102(ne)001:10782: snying po yongs su 'phel ba med //
NK102(ne)001:10783: sems can mtha' thug med byung yang //
NK102(ne)001:10784: de nyid de la sgrib pa med //
NK102(ne)001:10788: ci ga snang ba thams cad snang ba de gsang sngags sam /
NK102(ne)001:10789: 'on te thams cad kyi rang bzhin mi snang ba de gsang sngags sam /
NK102(ne)001:10790: ci gnyi ga ma yin pa cig gsang sngags yin /
NK102(ne)001:10791: gsang ba'i bdag pos smras pa /
NK102(ne)001:10792: lang ka'i bdag po thams cad snang ba de gsang sngags ma yin /
NK102(ne)001:10793: gal te snang ba de gsang sngags yin na ni /
NK102(ne)001:10794: gsang sngags zhes brjod pa nyid dang 'gal la /
NK102(ne)001:10795: gang sems can gyi 'du shes dang /
NK102(ne)001:10796: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yang khyad par med par 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:10797: de las gzhan yang gsang sngags yod pa ma yin /
NK102(ne)001:10798: gal te de las gzhan pa 'ba' zhig gsang sngags yin na ni /
NK102(ne)001:10799: thams cad chos nyid du ma 'dus par 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:10800: thams cad kyi rang bzhin mi snang ba de gsang sngags ma yin /
NK102(ne)001:10801: gal te mi snang ba de gsang sngags yin na ni /
NK102(ne)001:10802: gzhan mu chad pa dag yang dag par rdzogs pa nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:10803: gang gnyi ga ma yin pa de yang gsang sngags ma yin /
NK102(ne)001:10804: gal te gnyi ga ma yin pa zhig gsang sngags yin na ni /
NK102(ne)001:10805: gsang sngags zhes bya ba zhig btsal bas rnyed pas gnas gzhan med de /
NK102(ne)001:10807: gsang sngags zhes bya ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:10808: snang ba dang mi snang ba gnyis su med pas /
NK102(ne)001:10809: gnyis kyi ngo bo nyid las grol ba dbu mar
NK102(ne)001:10810: mi dmigs pa gang yin pa de kho na nyid
NK102(ne)001:10812: 'on tang na ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid
NK102(ne)001:10813: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba de'i mtshan nyid
NK102(ne)001:10815: yin yin du bzung du mi 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:10816: lhag pa'i rnal 'byor chen po che la gnas pa
NK102(ne)001:10817: yang bsam pa thams cad ma bkag bral bas snang
NK102(ne)001:10819: de ci'i phyir thams cad kyang bdag yin la /
NK102(ne)001:10820: bdag thams cad du snang bas /
NK102(ne)001:10821: snang ba dang mi dmigs pa'i don dus gcig tu dmigs gtad med par gsal lo //
NK102(ne)001:10823: dper na sgyu ma'i mkhan po zhig gis /
NK102(ne)001:10826: 'gro ba bzang mo la sogs par sprul nas /
NK102(ne)001:10827: 'thab rtsod pa dang rol mo'i dga' ba ci byed kyang /
NK102(ne)001:10828: ltad mo pa 'khrul pa dag ngo mtshar skye la /
NK102(ne)001:10829: sgyu ma'i mkhan po la ni ngo mtshar med de /
NK102(ne)001:10830: de dag 'dug pa dang sgyu ma yin pas /
NK102(ne)001:10831: de dpung bu chung la sogs pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:10832: de pa med pa gnyi ga shes pa dang bral lo //
NK102(ne)001:10833: de ltar gnad chud pa'i mi chen po dag ni /
NK102(ne)001:10834: bsgom pa la blo 'jug pa yang med /
NK102(ne)001:10841: mtshan ma ldang ba ci byung yang rang 'byung dbyings su rang gsal te /
NK102(ne)001:10842: skyes bu de la blo dang lus bdag med par ga la gnod de /
NK102(ne)001:10843: nyam thag pa tsam yang med par shes par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:10844: de rtas pa'i rmi ltas dang mngon sum du ngan
NK102(ne)001:10845: sri sdug bsngal bag mi tsha ba dang bdud la
NK102(ne)001:10846: mi 'jigs pa dang skye shis mi 'jigs pa dang
NK102(ne)001:10847: 'khor ba la mi skyo ba dang 'dod spyod dbyings
NK102(ne)001:10848: su sbyor ba dang tshig la mi dad pa la
NK102(ne)001:10850: lta bas na don de thog mar lta bas thag
NK102(ne)001:10851: bcad du med par chod par bya ba shin tu
NK102(ne)001:10852: gces so // rmongs pa dag gis lta ba phyogs las gol te /
NK102(ne)001:10853: ji bzhin pa dngos po 'di kho na snang ba
NK102(ne)001:10854: ltar 'dod pa na rdzogs chen du khas 'ches nas
NK102(ne)001:10855: skye bo phal pa'i sa la gnas so //
NK102(ne)001:10856: dmigs 'dzin gol pa sogs sngar bstan par zad do //
NK102(ne)001:10857: de lta bu don gyi gser 'chang ba'i lta ba'i dpe /
NK102(ne)001:10860: blo 'jug tu med pa'i bsgom lugs dang gnad thun mong du ston /
NK102(ne)001:10862: de yang bsgom pa las 'jug pa'i bzhag thabs dang /
NK102(ne)001:10864: de la lus kyi bzhag thabs ni /
NK102(ne)001:10865: bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor man chad lhang lus bcos la bzhag pa med de /
NK102(ne)001:10866: lus 'dzin pa'i 'du shes dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:10867: lus la 'dug thabs nges par bzhag pa med do //
NK102(ne)001:10868: 'o na 'og ma'i skyil mo krung la sogs pa dgag gam zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:10869: lus su ma dmigs phan chad dgag tu med de /
NK102(ne)001:10870: ched du dang du len pa med na /
NK102(ne)001:10871: skyil mo la sogs pa gan rkyal khas bub gang du 'gre yang 'gal med de /
NK102(ne)001:10872: rnal 'byor nyid gang bde bar bya ste /
NK102(ne)001:10873: snyoms las kyis ni bya ba ma yin no //
NK102(ne)001:10874: nga'i yid ches par bya ba'i rgyab gnon du /
NK102(ne)001:10876: lus sems ma skyes gzhi med pas //
NK102(ne)001:10877: kha ltar bcos pa'i kha na med //
NK102(ne)001:10880: sgyu ma bzhin du lus shes na //
NK102(ne)001:10882: spyod lam gsum gyis gnas pa gang //
NK102(ne)001:10883: ched du bya med byed pa'ang med //
NK102(ne)001:10886: gang la gnas gzhi rten med pas //
NK102(ne)001:10887: gnas der lus bcos kha na med //
NK102(ne)001:10889: bsam gtan lus dben bcos mi bya //
NK102(ne)001:10890: de la de dben ma bcos pa //
NK102(ne)001:10891: de nyid ye shes dben pa'i gnas //
NK102(ne)001:10894: mtha' yas zhing khams bdag lus phyir //
NK102(ne)001:10895: rnam pa'i lus ngan ma spangs bral //
NK102(ne)001:10896: lus su dben pa'ang dben pa'i phyir //
NK102(ne)001:10897: skyil krung drang por 'dug pa'ang med //
NK102(ne)001:10899: lus bying bzhag thabs bya ba med pas /
NK102(ne)001:10900: byas pa mi 'gog par bzhed do //
NK102(ne)001:10901: 'o na bcos pa'i skyon ji lta bu zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:10902: gang lus 'chos pa la ni da rung lus su 'dzin pa yod de /
NK102(ne)001:10903: 'dzin pas nam du yang don mthong bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:10905: tshad mar lus sems 'chos byed pa //
NK102(ne)001:10906: 'dzin pa'i phur pa de la yod //
NK102(ne)001:10909: zhen pas spyod lam spyod byed pa //
NK102(ne)001:10910: de ni lus spyod bslad pa yin //
NK102(ne)001:10912: der ma zad gnas kyang ched du dgon pa blang du med de /
NK102(ne)001:10913: sngar bstan pa ltar ye dben pa chen po yin pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:10914: 'gro drug rang 'byung gi sangs rgyas la mi dang mjal mod /
NK102(ne)001:10915: sangs rgyas nang zhal ba yin mod /
NK102(ne)001:10916: de bas na ched du dgon pa la chags pa yang spang ngo //
NK102(ne)001:10917: yang bas grong yul du tshig tsam la khungs phyung nas 'dug pa yang min te /
NK102(ne)001:10918: gdengs chud nas spang blangs med pas dgon par gnas so //
NK102(ne)001:10920: ri phug gzhal med bcos mi bya //
NK102(ne)001:10921: de nyid dpag med ma bcos pa'i //
NK102(ne)001:10923: byed pa med par rang 'byung pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:10924: zhes 'byung ba'i don gyis gnas su gang yang bzang ngo //
NK102(ne)001:10925: de lta bas na mi dang phrad kyang /
NK102(ne)001:10928: phrad par bya rgyu yang ma dmigs so //
NK102(ne)001:10929: dus da lta ni grong yul la zhen /
NK102(ne)001:10930: mig tsam gyi lta ba kha la bcangs te /
NK102(ne)001:10931: dgon pa na don chen po spyod pa la 'phya ba mang ste /
NK102(ne)001:10932: de dag ni ltung ba'i rgyu rab tu che'o //
NK102(ne)001:10936: de ni ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid de la /
NK102(ne)001:10938: bdag nyid mi rtog pa chen po'i ngo bor gsal bas /
NK102(ne)001:10939: da 'jug tu med par shes pa nyid zhugs par bzhed do //
NK102(ne)001:10940: skol mdo lo ts+aa ba dpal brtsegs kyi bshad pa las /
NK102(ne)001:10941: a ti yo ga dmigs su med pa'i ye shes kyi stobs kyis 'jug /
NK102(ne)001:10947: mi g.yo ba la mi rtog pa nyid du gnas sam /
NK102(ne)001:10953: bdag nyid mi rtog pa nyid las /
NK102(ne)001:10954: bzod pa mi rtog pa la 'jug mi 'tshal ba'i slad du'o //
NK102(ne)001:10955: gal te bdag ye nas rnam par mi rtog pa ma lags na ni /
NK102(ne)001:10956: rnam par mi rtog pa la bdag 'jug pa zhig na /
NK102(ne)001:10957: thams cad ye nas rnam par mi rtog pa'i slad du'o //
NK102(ne)001:10959: don de dang sbyar na blo gang du yang bsam spyod ma skyes pa nyid du zhugs pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:10963: rtog med rig pa thabs kyis 'jug /
NK102(ne)001:10964: dmigs med nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK102(ne)001:10965: bsam med rim pa thabs kyis 'jug /
NK102(ne)001:10967: de ltar blo 'jog pa'i skyon gsum ste /
NK102(ne)001:10969: de la nges par 'dzin pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK102(ne)001:10970: yid la byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK102(ne)001:10971: yongs su tshol ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK102(ne)001:10973: don ji bzhin pa cir yang bsam du med la /
NK102(ne)001:10974: 'di kho na la'o zhes nges par bzung nas yid la byed pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:10975: des yang dag pa'i don mi mthong ngo //
NK102(ne)001:10976: de yang 'dzin pa'i skyon yin te /
NK102(ne)001:10979: chos nyid yangs pa'i klongs bsam dpyod ngang gis bral
NK102(ne)001:10980: ba la mnyam par 'jog cing sems kyi bzhag sa
NK102(ne)001:10981: tshol te / dper na bung ba khung tshol ba lta bur 'du shes te /
NK102(ne)001:10983: de ltar bzhag na rung ngam snyam pa'i bsam pa tshor rtog can /
NK102(ne)001:10984: de yang bsam pa byed pa'i skyon yin no //
NK102(ne)001:10985: de yang rdo rje bkod pa las /
NK102(ne)001:10986: gzhi'i don la yud tsam zhig /
NK102(ne)001:10988: de la dran pa mang 'phel zhing //
NK102(ne)001:10989: lam tshol ba yi grangs byung na //
NK102(ne)001:10991: chos nyid don du ga la 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:10992: zhes pa'i don gyis 'dir brgyud pa tsam las /
NK102(ne)001:10993: dngos su mthong bar mi nus bar la bcad do //
NK102(ne)001:10994: phra men gyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK102(ne)001:10995: mnyam pa'i klong la rnam rtog ka nas dag pa /
NK102(ne)001:10996: chos nyid bya ba tsam du yang btsal du med
NK102(ne)001:10997: pa la blo gnyis med kyi gnad ma chud pas
NK102(ne)001:10998: / res mtshan ma med pa'i don gsal /
NK102(ne)001:10999: res mtshan ma'i rtog pa rgyu ste /
NK102(ne)001:11000: 'dren mar byung na phra men te /
NK102(ne)001:11001: des gza' gtad med pa'i bsgom pa mi rtogs so //
NK102(ne)001:11002: yang sems nyid bde ba ma mthong na //
NK102(ne)001:11003: yid la mtshan med don gsal dang //
NK102(ne)001:11004: mtshan ma 'khrul bar rgyu ba rgyur ba na sangs rgyas rang gi 'dod kyi /
NK102(ne)001:11008: de yang brgyud pas phebs pa tsam mo //
NK102(ne)001:11009: 'on kyang de dag dang bral bas blo tha snyad
NK102(ne)001:11010: tsam du bzhag pa'i bzhag tu med par shes par
NK102(ne)001:11012: spyir thob par byed pa'i don tha snyad thams cad byang chub kyi lam yin pas /
NK102(ne)001:11013: thabs brtan sgo drug dgag tu med yul snang ba bsam du med pas lhug pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:11015: yongs su mtha' gsum las grol bas yul dang bral ba nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:11016: zhib tu tshig 'di dag la rtogs shing zhar la
NK102(ne)001:11017: bsgom zhing nyams longs rang rig pa nang nas rang
NK102(ne)001:11019: lta ba'i khong gis khrol te /
NK102(ne)001:11020: de la lhag pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK102(ne)001:11021: bsgom pa'ang gong du thag chod pa'i don ji bzhin te /
NK102(ne)001:11022: don dang bsgom pa por rgya ma chad de gcig
NK102(ne)001:11023: pa'i phyir chos nyid ji bzhin pa'i ngo bo yin
NK102(ne)001:11024: pas / blo ji bzhin par ched du ma bzhag par shes pa nyid /
NK102(ne)001:11026: de bzhin du chos nyid lhun gyis grub pas rang
NK102(ne)001:11027: rig pa'ang lhun de gnyis tha dad med pa'i phyir
NK102(ne)001:11029: chos nyid thig le chen po'i ngo bor gsal bas /
NK102(ne)001:11030: rang rig pa'ang thig le chen por bzhag go //
NK102(ne)001:11031: don bya ba rtsol ba dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:11032: rang rig pa bya ba rtsol ba dang bral ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:11033: chos nyid gnyis su med pas /
NK102(ne)001:11034: rig pa gnyis su med pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:11035: chos nyid gza' gtad dang bral bas /
NK102(ne)001:11036: rig pa gza' gtad dang bral ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:11037: chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes pas /
NK102(ne)001:11038: rang rig pa rang byung gi ye shes so //
NK102(ne)001:11039: chos nyid thams cad bdag nyid chen po pas /
NK102(ne)001:11041: chos nyid thams cad cir yang mi bsam pas /
NK102(ne)001:11042: blo cir yang mi bsam mo //
NK102(ne)001:11043: chos nyid cir yang mi g.yo bas /
NK102(ne)001:11045: chos nyid cir yang mi 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:11049: chos nyid cir yang mi snang bas /
NK102(ne)001:11051: chos kyi ngang la mi rtog mi dpyod mi tshol mi len pas /
NK102(ne)001:11052: blo mi rtog mi dpyod mi tshol mi len no //
NK102(ne)001:11053: chos nyid mi skye mi 'gag pas /
NK102(ne)001:11054: rang gi blo gang du'ang mi skye mi gnas mi 'gog go //
NK102(ne)001:11055: chos nyid kyi ngang ched du mi byed /
NK102(ne)001:11056: mi 'chos ma bslad pas rang gi blo yang ched du mi byed mi 'chos mi bslad do //
NK102(ne)001:11057: chos nyid gsal la mi rtog pas /
NK102(ne)001:11058: rang rig pa yang gsal la mi rtog go //
NK102(ne)001:11059: chos nyid mi 'byung mi 'jug 'du shes med pas /
NK102(ne)001:11060: rang rig pa'ang mi 'byung mi 'jug 'du shes med do //
NK102(ne)001:11061: chos nyid mi rtog mi g.yo mi dmigs pa la'ang gnas pa med pas /
NK102(ne)001:11062: rang gi blo yang mi rtog mi g.yo mi dmigs pa la'ang gnas par mi byed do //
NK102(ne)001:11063: chos kyi de kho na nyid ye phyad pa thun mtshams bral bas /
NK102(ne)001:11064: rang rig pa'ang dus gsum phyad pa chen po thun mtshams bral ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:11066: chos nyid ji bzhin pa gang yin pa rang rig pa nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK102(ne)001:11067: lugs chen po la gnas pa cig car yang mi bsam mo //
NK102(ne)001:11069: byang lam pas bsgom pa'i dus na'ang /
NK102(ne)001:11070: chub kyi snying por zhugs pa'i tshe /
NK102(ne)001:11071: stong pa'i chos la stong pa'i yul med de mi gnas so //
NK102(ne)001:11072: zhes 'byung bas yul med pas gsal lo //
NK102(ne)001:11073: 'o na tshe skabs bzhugs pa'i tshe zhes pa /
NK102(ne)001:11075: yul med kyang bzhugs cing mnyam par ma bzhag pa'i tshe /
NK102(ne)001:11076: yul spyod pas thun mtshams kyang yod do zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:11077: de ni don 'byung 'jug med de gdul bya'i ngor bstan pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:11078: 'on tang 'dir ni chu tshod thun brtag pa'i dum bu med de /
NK102(ne)001:11079: ye mnyam pa ji bzhin nyid la su yi gang la bsgoms te bya ba med de /
NK102(ne)001:11080: de ltar thag chod nas dran pas slong ba ci ma 'gags kyang dran pa med do //
NK102(ne)001:11081: man ngag de nyid rgyun gyi man ngag ril btags pa tsam phyir rig par snang ngo //
NK102(ne)001:11083: dran med mi yang 'khor rgyun mi byed de //
NK102(ne)001:11086: de ltar yun ring ma brjed na /
NK102(ne)001:11087: 'jug tshig don mthun pa'i nyams 'byung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:11089: mdor thun kyang skyon du bkag pa'ang med /
NK102(ne)001:11090: blang ba yang med de thun med par shes nas thun du bcad kyang skyon med do //
NK102(ne)001:11091: de ltar bsgom pa'i snying po byang chub de /
NK102(ne)001:11092: gnas pa'i yun nges pa med de /
NK102(ne)001:11093: de yang rnal 'byor grub pa'i lung las /
NK102(ne)001:11107: ye de kho na nyid du pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11109: bskal pa tshad med pas so //
NK102(ne)001:11111: lam pa la snang ba'i rig pa la snang ba'i yun dang /
NK102(ne)001:11112: dus de dag nyid du snying po byang chub rang shar ba gnyis kar sbyor ro //
NK102(ne)001:11113: rnam gcig tu a ts+aar+ya rgyal ba gsal gyis bzhed /
NK102(ne)001:11114: a ti yo ga'i bsgom pa klong phebs pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:11116: ye yin klong chen don rtog ma yengs pa //
NK102(ne)001:11117: byang chub sems chen klong gi bsgom pa yin //
NK102(ne)001:11118: zhes pa'i don dang sbyar na /
NK102(ne)001:11119: gong du lta bas thag chod pas ci yang rig
NK102(ne)001:11120: pa med pas rig pa la sems ched du ma
NK102(ne)001:11121: btang ma shor tsam du dran pas dran rgyu med
NK102(ne)001:11123: de bsgom pa ma nor ba ste /
NK102(ne)001:11124: de yang bya ba med pa'i brtson 'grus kyis yun bsrings na /
NK102(ne)001:11125: phyi mo chos nyid rang mngon du 'a gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:11126: rnam gcig tu dge slong ma kun dga' ma'i bzhed /
NK102(ne)001:11127: lta ba a ti yo ga'i bsgom mnal du phebs pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:11128: 'di ltar bsgom ste khyung chen las //
NK102(ne)001:11129: shin tu myur ba'i bsam pa kun dang bral //
NK102(ne)001:11132: bsam gtan nyid pas bsam du med //
NK102(ne)001:11133: ma bsams ma sbyangs chos bzhin du //
NK102(ne)001:11134: rnam rtog bsam pa nyid las skye //
NK102(ne)001:11135: zhes pa'i don dang sbyar na /
NK102(ne)001:11136: rig pa rang byung gi spyod yul dang bral ba la /
NK102(ne)001:11137: ngag gis bsam du med pas rang rig pa cir yang bsam spyod med /
NK102(ne)001:11138: ye shes kyi klong du brdal ba la 'dzin rtog
NK102(ne)001:11139: med pa nyid ni rig pa nam mkha' dang 'dra
NK102(ne)001:11140: ste / nam mkha' ni ci la yang mi bsam
NK102(ne)001:11141: mi gnas pa'i phyir na blo bzhag pa med par
NK102(ne)001:11142: ste / bzhag pa ste / don de la ci spyod kyang mi nyams par bya'o zhes gsungs so //
NK102(ne)001:11143: yang rnam gcig gsal ba rgyal gyis bzhed cing /
NK102(ne)001:11145: rdzogs pa chen po la gnas pa'i sgom chen pas blo 'di bzhin du bzhag ste /
NK102(ne)001:11147: snang ba rgya mtsho chen po bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:11148: mi rtog nam mkha'i mtha' ltar yangs //
NK102(ne)001:11149: zhes pa'i don dang sbyar na /
NK102(ne)001:11150: rig pa ye shes kyi rgya mtsho chen por rang gsal ba las /
NK102(ne)001:11151: snang ba'i chos gang yang mi 'gog mi gzung /
NK102(ne)001:11153: rgya mtsho dwangs pa la gza' skar gsal la mi 'dzin pa ltar /
NK102(ne)001:11154: rang rig pa cir yang rang shar ba la mi
NK102(ne)001:11155: 'gog mi rtog par blos ma bsam par rang gsal
NK102(ne)001:11157: blo tha dad med par bzhag ces bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:11158: spyod lam rnam bzhir yang don gyi rlung de las ma nyams par sbyar bar bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:11159: yang rnam gcig 'bu ta kug ta'i bzhed /
NK102(ne)001:11162: snang ba med pa'i chos nyid ni //
NK102(ne)001:11163: ma btsal bzhag pas bsgom pa yin //
NK102(ne)001:11165: snying po byang chub ji bzhin rnam pa thams cad
NK102(ne)001:11166: pa'i phyir rnam pa'i snang ba 'di lta bu'o zhes
NK102(ne)001:11167: pa med / pa ni mtha' gang yin gyis ma rig pas /
NK102(ne)001:11168: dus gsum du yul du snang ba myong la /
NK102(ne)001:11169: don de la ngo bo med pas /
NK102(ne)001:11170: de la dmigs gtad gang yang mi bya ste /
NK102(ne)001:11171: gang bcos pa ni bslad pa yin te bya ba
NK102(ne)001:11172: med pas rang bzhin bzhag pa med par gsal na
NK102(ne)001:11173: bzhag pa ste thabs dam pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:11174: rnam gcig 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis bzhed /
NK102(ne)001:11177: rnam pa cir yang mi 'byed ye shes gti mug dang //
NK102(ne)001:11178: thogs med gsal ba'i mar me bsam pa kun dang bral //
NK102(ne)001:11179: ngang gis mi g.yo rmugs shing ting 'dzin rgyal por gnas //
NK102(ne)001:11180: zhes pa'i don dang sbyar na /
NK102(ne)001:11181: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i ye shes ji bzhin pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:11182: phyogs ris thams cad dang bral ba la /
NK102(ne)001:11183: mtha' ma reg par rang gsal bas /
NK102(ne)001:11185: rnam rtog ldang ba'i sa med /
NK102(ne)001:11186: g.yo ba'i yul ma dmigs te /
NK102(ne)001:11187: mi g.yo bar chen por gsal ba med par gsal ba ni nyi ma dang 'dra ste /
NK102(ne)001:11188: nyi ma la de gsal bar bya mi dgos pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:11189: gsal bar ched du mi byed pa dang 'dra ba ni bsgom pa'i mchog ste /
NK102(ne)001:11190: de la blo lhun gyis grub pa'i rjes su 'brang zhing mngon du byed pa med na /
NK102(ne)001:11191: bsgom klong brdal ma nor ba ste /
NK102(ne)001:11192: de la dran pa tsam gyis chog ste /
NK102(ne)001:11193: dran nas yid la bya ba thams cad dang bral te /
NK102(ne)001:11194: skye shi chos dus gsum du med par la bcad do //
NK102(ne)001:11195: rnam gcig bi ma la mi tra'i bzhed /
NK102(ne)001:11198: chos nyid bsam du med pas nam mkha' che //
NK102(ne)001:11199: nam mkha'i bsam pa de dag kun dang bral //
NK102(ne)001:11200: bsam du med pas nam mkha' bsam pa dag /
NK102(ne)001:11201: nam mkhar mi dmigs par yang dmigs su med //
NK102(ne)001:11202: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid kun la rab 'das pa //
NK102(ne)001:11203: med pas nam mkha' la yang nam mkha' med //
NK102(ne)001:11204: nam mkha' de nyid bsgom du med pas ni //
NK102(ne)001:11205: brjod med nam mkha'i bsgom du med las 'das //
NK102(ne)001:11206: zhes gcig dang gnyi ga las byung ba dang sbyar na /
NK102(ne)001:11207: dngos po rnams kyi de kho na nyid kyi nam mkha' ni /
NK102(ne)001:11208: ye lhun gyis brdal bar gsal ba la /
NK102(ne)001:11209: bsgom bya bsgom byed dus gsum du ma dmigs pas /
NK102(ne)001:11210: bsgom pa'i blo nyid dang sgom pa'i nam mkha' la cir yang mi bsam /
NK102(ne)001:11214: mi bsgom pa la mi dmigs shing /
NK102(ne)001:11215: mi sgom bya ba rang tsam du yang /
NK102(ne)001:11216: dmigs pa dang dran bag med par gsal ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:11217: blo chos nyid las ma g.yos pas /
NK102(ne)001:11219: rnam gcig bee ro tsa na'i bzhed /
NK102(ne)001:11221: lhag pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams blo 'di ltar bzhag ste /
NK102(ne)001:11223: bsgom pa'i yul med de la bsgom mi gnas //
NK102(ne)001:11224: bsgom chags bde bar 'dod pa bdag 'dzin sdug bsngal yin //
NK102(ne)001:11225: bsgom pa'i gnas med rab tu dag rtogs na //
NK102(ne)001:11226: bsgoms kyang skyon med chos dbyings nam mkha' 'dra //
NK102(ne)001:11227: zhes pa'i don gyis nyams su blangs na /
NK102(ne)001:11228: bya rtsol dang bral ba'i chos bsgom pa'i yul bral bar thag chod nas /
NK102(ne)001:11230: bya ba thams cad bral ba'i don la /
NK102(ne)001:11231: lus sems khong klod yangs bag tu bzhag la /
NK102(ne)001:11232: bya ba med pa'i brtson 'grus kyis /
NK102(ne)001:11233: khong don dang bral ba med pa /
NK102(ne)001:11234: med par rang gsal ba bsgom mo /
NK102(ne)001:11236: bsgom pas bsgom pa'i rtogs 'dzin med la /
NK102(ne)001:11237: dmigs pa ma dmigs pa'i rtogs 'dzin med pa /
NK102(ne)001:11238: goms par bya ba ma 'gags bya rgyu med de /
NK102(ne)001:11239: de ni thabs mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:11240: rnam dga' rab rdo rje'i bzhed /
NK102(ne)001:11242: bsgom pa'i don ma nor ba'i klong dkyil nas bzhag na 'di ltar bzhag ste /
NK102(ne)001:11245: thams cad mkhyen pa bsgom pa'i mchog /
NK102(ne)001:11246: ngo bo nyid ni dmigs su med //
NK102(ne)001:11247: nga yi lus su sbyor ba la //
NK102(ne)001:11248: byang chub med cing bsgom pa med //
NK102(ne)001:11249: ces pa'i don la gtugs na /
NK102(ne)001:11250: rang byung ye shes mu mtha' med pa'i klong du /
NK102(ne)001:11251: bdag gzhan med par rang gsal la /
NK102(ne)001:11252: g.yo ba med par bsgom pa'i mchog go //
NK102(ne)001:11253: de'i mtshan nyid ci 'dra zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:11254: ye shes chen po'i ngang la thams cad bdag nyid du snums pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:11258: de las nyon mongs pa ngang gis glo bur mi
NK102(ne)001:11259: skye ba'i don de ni rgyal ba'i dgongs pa mngon
NK102(ne)001:11260: du phyung ste snyan khung brgyud pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:11261: yang las dang po'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK102(ne)001:11264: ma skyes pa yi chos rnams la //
NK102(ne)001:11265: ngo bo med de bsgom pa'ang med //
NK102(ne)001:11266: nam mkha'i tshul du rab sbyor bas //
NK102(ne)001:11267: dngos grub kun tu rab tu grags //
NK102(ne)001:11270: rang rig pa las byung ba'i chos rnams la //
NK102(ne)001:11271: gang yang bsam du med pa nyid kyi don du gyur pa'i gnas ni /
NK102(ne)001:11272: byang chub sems rmad du byung ba nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:11273: zhes pa'i don gyis thams cad kyang ngo bo med pas yul dang rig pa gnyis med de /
NK102(ne)001:11274: ma skyes pa ji lta ba rang rig pa rang brdal te /
NK102(ne)001:11275: nam mkha' la nyi ma shar ba ltar gsal la /
NK102(ne)001:11279: ched du bsgom pa yang med /
NK102(ne)001:11280: yengs zhing bral ba yang med na /
NK102(ne)001:11282: de lta bu'i don la gnas na /
NK102(ne)001:11286: rgyal ba nyid dang spyod yul gcig go //
NK102(ne)001:11287: rna brgyud kyi man ngag las /
NK102(ne)001:11288: ji bzhin par snang ba'i dus na /
NK102(ne)001:11292: blo ji ltar yang mi 'jug par /
NK102(ne)001:11293: g.yo ba med na thog tu phebs pa yin pas /
NK102(ne)001:11294: bde ba chen po'i ro'ang dbang med par 'byung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:11296: bsgom lugs de ji ltar bstan kyang gang zag blo mi mthun pas /
NK102(ne)001:11297: skye ba'i mchog dang chos kyi gzhung tsam ste /
NK102(ne)001:11298: don la zab mi zab med de /
NK102(ne)001:11299: de gang ltar bsgoms kyang thog tu phebs par 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:11302: phyi nang gi chos thams cad rang byung gi ye shes su thag chod pa la /
NK102(ne)001:11303: a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po pas /
NK102(ne)001:11304: chos thams cad blo phyi rol du 'phros pa'ang med /
NK102(ne)001:11305: nang du bsu rgyu yang med /
NK102(ne)001:11306: bar du bzhag rgyu yang med par rang gsal ba
NK102(ne)001:11307: lam pa las nyams su dogs pa'am rtogs pa 'phros
NK102(ne)001:11308: su dogs gsal / gzhi bdag rang lugs /
NK102(ne)001:11312: blo cir yang 'di la tshul gnyis kyi mi reg ste phyogs mthun pas mi reg pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11313: mthun par mi reg pa dang mi mthun pas mi reg pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:11314: phyogs mthun pas mi reg pa'ang tshogs drug 'gags te
NK102(ne)001:11315: zhi bas mi reg 'du shes kyi mi reg btang
NK102(ne)001:11316: snyoms kyi mi reg 'gags snang mi reg /
NK102(ne)001:11318: mi mthun pas mi reg pa ni yid la byed pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11320: tshor ba dang 'du shes kyi bzung ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:11321: nyams su myong bas ma yin no //
NK102(ne)001:11322: mi 'jug mi bsgom ma yengs ba la tshogs drug
NK102(ne)001:11323: rtog pa ma bkag pa la mthong thos med pa
NK102(ne)001:11327: ye shes chen po'i klong du bsam dpyod med par rang gsal lo //
NK102(ne)001:11328: de lta bu theg pa chen po 'di'i ting nge 'dzin yang mang ste /
NK102(ne)001:11329: bla ma'i gong na med pas /
NK102(ne)001:11331: rang dbang cir yang snang ba mi 'gog pas /
NK102(ne)001:11333: bdag ril bdag tu rdzogs pas /
NK102(ne)001:11334: nyid chen po'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK102(ne)001:11335: zil gyis gnon pa'i don gyi khong 'og tu chud pas /
NK102(ne)001:11337: mi g.yo srid gsum dkrugs kyang mi g.yo /
NK102(ne)001:11339: snang gsal rang rig ye shes nyi ma shar nub med pa nyi ma stong gis mi snyeg /
NK102(ne)001:11342: gti mug gang la'ang ris su 'byed pa med mi 'byed pa'i ting nge /
NK102(ne)001:11344: 'joms pa bya rtsol 'khor ba ka dag pas /
NK102(ne)001:11345: chen po'i ting nge 'dzin dang brgyad kyis gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:11346: yin na ni de kho na ltar yin na /
NK102(ne)001:11347: las dang po pa ni mtshan ma la mi dga'/
NK102(ne)001:11348: mtshan ma med pa la dga' 'o //
NK102(ne)001:11353: bsam pa med par zer zhing bsam pa byed /
NK102(ne)001:11354: spyod yul bral bar zer zhing mngon du byed pas don mi mthong ste /
NK102(ne)001:11356: dper na me dang du ba 'dra ste /
NK102(ne)001:11360: ma g.yos na mi ldang ngo //
NK102(ne)001:11363: char chad na na bun ldang ste /
NK102(ne)001:11364: de ltar las dang po pa'i sems cung zad don
NK102(ne)001:11365: gsal bar byed pa'i bar du rtog pa mi rgyu
NK102(ne)001:11366: yang / btang tsam na ldang ngo //
NK102(ne)001:11368: ji bzhin pa zhes rnam rtog de phyir rtag sgom pa //
NK102(ne)001:11369: bde ba chen po 'dod pas chags pa'i nad yin te //
NK102(ne)001:11371: yongs mnyam pa'i don gyi gdengs ma rnyed na /
NK102(ne)001:11372: blo bzhag pas cung zhig kyang mi g.yo yang /
NK102(ne)001:11373: thag ma chod pa'i rgyus rtog pa phyis snang ste /
NK102(ne)001:11374: nya lcibs can gyi chu la bcus na skyogs bcug pas /
NK102(ne)001:11375: nya lcibs tha mar gyes kyang /
NK102(ne)001:11376: phyung ma thag tu slar 'dus te /
NK102(ne)001:11378: des na chos nyid kyi rjes su 'brang zhing /
NK102(ne)001:11379: 'dod pa yod na ni skyon gyi rgyu kho na ste /
NK102(ne)001:11381: yon tan mnyam du mthong las byung //
NK102(ne)001:11384: bdud ni gang las byung zhe na //
NK102(ne)001:11385: rtag tu grub pas byung ba yin //
NK102(ne)001:11386: ci phyir mi 'grub de bzhin bdud //
NK102(ne)001:11388: de bas na skal pa dang ldan pa'i mi rnams kyis cha chugs 'di lta bu spyod na /
NK102(ne)001:11389: blo ci la'ang brtag bya rtogs byed bral bas /
NK102(ne)001:11390: mi brtag mi rnam pa'i yul du med pas /
NK102(ne)001:11392: yid la bya ba rang rig rang gsal bas /
NK102(ne)001:11394: don du chos nyid kho na rang sems pas /
NK102(ne)001:11396: mngon du ye nyid nas rang rig mngon sum rang gsal bas /
NK102(ne)001:11397: mi byed gsal bar ye gsal bas 'phral du /
NK102(ne)001:11399: chos nyid ched du dngos po bor nas /
NK102(ne)001:11403: de dag tu yang mi gang gi don de nyid la'ang zhes pas /
NK102(ne)001:11407: mi len logs nas chos nyid gcig gang gis mi g.yo ba ma yengs pa'i ngo bo bas /
NK102(ne)001:11409: de lta bas na rtsol ba'i blo zhugs na rtsol ba med pas gol /
NK102(ne)001:11411: bsam dpyod byas na rtogs pa skye /
NK102(ne)001:11413: mtshan ma'i rjes bcad na 'dzin pa'i gzungs su 'gyur /
NK102(ne)001:11415: blo don gyi rjes su 'brangs na yul can du song /
NK102(ne)001:11417: rig pa nang nas ma shar na gnyis 'dzin gyi dbang gi /
NK102(ne)001:11422: spyod kyi rang bcing pa khu 'phrig 'byung /
NK102(ne)001:11424: bsgom pa mig btsum ma thag rtogs pa sngangs /
NK102(ne)001:11425: yang rtog pa'i rlung 'tshub kyis rlung du 'gro bar rbad kyis bcad do //
NK102(ne)001:11427: dus phyi pa'i gang zag dmigs pa'i man ngag can /
NK102(ne)001:11428: nga la rgya gar gyi man ngag yod pas /
NK102(ne)001:11429: zhag dang zla bas sangs rgyas te /
NK102(ne)001:11430: khyod kyi 'di lta bu yug pa rkyang gtad med do zhes smra ba'i 'chal pa dag 'byung ste /
NK102(ne)001:11431: de ni don chen po rang la ma shar bar mngon te /
NK102(ne)001:11432: khams sa'i mi mo mi shes par 'jim pa'i sku lugs ma brtsoms pa dang 'dra ste /
NK102(ne)001:11433: dmigs pa'i thabs sna res don chen po gtan la 'bebs pa ni de dang 'dra'o //
NK102(ne)001:11434: ci dmigs pas sangs rgyas pa nyid bsti gnas kyi
NK102(ne)001:11435: sangs rgyas pa yin gyi yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK102(ne)001:11437: de tang khyod la sangs rgyas pa'i thabs yod na /
NK102(ne)001:11438: kho bo 'di la sangs rgyas yang mi dgos te de nyid kyis gsal lo //
NK102(ne)001:11439: de ltar rnal 'byor chen po las kyang khyad par du gyur pa'i theg pa las /
NK102(ne)001:11440: sde rgyud yang rtog bla na med pa'i don gong
NK102(ne)001:11441: nas bshad pa bzhin dran pas chog /'da' ka'i man
NK102(ne)001:11442: ngag ma nor ba yang de nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:11444: 'da' ba nyid ma 'gags la ma dmigs pas /
NK102(ne)001:11445: mtshan ma'i las gang gi yang dbang du mi 'gyur te /
NK102(ne)001:11447: ma skyes rmad byung byang chub la //
NK102(ne)001:11448: nyon mongs las kyi gos mi 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:11451: khyad par cir yang mtshungs pa la //
NK102(ne)001:11452: las so zhes ni rnam par brtags //
NK102(ne)001:11453: ci ste las kyi dbang gyur na //
NK102(ne)001:11454: rang byung ye shes yod ma yin //
NK102(ne)001:11456: dge ba'i phyogs dang sdig las sogs //
NK102(ne)001:11457: tha snyad tsam yang yod ma yin //
NK102(ne)001:11459: 'da' ka'i man ngag gi yang de nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:11460: rnam gcig 'da' ka'i ting nge 'dzin 'di la gnas par bya ste /
NK102(ne)001:11461: a tsa ra rnam gsum brgyud pa'i man ngag go //
NK102(ne)001:11462: de yang man ngag bde klong las /
NK102(ne)001:11463: man ngag gsang chen 'da' ka ma //
NK102(ne)001:11464: ma bcos thig le zlum po la //
NK102(ne)001:11465: gsang ba'i mdzod gsum dbus su dgab //
NK102(ne)001:11466: sems kyi srog btsug gdengs su gyur //
NK102(ne)001:11467: rtse mo rnam gsum dbyings na yan //
NK102(ne)001:11468: gting dpag med pas khong yangs te //
NK102(ne)001:11469: rnam dag rin chen gter lta bu //
NK102(ne)001:11470: bo de tsit+ta'i gzhal yas su //
NK102(ne)001:11471: 'chi ba med pa'i srog btsugs shing //
NK102(ne)001:11472: gol sa med pa'i lam ston te //
NK102(ne)001:11473: tshon gang rin chen gzhal yas su //
NK102(ne)001:11474: 'degs med dbugs kyi rta pho la //
NK102(ne)001:11475: 'bras bu srog gi rgyal po zhon //
NK102(ne)001:11476: a dang ya yis spar byas te //
NK102(ne)001:11478: re dogs med pa'i klong 'byams su //
NK102(ne)001:11479: skye shi med pas dang re spro //
NK102(ne)001:11480: gser zhu zhi gar blugs pas gzugs su gsal ba bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:11481: snang srid sems su gsal na bdag nyid che //
NK102(ne)001:11482: bsgom dang mi bsgom gnyis ni tshig gi lam //
NK102(ne)001:11483: klong du gyur na bsgom pa'i rgyal po yin //
NK102(ne)001:11485: de'i don ser sna spangs pa'i sems kyis /
NK102(ne)001:11486: lus srog yan chad phul la /
NK102(ne)001:11487: bla ma'i zhal byang du zhu'o //
NK102(ne)001:11488: de ltar don la gnas shing bsgom pa'i tshe /
NK102(ne)001:11489: nam mkha' yod pas sprin 'byung ba'am /
NK102(ne)001:11490: chu dang rnyog ma ltar bsam pa'i skyon dag byung yang /
NK102(ne)001:11491: de la ched du sgo gsum bcos su med pa /
NK102(ne)001:11492: de la skyon ni rnal 'byor chen po dang /
NK102(ne)001:11494: bcos lugs la khyad par yod do //
NK102(ne)001:11495: de bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i skyon ni /
NK102(ne)001:11496: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa gting zug rgyu 'phral gyi rkyen med par shugs kyis 'byung ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:11497: rkyen las byung ba'i skyon ni /
NK102(ne)001:11498: sgras rkyen pa'i brag cha dang 'dra ste /
NK102(ne)001:11499: 'phral la yul glo bur ba slong ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:11500: ched du byas pa'i skyon ni /
NK102(ne)001:11501: 'phral la sgo gsum bcos pa'i skyon rnams so //
NK102(ne)001:11502: nyams su myong ba'i skyon ni /
NK102(ne)001:11503: don yul du byas pa snyam pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:11504: shugs kyi snang ba'i skyon ni /
NK102(ne)001:11505: me long skar mas brgyan pa lta bu mthong bas dga' ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:11507: bdag po gzhir bzhag byas nas bsgom pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:11508: skyon de dag dus gcig tu mi ldang ste /
NK102(ne)001:11510: de yang dang por dgos brtson 'grus rtsol la /
NK102(ne)001:11511: btang snyoms yin pas rtsol na skyon ngos bzung /
NK102(ne)001:11513: btang snyoms yin pa la bsgribs na skyon yin /
NK102(ne)001:11515: 'jug gi dgos pa thog mar sgrib pa'ang 'byung bas ngo shes par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:11516: de la skyon spyi ston mun rtson men yan chad dang /
NK102(ne)001:11517: a ti a nu yo ga man chad dang ma
NK102(ne)001:11518: h+aa yo ga yan chad skyon ji lta bu ba
NK102(ne)001:11520: dgos skyon ni spyi mthun ma mthong zhing ltung ba mang bas khyad par skyon no //
NK102(ne)001:11521: de la bar 'ga' ni skyon 'di lta bu 'byung ste /
NK102(ne)001:11522: don la 'jug par 'dod pa ni 'jug tu med pa'i skyon no //
NK102(ne)001:11523: don ched du gsal bar 'dod pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:11524: 'di kho na ltar bzhag snyam ste /
NK102(ne)001:11525: snyam pa tsam gyi skyon ni /
NK102(ne)001:11528: nyams kyi myong bar byed pa dag 'byung ste /
NK102(ne)001:11529: mdor de dag bslad pa'i skyon zhes bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:11530: dper na mar me rlung gis bskyod pa dang 'dra ste /
NK102(ne)001:11531: bya ba med pa'i rlung las nyams so //
NK102(ne)001:11532: 'on tang de dag ji ltar thag chod pa'i don
NK102(ne)001:11533: skad cig dran pas de dag byas pa med par
NK102(ne)001:11534: rang shar ro // la la dag lta ba'i gdeng
NK102(ne)001:11535: du chud pa blo bzhag tu med par thag chod
NK102(ne)001:11536: rang shar ro // kyang / mi bsgom na 'gal /
NK102(ne)001:11537: pa'i bsgom par mi gtub pas 'gal zer na /
NK102(ne)001:11538: par mtshan ma mang po dang /
NK102(ne)001:11539: lhag mthong gi rgyu shes rab bsam pa'i /
NK102(ne)001:11540: dran pa mang po dbang med du rgyu ba 'ong na /
NK102(ne)001:11541: lnga par theg pa chen po thos bsam byas kyang /
NK102(ne)001:11542: ma bsgom pas mi g.yo ba'i shas chung ba ste /
NK102(ne)001:11543: de la khong lhod bag tsam brdal te /
NK102(ne)001:11544: don la bya ba med pas khong du ma bsgrims bya ba med pa'i brtson 'grus /
NK102(ne)001:11545: pa'i grims par byas te bzhag dang rang bzhin gyis brtan te /
NK102(ne)001:11546: bsam pa gang du yang mi bsam mi dgag /
NK102(ne)001:11547: so gzud du ji bzhin pa'i ngang las /
NK102(ne)001:11549: pa de so thub 'di nyid kyi 'du shes kyang /
NK102(ne)001:11551: de la ni brtan par byed pa'i thabs blo chung zhen na /
NK102(ne)001:11553: thams cad kyang 'di nyid kyi thabs yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK102(ne)001:11554: gzhan yang ting nge 'dzin gyi bdud drug la /
NK102(ne)001:11555: le lo che zhing bya ba mang pos bar du gcod pa'i bdud dang /
NK102(ne)001:11556: me mar rlung gis bskyod pa ltar sems g.yengs rgod kyi bar du gcod pa'i bdud dang /
NK102(ne)001:11557: rtsol bsgrub chung zhing le lo /
NK102(ne)001:11558: gnyid che ba'i bar du gcod pa'i bdud dang /
NK102(ne)001:11559: rmugs shing 'dod pa che bas bar du gcod pa'i bdud dang /
NK102(ne)001:11560: bsam pa'i rjes su 'brangs pas bar du gcod pa dang drug bdud gcig /
NK102(ne)001:11563: shes rab mi gsal rmugs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11564: gsal ba rgod 'phyar gyi sgrib pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11565: 'thim pa skyes bu mun khung du chud pa 'dra ba'i sgrib pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11566: bsam gtan gyi bde ba'i ro la chags pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11567: ye shes la shes pa skyes pa gzung 'dzin gyi sgrib pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11568: mngon par shes pa dang ldan du rung ba'i sgrib pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11569: rdzu 'phrul 'byin par 'dod pa'i 'dod sems ma bral ba'i sgrib pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11570: bdag gi lta ba bsnyems pas shes pa la ngar brtag pa'i sgrib pa dang sgrib pa gnyis /
NK102(ne)001:11572: bsam gtan gyi skyon drug la /
NK102(ne)001:11573: glo bur du 'dod chags chen po ldang ba sred len gyi skyon dang /
NK102(ne)001:11574: zhe sdang chen po 'byung ba mnar sems kyi skyon dang /
NK102(ne)001:11575: phrag dog chen po byung bas gnod sems kyi skyon dang /
NK102(ne)001:11576: nga rgyal chen po khengs sems kyi skyon dang /
NK102(ne)001:11577: gti mug chen po rmongs sems kyi skyon dang /
NK102(ne)001:11578: rang gi lta ba 'dzin pa snyems pa ngar 'dzin pa'i skyon dang drug go //
NK102(ne)001:11580: med pa da ltar gyi chos 'di glo bur du
NK102(ne)001:11581: skyes pa 'ba' zhig yod de tshe phyi ma man
NK102(ne)001:11583: rnam par smin pa yang med /
NK102(ne)001:11586: mur thug pa'i gol ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:11587: mu stegs chad par lta ba ste /
NK102(ne)001:11588: de ni byang chub sems bde ba chen po'i ngang
NK102(ne)001:11589: la so sor rang gis rig pa'i lta ba mi
NK102(ne)001:11590: gsal ba med cing rig pa'i ye shes la gsal
NK102(ne)001:11591: bas / med pa mur thug pa'i gol sa bsal /
NK102(ne)001:11592: phyal ba g.yeng ba'i gol ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:11593: don gang yang ma shes pas gtad med pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:11594: 'di ni 'jig rten bral ba'i byang chub sems te /
NK102(ne)001:11595: yod med dang mtshan ma la rjes su mi 'brang bas /
NK102(ne)001:11596: phyal ba g.yeng ba'i gol ba bsal /
NK102(ne)001:11597: gcig pu don mi gsal ba'i gol ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:11598: rtag par lta ba'i bdag tu snang la mi rtog par 'dod pas /
NK102(ne)001:11599: yang dag pa'i don mi gsal ba ste /
NK102(ne)001:11600: de ni byang chub bde ba chen po rig par rang dbang du gyur nas /
NK102(ne)001:11601: ye shes kyi snang ba chen po rang las shar ba gang yang zin chags med par gsal lo //
NK102(ne)001:11602: de ni rtse mo byung rgyal las /
NK102(ne)001:11603: rtag chad gnyi gar gang gi blo zhen pa //
NK102(ne)001:11604: don gyi snying po bzhed las gol bar gsungs //
NK102(ne)001:11607: drin byung mtshan ma'i rjes su 'brengs na /
NK102(ne)001:11609: de yang rang rig pa ci yang ma yin pa la /
NK102(ne)001:11610: dran rtogs byar med par rtogs pas gsal te /
NK102(ne)001:11611: dran byung ci yang med par blun na 'du shes
NK102(ne)001:11612: med pa'i gol ba ste de ni ye shes chen
NK102(ne)001:11613: po phyogs med par rang gsal bar rtogs pas gsal
NK102(ne)001:11614: lo // bsam gtan bzhi'i gol sa ni /
NK102(ne)001:11618: mos pa chung du thams cad ni //
NK102(ne)001:11619: gang la bdag med rten gzhi mthong //
NK102(ne)001:11620: gar 'dod pa dang sdig pa tshogs drug /
NK102(ne)001:11625: bsam gtan dang po kho na'o //
NK102(ne)001:11626: kun stong 'phro ba'i stong pa la //
NK102(ne)001:11628: rtog med la spyod pa yod pa /
NK102(ne)001:11634: dga' ba med pa gsum pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:11635: bdag gam gzhan gyi mthus bsten te //
NK102(ne)001:11636: skyon med la blo btang snyoms su 'dod /
NK102(ne)001:11639: 'dir rig pa spyod yul med de /
NK102(ne)001:11640: bya rtsol dang bral ba la /
NK102(ne)001:11641: rtog dpyod byar yang med la /
NK102(ne)001:11642: ro la chags pa'i dga' ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:11643: btang snyoms 'dzin pa med pa nyid kyis dag go //
NK102(ne)001:11644: gzhan yang rnam par rtog pa'i byung tshor 'gegs shing /
NK102(ne)001:11645: zhi bar byed na nyan thos su gol te /
NK102(ne)001:11647: mthong thos med pa nyid rang bzhin no //
NK102(ne)001:11649: drug gi spyod yul mtshan ma ste //
NK102(ne)001:11650: mtshan ma dngos por snang bas na //
NK102(ne)001:11651: ci dgar bzhag pas de bzlog med //
NK102(ne)001:11654: drug gi mtshan ma ci skyes kyang //
NK102(ne)001:11655: ma bcos rang byung de bzhin nyid //
NK102(ne)001:11656: ma skyes bas na bzlog tu med //
NK102(ne)001:11657: rang byung rang zhi ci dgar bzhag /
NK102(ne)001:11659: rtogs pa 'gag nas zhi ba'i ro la chags na /
NK102(ne)001:11660: mya ngan las 'das pa'i mtha' zhi ba phyogs gcig pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:11661: rang rgyal ba'i gol sa yin no //
NK102(ne)001:11663: mngon sum thob par 'dod pas rgyu la rtag tu bsgom //
NK102(ne)001:11664: bsgom chags bde ba de las nyams pa'i don mi 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:11667: ting 'dzin bde ba'i ro la chags //
NK102(ne)001:11668: gnas pa g.yo med rgyu la mi gnas chos nyid yin //
NK102(ne)001:11669: de bas chags pa'i gnas la ting 'dzin ni //
NK102(ne)001:11670: zhi ba'i sa de mya ngan de mi 'da' //
NK102(ne)001:11672: der 'di gnyis su med pa'i ngang la gang gis
NK102(ne)001:11673: gang la chags te ro myong bar mi byed de
NK102(ne)001:11674: / des na mi rtog pa'i lung las /
NK102(ne)001:11675: ji srid yid kyi blo g.yos na //
NK102(ne)001:11676: bag chags rgyu ba rtsing zhib las //
NK102(ne)001:11677: gal te mtshan mar de rtog na //
NK102(ne)001:11678: de srid bdud kyi spyod yul yin //
NK102(ne)001:11679: bag chags rgyu ba rtsing zhib rnams //
NK102(ne)001:11680: sems kyi rgyu 'grul ma yin pa //
NK102(ne)001:11681: logs nas grub pa ci yang med //
NK102(ne)001:11682: dmigs med shes rab dran shar bas //
NK102(ne)001:11683: bsam med dbyings la rab gzhol zhing //
NK102(ne)001:11684: byung tshor rjes su ma 'brangs la //
NK102(ne)001:11685: bying rmugs dbang du ma btang zhing //
NK102(ne)001:11686: ting 'dzin ro la ma chags na //
NK102(ne)001:11687: mi rtog pa la mi rtog bsgom //
NK102(ne)001:11688: rtag chad mu bzhi gtan med pas //
NK102(ne)001:11689: mu stegs lta bar de mi ltung //
NK102(ne)001:11690: gsang ba'i ye shes mngon shar bas //
NK102(ne)001:11691: 'gog pa'i lta bar de mi ltung //
NK102(ne)001:11692: snying po'i don la rab gnas shing //
NK102(ne)001:11693: gcig dang gnyis su mi 'brang bas //
NK102(ne)001:11694: rang rgyal lta bar de mi ltung //
NK102(ne)001:11695: snying po'i don la sgrib med ye shes gsal //
NK102(ne)001:11696: bying rmugs dbang du de mi 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:11698: dngos po ye nas bde ba chen po'i ngang la 'khrul pa snang bar 'dod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11699: gnyis med kyi ye shes la dag pa 'jig rten pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11700: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes skad cig mar lta ba sems tsam du gol ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:11702: chos las 'khrul bar mthong ba de nyid 'khrul pa yin par rab rtogs te //
NK102(ne)001:11705: mngon sum pa dang rgyab nas byung //
NK102(ne)001:11706: de yang snang ba'i skyon yin te //
NK102(ne)001:11708: 'dir stong gsum bde chen du rgyas btab pa la /
NK102(ne)001:11709: spyod yul med pas 'khrul pa snang ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:11711: skad cig ma med pas bsal te /
NK102(ne)001:11713: chos dbyings rdo rje rtse mo de dag phyogs nyid med pas skad cig min //
NK102(ne)001:11714: dag pa'i dge rtsa gzugs brnyan med pas 'jig rten ye shes yod ma yin //
NK102(ne)001:11716: ye nas mu mtha' med pa'i don la kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du lta la /
NK102(ne)001:11717: don dam par ma skyes pa lta na /
NK102(ne)001:11720: mtshan nyid med pa'i chos nyid chen po 'di //
NK102(ne)001:11721: chos kyi dbyings la sgyu mar gar bsgyur yang //
NK102(ne)001:11722: sgyu ma'i lam du rgyal bas ma basngagasa so //
NK102(ne)001:11724: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyi stong pa lus ngag
NK102(ne)001:11725: yid gsum skyon ci yang stong pa nyid yin pas
NK102(ne)001:11726: lus stong zhing dben pa ngag dang yid kyang stong
NK102(ne)001:11727: zhing dben pas / dgon pa gsum la gnas so //
NK102(ne)001:11728: des grub par lta na ston mun du gol ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:11730: 'phra ba'i sgo mor ming btags pas /
NK102(ne)001:11731: sems kyi dben pas lam tshol zhing //
NK102(ne)001:11732: dgon pa'i rgyud du dben 'dzin pa //
NK102(ne)001:11738: 'dir yang ye shes chen po'i ngang la rnam rtog stong par byar med pa nyid kyis dag go /
NK102(ne)001:11740: bya bral yul la mi gnas gnyen pos bcos su med //
NK102(ne)001:11742: a tsa ra rnam gsum gyi man ngag las /
NK102(ne)001:11744: nam mkha' bzhin khong ched du klod pa med /
NK102(ne)001:11745: klod pas go 'byed pa ltar na /
NK102(ne)001:11746: rang bzhin med pas thams cad byang chub sems su 'dus te /
NK102(ne)001:11747: chos nyid la go 'byed pa med de /
NK102(ne)001:11750: 'dir ji bzhin pa de kho na nyid kyi klong la ngo bor bzung du med bzhin du /
NK102(ne)001:11751: byang chub sems rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i gol ba /
NK102(ne)001:11752: dpa'i 'od dang thig le'i rang bzhin rtag pa can
NK102(ne)001:11753: du bzung nas bsgom pas lus 'dar bde ba skye
NK102(ne)001:11754: bar 'dod na / ba la sogs pa byung na /
NK102(ne)001:11757: 'di la brtul zhugs drag shul gyis //
NK102(ne)001:11758: gnas su bya ba'i ming med de //
NK102(ne)001:11759: a dang par ni rnam ldan na //
NK102(ne)001:11760: rgyu ba'i bde ba bskyed par 'dod //
NK102(ne)001:11761: de yang 'dzin pa'i skyon yin te //
NK102(ne)001:11763: gnyis med bde chen byang chub las //
NK102(ne)001:11764: snying dkrugs ma yin 'dar ba min //
NK102(ne)001:11765: blang dang dor bstod gsib pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:11766: rdul byung ba spu 'greng pa min //
NK102(ne)001:11768: rnam gcig bskyed pas rim pas gol ba /
NK102(ne)001:11770: phung po khams skye mched lhar bsgoms te kun btags log zhes /
NK102(ne)001:11771: rtog pa dang po byung nas /
NK102(ne)001:11773: de la yang mi gnas par byed pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:11774: sngags kyi mtshan mar gol ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:11775: de yang nam mkha' che las /
NK102(ne)001:11776: srid pa gsum na sbyor ba yang //
NK102(ne)001:11777: ming tsam sgyu mar snang ba ste //
NK102(ne)001:11778: 'khor lo bsgyur ba'i gnas chen yang //
NK102(ne)001:11779: sgyu mas sbyor ba'i bsti gnas yin //
NK102(ne)001:11782: 'ja' tshon sgyu ma 'phags pa'i sku brgyud kyang //
NK102(ne)001:11783: bsod nams bskyed kyang sgyu mar mi rtog na //
NK102(ne)001:11784: rnam dag lam chen lhun gyis grub pa la //
NK102(ne)001:11785: bsod nams med kyang grub ces rgyal bas gsungs //
NK102(ne)001:11787: ma h+aa yo ga'i bsod nams mi rten pas gsal to //
NK102(ne)001:11788: sngags kyi de bzhin nyid du gol ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:11789: ma h+aa yo ga pa ni chos thams cad rang
NK102(ne)001:11790: rig pa'i ye shes dus gsum mnyam pa chen po
NK102(ne)001:11791: / de bzhin nyid la blo 'jug pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11792: bsgom pa dang ldan pa yod na bdag nyid chen po bya ba med par ma shes so //
NK102(ne)001:11794: byar med pa de la chags pa dang ma bral na /
NK102(ne)001:11795: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid kyang 'byung 'jug go //
NK102(ne)001:11797: der gsal ba ni 'dir rang byung chen po nyid du bsam pa dang bral bas /
NK102(ne)001:11798: 'byung 'jug med de phyad pa chen po'o //
NK102(ne)001:11800: rang byung ye shes dbang la ma rten pas //
NK102(ne)001:11801: re zhing dogs pa'i mtha' kun rnam par zhi //
NK102(ne)001:11803: a nu yo gar gol ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:11804: ma h+aa yo ga ni ci yang ched du byed /
NK102(ne)001:11805: de las khyad par 'phags par gsal ba'i a nu yo ga yang /
NK102(ne)001:11807: ched du bya ba med pa skad zer yang /
NK102(ne)001:11810: kha dog grangs kyi rtsol ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:11813: mi dmigs pa'i ngang skad cig mas lha grangs med
NK102(ne)001:11814: du bskyed cing don byed pa nyid la mthong ste
NK102(ne)001:11815: gol lo // 'dir bsgom lugs la sogs pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11816: 'byed pa ci yang med pa lta ba'i skabs su bstan pa nyid kyis dag go //
NK102(ne)001:11818: yang rnam gcig tu gol sa gsum ste /
NK102(ne)001:11819: yal bar 'jog pa dang don med pa'i phyal ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:11822: gang 'dir nyams pa'i log sred can //
NK102(ne)001:11823: yal ba phyal ba dmigs pa gcig /
NK102(ne)001:11824: gang 'dir lta bas mdongs pa dag /
NK102(ne)001:11825: bdag la brten nas mtha' bsgrubs te //
NK102(ne)001:11826: med myos des 'gro med snyam nas //
NK102(ne)001:11829: de dag mu stegs su gol ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:11830: yang bsam gtan gyi skyon bcu bar gcod do /
NK102(ne)001:11832: le lo che 'di dag rang re'i don gyis dag ste /
NK102(ne)001:11834: bya ba mang yengs ma yengs med pa /
NK102(ne)001:11837: blo ma h+aa dang a nu'i don man chad yid
NK102(ne)001:11838: la byed cing a ti'i don mi gsal na'ang yid
NK102(ne)001:11840: g.yeng ba drug gi dbang du song ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:11842: lta ba ting nge 'dzin gsal bar 'dod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11845: gol lam lhung g.yeng med par shes pas /
NK102(ne)001:11847: the tshom za nges pa'i gdengs kyis /
NK102(ne)001:11849: sems nang du nang du 'dzin pa med pas dag /'du bar byed pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11850: yul la phyir 'phro phyi rol gyi 'du shes kyi bral bas dag /
NK102(ne)001:11851: chos spyod kyi bya ba mang po spyod 'dod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11852: sems can don las 'byung bar 'dod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11854: de yang mnyam par thag chod pas bya bsam med pa nyid kyis mi ldang ngo //
NK102(ne)001:11857: le lo bya mang rgod pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:11858: g.yeng dang rmugs pa 'dod pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:11859: gnyid dang re dogs the tshom dang //
NK102(ne)001:11861: de yang rang bzhin de bzhin nyid //
NK102(ne)001:11865: sems mi g.yo ngang gis mi g.yo ba la /
NK102(ne)001:11867: don gcig bdag nyid las rtsad nas gsal bar byar med pa /
NK102(ne)001:11869: sems bde gnyis med nyams su myongs su med pa la /
NK102(ne)001:11871: las su mi rung ye gsal bar grub zin zhing /
NK102(ne)001:11872: gis dogs pa'i sdug bsngal dang /
NK102(ne)001:11875: mngon shes gsal bar rang rig las 'dres ye rdzogs par gsal bzhin /
NK102(ne)001:11877: rdzu 'phrul 'byin par che ba dbyung du med par /
NK102(ne)001:11879: 'di las med do zhes chos nyid ngo bo med pa /
NK102(ne)001:11880: nges par 'dzin pa chog par sems pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11882: gyi lta ba khyad du gsod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11883: rang gi lta bar bdag 'dzin bral zhing /
NK102(ne)001:11886: sems yul las 'byung ba sgom pa las blo 'byung /
NK102(ne)001:11888: rnam rtog zhi bar ngang gi bral ba bzhin /
NK102(ne)001:11890: tha ma gnyis ni bcos pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:11892: 'on tang skyon bcur nges te sngar bshad do //
NK102(ne)001:11894: rtse mo gzhan la bstan mi dgos gzhan gyi lta ba khyad du gsod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:11895: rang gi lta ba'o snyams pa'i yid ches par byed
NK102(ne)001:11896: pa'i gtan tshigs spyir yang nas yang 'dir man ngag
NK102(ne)001:11897: nyid las drangs pas yid pas ches pa'i rgyur che'o
NK102(ne)001:11899: gsang sngags dbang phyug go 'phang chen po 'dir //
NK102(ne)001:11900: phyi nang gsang ba'i don dang gti mug dbang gis bag zon ma chags pas //
NK102(ne)001:11901: dran drod yas bzhag btsan thabs dregs pa yis //
NK102(ne)001:11902: bdag las gzhan med dpe zla 'phags 'dod pa //
NK102(ne)001:11903: gzhan la brnyas 'dod bdag nyid lhar bsgoms kyang //
NK102(ne)001:11904: mnyam pa'i rgyal po'i don las 'gal ba'i phyir //
NK102(ne)001:11905: lta spyod ya cha bdud kyi las su 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:11908: rang gi shes pa dam par byed //
NK102(ne)001:11909: de kun las rgyal de bsnyems nas //
NK102(ne)001:11910: 'dod chags zhe sdang skyes nas rtsod 'byung gti mug yin te don mi mthong //
NK102(ne)001:11912: de dag gang spyi'i gtan tshigs /
NK102(ne)001:11914: dam pa'i don la gang sgrib pa //
NK102(ne)001:11915: mi g.yo gsal bde sdug bsngal dang //
NK102(ne)001:11916: skye ba gsal bar 'byin pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:11917: nges dang khyad snyems rang sma ga /'gyu rang /
NK102(ne)001:11920: de dag la sogs pa bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor chen po'i skabs su bshad pa dag skyes na /
NK102(ne)001:11921: de nyid rang lugs bcos su med pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:11923: rgyu ba bzhin du sems med na //
NK102(ne)001:11924: mi gnas mi dmigs byed pa gang //
NK102(ne)001:11925: nam mkha' rang las mi gnas par ched du byed pa /
NK102(ne)001:11927: bsgom pa don dang ldan pa min //
NK102(ne)001:11930: ldang dang mi ldang ched du mi spongs sems rten mi 'cha' mngon du min //
NK102(ne)001:11931: 'jam dpal ma yin rdul tsam g.yo ba de nyid de yin der mi gnas //
NK102(ne)001:11934: thams cad sems kyi chos nyid du //
NK102(ne)001:11935: tshig med lta bas thag chod na //
NK102(ne)001:11936: ma bcos ma yengs yeng thub phyir /
NK102(ne)001:11938: rtsol sgrub re dogs ga la yod //
NK102(ne)001:11939: mi mthun gnyen po bsgom mi dgos //
NK102(ne)001:11943: dug lnga la sogs kun byung ba la rtog pa
NK102(ne)001:11944: dang mtshan ma dus gsum du mthong rgyu med pa
NK102(ne)001:11946: rang byung rang zhi de bzhin nyid //
NK102(ne)001:11949: rnam par rtog pa'i mtshan ma ci byung yang //
NK102(ne)001:11950: rtog pa de nyid chos nyid yin zhe na //
NK102(ne)001:11951: chos kyi dbyings nyid gzhan du bsgom mi dgos //
NK102(ne)001:11954: dper na nam mkha'i rang bzhin las //
NK102(ne)001:11955: sprin dang na bun khug sna dang //
NK102(ne)001:11956: zla ba nyi ma skar tshogs dag /
NK102(ne)001:11957: snang yang nam mkha' bzhin du gnas //
NK102(ne)001:11958: de bzhin sems kyi nam mkha' la //
NK102(ne)001:11959: mtshan ma'i cho 'phrul ci byung yang //
NK102(ne)001:11960: bsam spyod bral ba'i bsam pa cig gis zhi nas ldang mi nus te /
NK102(ne)001:11962: gnyen po re re bsam mi dgos so //
NK102(ne)001:11964: khyung lding la ri zag gyen rtog pa ya med pa /
NK102(ne)001:11965: thur mi bde ba ril khobs khog tu tshud pa dang 'dra'o //
NK102(ne)001:11966: de la ni gol sgrib ming yang med do //
NK102(ne)001:11968: mi nub ma chags bde chen sems //
NK102(ne)001:11969: sems kyi dbyings las ma gtogs pa //
NK102(ne)001:11970: gzhan zhes gang yang med pas na //
NK102(ne)001:11971: su zhig gol sgrib don du gnyer //
NK102(ne)001:11972: gang gis gol sgrib ji ltar rnyed //
NK102(ne)001:11973: gol sgrib nyid kyang de nyid dbyings //
NK102(ne)001:11975: de lta bas na don ma nor ba'i bsgom pa 'di la gol ba med do //
NK102(ne)001:11976: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma'i sgom pa nor ta re bstan pa /
NK102(ne)001:11979: don ma nor bar phebs pa yul gang la yang /
NK102(ne)001:11981: mi g.yo ba bying rgod las /
NK102(ne)001:11982: dben cir yang 'dzin pa med pa /
NK102(ne)001:11985: rnam par so so bye brag tu /
NK102(ne)001:11989: rnam par mi mi rtog pa nyid du'ang mi rtog pa /
NK102(ne)001:11993: mi sems yid la bya ba med /
NK102(ne)001:11996: sems la dbyibs dang kha dog /
NK102(ne)001:12002: byang chub la yang gzugs med do //
NK102(ne)001:12003: sems kyi rang bzhin ni byang chub ste dbyer med do //
NK102(ne)001:12005: byang chub de dbyer med do //
NK102(ne)001:12006: kyi rang bzhin ni chos thams cad do //
NK102(ne)001:12007: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ni de kho na ji bzhin pa /
NK102(ne)001:12010: bsgom pa'i mtshan nyid bcu gnyis dang ldan par bstan to //
NK102(ne)001:12011: de las khyad par du gnyis med kyi rang bzhin ni nam mkha' dang 'dra ste /
NK102(ne)001:12015: dbyibs kha dog med pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12034: mngon par 'du byed pa med pa yin te /
NK102(ne)001:12035: mtshan nyid so bzhis dpe don sbyar ro //
NK102(ne)001:12036: de lta bu la yun ring du gnas na 'og gi rtags kyang rang 'char ro //
NK102(ne)001:12037: de lta bu mi shes par sgo gsum ched du 'chos shing rtsol ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:12039: sgrib pa yin te zhib tu sngar yang bstan /
NK102(ne)001:12041: bsam yul dmigs su med pa la //
NK102(ne)001:12042: btang snyoms chen po'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK102(ne)001:12043: ji bzhin pa nyid yid bzhin du //
NK102(ne)001:12044: lus dben sems kyi gol bar zhugs //
NK102(ne)001:12045: zhes 'byung bas bcos su med pa la bcos pa nyid /
NK102(ne)001:12046: rtog pa'i 'dzin pa dang phur pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:12047: de bas shin tu rnal 'byor gyi don spyod pa la /
NK102(ne)001:12048: thun mtshams bral bas ye rang byung du rang gsal
NK102(ne)001:12049: ba la rnam rtog ngang gis mi g.yo mi ldang
NK102(ne)001:12050: ste / ye nas lhun grub ngang chen po'i chos kyi skur brdal ba la /
NK102(ne)001:12051: 'phral du re mos su ting nge 'dzin las ldang
NK102(ne)001:12052: zhing slar 'jug cing bsgom pa med par la rbad
NK102(ne)001:12053: kyis bcad do // 'o na 'dir langs pa'i spyod mthong ji lta bu zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:12054: spyod lam yang ched du spyod par byar med de /
NK102(ne)001:12056: kun kyang bde gshegs kyis mdzad pa'i phyir ro //
NK102(ne)001:12057: de yang re zhig a ti yo ga'i spyod pa la rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK102(ne)001:12058: thugs rje chen po'i spyod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12059: bya rtsol bral bas don dang mthun pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12060: thabs chen po'i spyod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12061: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:12062: de la thugs rje chen po'i mdzad spyod ni /
NK102(ne)001:12063: 'dir thugs rje thabs kyi 'byung gnas chen por gyur pas /
NK102(ne)001:12064: snying rje chen po phyogs med par shar bas don mdzad do //
NK102(ne)001:12065: de yang tshul ci 'dra zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:12066: 'dir 'khor ba 'dren ched du btang bas sems ma 'gags la ma dmigs par rig pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12067: thugs rje chen po ye zin pa yang min /
NK102(ne)001:12068: rang byung gi ye shes las mdzad pa dang sprul
NK102(ne)001:12069: pa rgyun mi chad pa nyid bdag nyid kyi mdzad
NK102(ne)001:12070: spyod do // bdag gis de ltar shes nas /
NK102(ne)001:12071: thugs rje chen po btsal ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12072: dmigs pa med par don mdzad do //
NK102(ne)001:12074: byams pas don nyid rnam sbyangs phyir //
NK102(ne)001:12075: snying rje chen po ched du bya ba med pas cir yang snang /
NK102(ne)001:12079: ma skyes mi gnas nam mkha'i rang bzhin las //
NK102(ne)001:12080: thugs rje cho 'phrul ya mtshan chen po ston //
NK102(ne)001:12083: rang byung ye shes dbyings las ma g.yos kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12084: stong khams yongs su snyoms pa'i snying rje can //
NK102(ne)001:12085: 'gro ba'i dpal mgon sna tshogs kun tu bzang //
NK102(ne)001:12088: mthun 'jug tshang ba'i spyod pa rgya mtsho ni //
NK102(ne)001:12089: bdag dang gzhan don ye nas lhun grub kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12090: thugs rje chen pos 'gro don rdzogs par mdzad //
NK102(ne)001:12093: de ltar de bzhin chos kyi dbyings rig nas //
NK102(ne)001:12094: ma rig rnams la snying rje chen po bskyed //
NK102(ne)001:12095: snying rje skyes nas sgyu ma'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK102(ne)001:12096: 'gro don thabs kyi spyod pa sna tshogs spyod //
NK102(ne)001:12099: 'dod dgur 'byung zhing snying rje'i thabs mi spong //
NK102(ne)001:12102: 'khor ba mya ngan 'das la dgod pa'i phyir //
NK102(ne)001:12103: rang byung ye shes ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12104: stong khams yongs la snyoms pa'i snying rje 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:12107: bdag med phyogs bral chos dbyings nam mkha' mnyam //
NK102(ne)001:12108: sems can kun 'dren byang chub dbyings la 'god //
NK102(ne)001:12110: mdor ched du ma byas pa'i snying rje chen po dus gsum du ma thal ba ste /
NK102(ne)001:12111: ci byas ci spyad cir snang yang bdag rang byung gi ye shes kyi mdzad spyod yin pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:12112: bdag mnyam pas ngang las ma g.yos pas 'gro don rdzogs pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:12113: snying rje chen po'i ngang la yul du byed pa
NK102(ne)001:12114: la dmigs pa rang 'byung ye shes su bsgral lo
NK102(ne)001:12115: // de ltar gang gis shes pa de la gnas pa ste /
NK102(ne)001:12117: stong pa nyid la gnas pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12118: byams pa gang la rigs su 'byed pa med do //
NK102(ne)001:12121: tshad med pa bzhi ga ma btsal bar rdzogs so //
NK102(ne)001:12122: bya brtsal dang bral ba'i phyir don rjes su bya ba med par spyod pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12123: rnal 'byor ma h+aa yo ga ltar /
NK102(ne)001:12124: ting nge 'dzin de kho na ltar las su rung bas byas pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:12125: ched du byas pa med pas dang du blang du med de /
NK102(ne)001:12126: bya ba med pa zhig tu dang du len na /
NK102(ne)001:12127: de nyid kyang bya byed kyi spyod pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:12129: dang du blang bya ngang gis med do //
NK102(ne)001:12130: 'o na cir yang byar med na /
NK102(ne)001:12131: mi bya bar 'dug gam zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:12132: lan du 'dug pa yang ma dmigs te /
NK102(ne)001:12133: gang 'dug pa yod na med pa'ang yod par 'gyur gyi /
NK102(ne)001:12134: spyod lam rnam bzhi nyid ma 'gags ma dmigs pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:12135: ci yang byas kyang byas pa med /
NK102(ne)001:12137: yod pa dang bral ba yang med de /
NK102(ne)001:12138: de ltar spyod pa gdengs chud pa la /
NK102(ne)001:12139: 'og gi mchod 'don la sogs pa ched du byar med do //
NK102(ne)001:12141: las rnams sna tshogs ci byas kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12142: thig le nyid pas spang du med //
NK102(ne)001:12145: sangs rgyas zhing khams thams cad du //
NK102(ne)001:12146: bdag nyid kun gyi lha yin pas //
NK102(ne)001:12147: kun gyi mchod pas bdag la mchod //
NK102(ne)001:12150: mnyam pas rim par bkod pa med //
NK102(ne)001:12151: gcig las phyogs su bsngo dang bral //
NK102(ne)001:12152: tshogs kyi brgyan dang bkram pa yang //
NK102(ne)001:12153: rang bzhin gnas nas 'grim pa med //
NK102(ne)001:12154: lhun gyis grub pas mi bsngo zhing //
NK102(ne)001:12155: gdod nas dag pa bdud rtsi yin //
NK102(ne)001:12158: mi bzung gtong bas gtor ma yin //
NK102(ne)001:12159: bya ba med pa'i las rnams te //
NK102(ne)001:12162: chos nyid bya rtsol kun bral las //
NK102(ne)001:12163: sgrub dang sgrub pa'i dmigs pa med //
NK102(ne)001:12165: rnal 'byor chos gzhung chen po'i yon tan las /
NK102(ne)001:12166: lus dang gzugs su snang ba thams cad ye nas ma g.yos pas mi 'gyur /
NK102(ne)001:12169: thams cad chos kyi sku'i ngang las gzung 'dzin gyi rtsol ba las 'das pa /
NK102(ne)001:12170: de lus kyi chos 'byung yin te /
NK102(ne)001:12172: chos thams cad rtsol ba med par ye nas lhun gyis grub par sangs rgyas zin pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:12174: de bas kyang ngag gi las su snying po bzlas /
NK102(ne)001:12175: chos thams cad tshig dang yi ge /
NK102(ne)001:12176: thams cad thugs ye shes yin par shes pas /
NK102(ne)001:12177: ci 'das pa thams cad chos nyid kyi bzlas brjod /
NK102(ne)001:12178: ye shes kyi cho 'phrul gnyis su med pa'i don yin par shes na /
NK102(ne)001:12179: ngag gis ci brjod pa chos kyi gzhung yin no //
NK102(ne)001:12180: bdag gi sems kyi gzhung bzhin ma rig pa'i dbang
NK102(ne)001:12181: las 'du byed langs pa'i dug lnga rang ka ma
NK102(ne)001:12184: log par lta ba la sogs pa lta ba log cing bsam pa gol ba ma yin pa /
NK102(ne)001:12185: chos nyid la 'jam rtsub med pas zhi zhing des pa'i sems la /
NK102(ne)001:12186: sangs rgyas la phyogs ris med pas thams cad la
NK102(ne)001:12187: mnyam snyoms chen po shong yangs che zhing bag yangs
NK102(ne)001:12188: pas kun dang mthun zhing yongs dang ma 'gras pa
NK102(ne)001:12189: / ris med cing nyes pa ci la yang mi bzod pa med pa /
NK102(ne)001:12190: legs pa la chags shing zhen pa med pas /
NK102(ne)001:12191: rgyu 'bras kyi chos thams cad gnyis su med pas srid pa nyid dag kyang ste /
NK102(ne)001:12192: mi 'gyur ba'i dbyings na ma yengs pa'i blo btang snyoms su ldem mi gnas pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12193: rnal 'byor pa'i sems kyi gzhung yin no //
NK102(ne)001:12195: bya bral rdzogs pa'i lung las /
NK102(ne)001:12196: sems nyid cir mi snang ba'i phyir spyod pa cir yang mi spyod de /
NK102(ne)001:12197: gtsang rme phyogs ris rtsod pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12198: che chung chags sdang blang dor sogs //
NK102(ne)001:12199: ci la yang bye brag mi bya na //
NK102(ne)001:12200: theg chen rnal 'byor ga la yin //
NK102(ne)001:12202: kun tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa las /
NK102(ne)001:12203: bde dang sdug bsngal rtog pas na //
NK102(ne)001:12204: bdag rgyal gzhan la pham ci'i chos //
NK102(ne)001:12205: bzang dang ngan par 'khrul pa na //
NK102(ne)001:12206: 'dod pas mi chog gang gis bstan //
NK102(ne)001:12207: mnyam nyid che chung med pa la //
NK102(ne)001:12208: bdag bstod gzhan smod su zhig smra //
NK102(ne)001:12209: gang nyid spong len med pa la //
NK102(ne)001:12210: blang dang dor ba gang gis brjod //
NK102(ne)001:12212: gtan tshigs de dag gis yid ches par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:12213: kun tu bzang po thabs kyi spyod pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12214: ye nyid ma lus chos thams cad kun tu bzang
NK102(ne)001:12215: po'i ngang du sangs rgyas pa la spangs blang yang
NK102(ne)001:12218: de ltar gdengs chud nas gang yang mi 'dor bar
NK102(ne)001:12219: spyod pa la mi gol ba ni kun bzang thabs
NK102(ne)001:12220: kyi spyod pa'o // de yang yid ches par byed pa'i rgyab nan sems bsgom las /
NK102(ne)001:12221: shes rab kyi spyod pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12223: la mi gnas phyir na bdud kyi 'dra bar spyod do //
NK102(ne)001:12224: drug nag po can gyi bu kor /
NK102(ne)001:12225: mi pham skra'i lwa ba can /
NK102(ne)001:12227: kun tu rgyu gnag lhas kyi bu /
NK102(ne)001:12228: gcer bu pa gnyen gyi bu /
NK102(ne)001:12229: smra 'dod kyi bu mo'i bu yang dag rgyal ba can dang drug go /
NK102(ne)001:12230: gis bstan pa'i bdud kyi las kyang mi 'dor ngan du mi rtog go //
NK102(ne)001:12233: spyod lam rnam bzhi gang spyad kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12237: brtul zhugs spyod pa spyod min te //
NK102(ne)001:12238: sems la sems gzhol rol spyod pa //
NK102(ne)001:12239: thabs chen yangs pa spyod pa'i mchog /
NK102(ne)001:12242: dper na sman 'tsho byed mkhas pas /
NK102(ne)001:12243: ston zla ra ba'i nya la yal ga dang lo
NK102(ne)001:12244: 'dab rgyas pa'i dus su nags tshal chen por song
NK102(ne)001:12245: na / ci skyes pa thams cad 'du ba rnam
NK102(ne)001:12246: bzhi'i nad la sman du ma gyur pa gang yang
NK102(ne)001:12247: med pa dang 'dra ba de bzhin du bzang ngan
NK102(ne)001:12248: dang spong len che chung med par shes pas thams
NK102(ne)001:12249: cad bzang par yid ches shing bka' yang dag pa
NK102(ne)001:12251: gang la'ang the tshom mi za bar spyod pa rnal 'byor gyi chos gzhung yin no //
NK102(ne)001:12253: dper na sman pa 'tsho byed gzhon nu yis /
NK102(ne)001:12254: dug dang rdzas ci sbyar bar /
NK102(ne)001:12255: phan pa'i bdud rtsir 'gyur ba bzhin /
NK102(ne)001:12256: rnal 'byor pa chos kyi don la mkhas pas /
NK102(ne)001:12257: 'khor ba dang mya ngan 'das pa'i chos la ji ltar spyad kyang nyes pa med cing /
NK102(ne)001:12258: thams cad bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin du 'gyur ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:12261: 'dod spyod snying rjes brlan pa la //
NK102(ne)001:12262: gang du dga' bar byang chub spyod //
NK102(ne)001:12265: kun spyod yon tan rnam lnga yang //
NK102(ne)001:12266: chos nyid dbyings kyi rgyan zhes gsungs //
NK102(ne)001:12269: rnam grangs brgya stong phrag yangs pas //
NK102(ne)001:12270: gang ltar spyad kyang me tog skye //
NK102(ne)001:12273: 'dzin pas btags shing snang ba'i chos rnams ni //
NK102(ne)001:12274: rang gi rkyen gyis snang bas mi 'dod spong mi byed //
NK102(ne)001:12275: rnam pa cir yang mi dgongs thabs kyis de la rol //
NK102(ne)001:12278: ye shes rtogs pa'i khyad par gyis //
NK102(ne)001:12279: spyod lam rnam bzhir gang spyod kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12282: bdag dang gzhan don lhun grub ma spangs pa //
NK102(ne)001:12283: spyod pa rgya mtshor sna tshogs ci bder spyod //
NK102(ne)001:12284: pad+ma skyes pa'i rgyu ni 'dam yin te //
NK102(ne)001:12285: pad+ma la ni 'dam gyis gos pa med //
NK102(ne)001:12286: chos nyid chags pa med par rtogs 'gyur na //
NK102(ne)001:12287: ye shes chags med nyams pa rdul tsam med //
NK102(ne)001:12288: thugs rje spyod pa bsam yas ji snyed pa //
NK102(ne)001:12289: rnal 'byor thabs kyi spyod pa de bzhin spyod //
NK102(ne)001:12292: dogs med spyad kyang de la ni //
NK102(ne)001:12293: gang ltar spyad kyang me tog skye //
NK102(ne)001:12296: ma bkag ci bde byang chub yan du khyer //
NK102(ne)001:12299: rang gi longs spyod rang las sprul //
NK102(ne)001:12300: rang las sprul pa'i sku rnams la //
NK102(ne)001:12301: rang gi longs spyod cir yang mdzad //
NK102(ne)001:12304: sku las kun 'byung ba'i chos la kun spyod pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:12305: sems las kun 'byung ba'i chos la spyod pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:12306: ngag las kun 'byung ba'i chos la spyod pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:12307: chos las kun 'byung ba'i chos la spyod pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:12308: yul wa r+aa na si'i kha dog so sor gsal ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12309: gos kyi kha dog bzhin du so sor 'gog pa med par thugs su chud do //
NK102(ne)001:12312: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das ni tshad med pa'i bsod
NK102(ne)001:12313: nams kyi tshogs dpag tu med pa rnams yang dag
NK102(ne)001:12315: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK102(ne)001:12316: gang la yang spangs blang mi bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:12317: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i spyod pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12318: ril sangs rgyas pa la 'khor ba ming med de /
NK102(ne)001:12319: 'bras bu nyi tsher gsal ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:12320: ston zla 'bring po'i nya bzhin pas spyod do //
NK102(ne)001:12321: phyogs thams cad sangs rgyas kyi mdzad par ma gyur pa med pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:12322: spyod pa ril 'dir mdzad spyod do //
NK102(ne)001:12323: yon tan chen po bcu las /
NK102(ne)001:12324: a ti yo ga'i spyod pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12325: mu stegs kri ya'i spyod pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12326: srid gsum sems can thams cad dang //
NK102(ne)001:12327: skye ba rnam bzhir rtogs pa kun //
NK102(ne)001:12328: rdzogs chen rang bzhin lhun gyis spyod //
NK102(ne)001:12331: spyod par byed dang spyad med pas //
NK102(ne)001:12332: srid dang mu stegs 'jig rten pa'i //
NK102(ne)001:12333: spyod par snang ba thams cad kun //
NK102(ne)001:12334: lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i mdzad spyod do //
NK102(ne)001:12337: sems can mang po'i byed spyod ni //
NK102(ne)001:12338: gsang ba mchog gi don yin te //
NK102(ne)001:12339: sangs rgyas nyid kyi mdzad pa yin //
NK102(ne)001:12341: de ltar gtan tshigs rgyab tu bzhag /
NK102(ne)001:12342: rig pas mdun na bsu ste /
NK102(ne)001:12343: gnyis mi 'gal bar yid ches par byed pa la the tshom ma za zhig /
NK102(ne)001:12344: spyod pa bzhi yang ngo bo tha dad pa ma yin te /
NK102(ne)001:12345: gcig kyang bzhi car du snang ngo //
NK102(ne)001:12346: de lta bu la ched du spyod lam dum bu can du med de /
NK102(ne)001:12347: thams cad du spyod pa las mnyam pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:12348: mnyam pa las langs ma langs mthong lugs la khyad par med de /
NK102(ne)001:12349: de yang kun tu bzang po rang gnas pa las /
NK102(ne)001:12350: snang la rang bzhin med pa yi //
NK102(ne)001:12351: chu zla smig rgyu sgyu ma bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:12352: med pa zang ma ma yin la //
NK102(ne)001:12353: yod par yang ni ma yin no //
NK102(ne)001:12354: yod med gnyis las 'das pa yi //
NK102(ne)001:12355: rang bzhin med par yid la dran //
NK102(ne)001:12356: shes rab chen pos rtogs pa'i rtags //
NK102(ne)001:12357: mkha' ltar mnyam par nyid la gnas //
NK102(ne)001:12358: shes rab chen pos khyab pa'i rtags //
NK102(ne)001:12359: mi g.yo mnyam bzhag 'dus ma byas //
NK102(ne)001:12360: shes rab chen po grub pa'i rtags //
NK102(ne)001:12361: ma chags thabs kyi kun spyod na //
NK102(ne)001:12362: shes rab chen po grub pa'i rtags //
NK102(ne)001:12364: de bas na don las ma nyams kyang sgyu mar snang ba 'gog pa med do //
NK102(ne)001:12365: spyod pa gol ba ni dus deng sang gi sngags pa thos pa rgya chen po dang bral bas /
NK102(ne)001:12366: gdengs ma chud cing lta ba kha la khyer nas /
NK102(ne)001:12367: kun tu bzang po yin zhes zer zhing 'dod sbyar gsod gcod dang /
NK102(ne)001:12368: rtsing chos phata hral 'dral gyi spyod pa byed pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12369: dmyal ba'i gting rdo byed do //
NK102(ne)001:12371: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pas ma zin dge ba'i chos ni gang yang rung //
NK102(ne)001:12372: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa'ang bdud kyi las te zad cing mthar thug 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:12373: de dag ldan pa'i las ni bdud kyi las kyang byang chub spyod par gsungs //
NK102(ne)001:12376: snying rje med pa'i las kyi gzhi rnams ni //
NK102(ne)001:12377: kun tu bzang po'i tshig tsam smra 'dra yang //
NK102(ne)001:12381: lta ba kha la yod snying la med la spyod pa rtsing na med /
NK102(ne)001:12383: de dag lta a cang yang ches rnam par dkar
NK102(ne)001:12384: ba'i las nyid kyang thabs 'dis ma zin na mi
NK102(ne)001:12387: bla ma mchod dang gtong ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12388: de bzhin bsod nams thams cad kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12389: ma chags mi g.yo'i stobs med na //
NK102(ne)001:12393: lta ba 'di med spyod pa sgyu mas min //
NK102(ne)001:12394: lta ba 'di yis ma zin 'khor ba las mi 'da' //
NK102(ne)001:12396: de lta bas na gdengs yod kyang sdig la shin tu 'dzem par byas na tshul dang ldan te /
NK102(ne)001:12398: sdig 'dzem cher skyes bsod nams khri phrag yas //
NK102(ne)001:12400: spyod pa 'di lta bu la mos pa'i yon tan yang /
NK102(ne)001:12402: gang zhig rtog pa dang mi ldan yang //
NK102(ne)001:12403: gzhung du spyod pa rnams mos pa'i stobs kyi thugs rje'i byin rlabs rang snang ste /
NK102(ne)001:12404: gser la nag tshur btang ba ltar don ma nor /
NK102(ne)001:12406: byas pa chud ma zos pas /
NK102(ne)001:12407: yid kyi ting 'dzin gsal byas te //
NK102(ne)001:12408: bla ma mkhas pa'i man ngag gis //
NK102(ne)001:12409: yang dag bdud rtsir byin rlabs nas //
NK102(ne)001:12410: gnyis su med par sangs rgyas so //
NK102(ne)001:12412: yongs spyi ru theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi
NK102(ne)001:12413: sgom chen gyis ji lta ba lta ba'i gdengs chud
NK102(ne)001:12414: kyang / de bzhin du ma mthong ba drang zhing
NK102(ne)001:12415: tshul dang ldan par bya ba'i phyir 'di ltar mdzad
NK102(ne)001:12416: kyang / 'tshal te / de la lus kyi spyod
NK102(ne)001:12417: pa yang chos thams cad mnyam pa'i ngang la bdag
NK102(ne)001:12418: mtho sar rgyu med pas tshul 'chos bzang du re
NK102(ne)001:12420: ril bdag nyid chen po yin pas grogs la mi chags par bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12422: glang po che ltar zon bag che bar bya zhing brjid brtan che bar bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12423: lus spyod ci yang ched du bcos par mi bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12424: gnas gang yang rung ba'i dgon par rtag par 'dug pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12425: skya chus mang po mi bya zhing de la'ang ma chags pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12426: spyod lam bzhi kar lus bya ba bsgyur zhing don dang ma bral ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12427: gos kyang grang bas mi nyen pa tsam las bzang
NK102(ne)001:12428: du re ba'i phyir rgyan gyis bcos slob mi bya
NK102(ne)001:12429: ba dang / kha zas kyang ched du zhim pa la chags par mi bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12430: stong 'phyor ngom 'phyar gang yang mi bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:12431: de yang yid ches pa'i gtan tshigs /
NK102(ne)001:12433: rdo rje lus kyi spyod pa ni //
NK102(ne)001:12434: phyin pa med pas tshul mi 'chos //
NK102(ne)001:12435: gcig pu nyid la gcig pur gnas //
NK102(ne)001:12436: glang po lta stangs ji bzhin dang //
NK102(ne)001:12437: de bzhin rnal mas gnas par bya //
NK102(ne)001:12438: gang du gnas pas rtag par gnas //
NK102(ne)001:12439: gnas pa de la chags mi bya //
NK102(ne)001:12440: spyod lam rnam bzhir gar ldan par //
NK102(ne)001:12441: ma bcos rnal mas gnas par bya //
NK102(ne)001:12442: gang gis gdung bas mi nyen pa'i //
NK102(ne)001:12443: gnod pa skyo ba tsam dag las //
NK102(ne)001:12444: bzang dang rgyan gyis chas mi bya //
NK102(ne)001:12445: gang du ji ltar bde ldan sbyar //
NK102(ne)001:12447: kha zas kyang lus su 'dzin pa'i 'tshe rten du /
NK102(ne)001:12448: yo byad kyis 'byor na bzang yang rung /
NK102(ne)001:12450: 'byor tshad las ro mchog can la ched du chags pas mi gnyer ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12451: de yang rlung dgag khams log tu dogs pa tsam /
NK102(ne)001:12453: ched ka can la yin pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12454: dro 'tshag dang nyams sel phyir blang ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12455: longs spyod pa yang ji bzhin pa'i don dang ldan pas dpyad pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12456: rang ka mas tshims par bya ba'i ched du skye bo'i bsam pas mi bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12457: ro zhim mi zhim gang la yang blang dor gyi sems mi bya /
NK102(ne)001:12458: theg pa chung ngu'i spyod pa bsod snyoms mi bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:12460: rnal 'byor nges pa'i bsam gtan pa //
NK102(ne)001:12461: rdo rje sngags kyi kha zas ni //
NK102(ne)001:12462: lus zungs 'dzin pa'i rten tsam du //
NK102(ne)001:12463: gang sngar 'byor ldan ma gtogs pa //
NK102(ne)001:12464: zas phyir ched du bsgrub mi bya /
NK102(ne)001:12465: tshag dang nyams phyir ga la yin //
NK102(ne)001:12466: ma bcos rnal mas ji bzhin baza'i //
NK102(ne)001:12467: 'tsho ba'i ched du bcos mi bya //
NK102(ne)001:12468: chags dang ma chags spang blangs med //
NK102(ne)001:12469: blang bar bya ba ma yin zhing //
NK102(ne)001:12470: slong mos 'tsho bar yong mi bya //
NK102(ne)001:12471: ci phyir don du mi 'gyur phyir //
