NK102(ne)001:12472: 'tsho ba yongs su ma dag pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:12475: chos kyi don du snyan par smra ba yang /
NK102(ne)001:12476: gad mo chen po rta gad mi bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12477: smra ba btsan par bya ste rdzun mi bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12478: 'chal bar smra ba mi bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12479: ci smras pa bdag gzhan gyi don du 'brel bar bya ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12480: dgos ched dang skabs la bab pa ma yin pa
NK102(ne)001:12481: bsam gtan grogs dang 'dus pa'i tshe yang 'chal gtam
NK102(ne)001:12483: smra brjod dpes mtshon la pha rol la go mjal du smra ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12485: ngag tshad mar smra ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12486: ji skad brjod pa nyid du med pa'i don yin pas /
NK102(ne)001:12487: ngag kyang che ngag dang rung du re mi bya bar don dang ma bral bar smra ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:12489: rdo rje ngag gi spyod yul yang //
NK102(ne)001:12490: bden pa'i ched du snyan smra las //
NK102(ne)001:12491: gzhan du kha gsag ga zha min //
NK102(ne)001:12492: brjod pa thams cad nges pa nyid //
NK102(ne)001:12493: dngos por smra zhing tshig mi 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:12494: ji ltar brjod pa de bzhin bya //
NK102(ne)001:12495: thams cad kun tu smra ma yin //
NK102(ne)001:12496: gang brjod don dang 'brel bar bya //
NK102(ne)001:12497: skabs dang dgos ched ma gtogs par //
NK102(ne)001:12498: rnam par 'chal bar bya ba min //
NK102(ne)001:12499: kun la dpes mtshon thog tu dbab //
NK102(ne)001:12500: thams cad tshad mas tshad mar bya //
NK102(ne)001:12501: ma bcos ngang gi rnal 'byor pa //
NK102(ne)001:12502: rdo rje ngag gi spyod par bshad //
NK102(ne)001:12505: rdo rje yid kyi spyod yul nyid //
NK102(ne)001:12509: mi g.yeng g.yengs ba drug med pa /
NK102(ne)001:12510: ma rmugs gsal bying rmugs med pa /
NK102(ne)001:12524: de rnyed nor rdzas rnyed pa la ma chags /
NK102(ne)001:12529: med pas don dang ldan pa /
NK102(ne)001:12530: yongs su gang la yang nang du skyon du /
NK102(ne)001:12532: go bgos lam nyid brtson 'grus kyi sgo gsum chos dang mi 'gal /
NK102(ne)001:12534: dug 'gyur lta ba'i thabs dang man ngag /
NK102(ne)001:12535: sman bsrel mtshon char lta ba che ba ste shes rab /
NK102(ne)001:12537: rdo rje'i rdzong la de rnyed pas mi 'bral /
NK102(ne)001:12539: yid bzhin byang chub sems zhi gnas lhag mthong 'brel /
NK102(ne)001:12541: gang du bsam pa yul gang gi dbang du /
NK102(ne)001:12542: mi 'gyur gang mi bsam pa dngos don las /
NK102(ne)001:12544: dbyings 'dir don gyi dbang gi kun dang mthun /
NK102(ne)001:12546: gang gi blo la mngon chos spyod mis spyod gzhan /
NK102(ne)001:12553: de nyid rang sems dpang du btsug /
NK102(ne)001:12555: de la nga 'am nga bdag 'dzin dang nga rgyal /
NK102(ne)001:12566: de nyid zhi ril rang rig tu /
NK102(ne)001:12567: bas 'khrul zhe sdang khong khro med dang //
NK102(ne)001:12568: gang nas phyogs kyang dngos grub ste rab /
NK102(ne)001:12575: gdung ba med 'dod chags kyi yul gang la yang /
NK102(ne)001:12577: ma chags pa'i bsam pa can /
NK102(ne)001:12578: 'byung bas chog par gang la chog par /
NK102(ne)001:12580: gang la'ang rtog pa dang ldan pa /
NK102(ne)001:12583: rme med cing dus gsum dus snga phyi 'dzin pa /
NK102(ne)001:12585: de bzhin dam pa'ang dang du len pa'i /
NK102(ne)001:12586: yod ma no spyod pa bzhi bcu'i gsum mo //
NK102(ne)001:12588: zhes 'byung ba'i don dang sbyar la spyod do //
NK102(ne)001:12589: de ltar tshul bzhin spyod pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12591: bya ba de dag byas kyang byas 'dzin dang /
NK102(ne)001:12592: dka' thub sems su'ang mi 'cha' ste /
NK102(ne)001:12593: rang bzhin gza' gtad med pas spyod do //
NK102(ne)001:12594: de la spong len ngang gis bral yang spyod pa ril spyod la /
NK102(ne)001:12595: de la dran pas bskul ba tsam mi 'gog la /
NK102(ne)001:12596: bskul na ched du dran pa yid la byed pa las kyang 'das so //
NK102(ne)001:12597: de lta bu'i dgongs pa la 'bras bu dang /
NK102(ne)001:12598: rtags mtshan gyi re ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12599: dogs pa dang yang bral yang /
NK102(ne)001:12600: nyams drod 'byung la 'gog pa med par 'char ba ste /
NK102(ne)001:12601: nyams ni rnal 'byor ma h+aa yo ga'i skabs su /
NK102(ne)001:12602: bstan pa'i sems du yang rung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:12603: de ltar byung yang ngo bo 'di snyom byed ces bstan du med de /
NK102(ne)001:12604: myong bya'i yul la dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK102(ne)001:12606: sla zhing dka' la sla phyir dka' //
NK102(ne)001:12607: mngon sum mi gnas kun tu khyab //
NK102(ne)001:12608: ming tsam 'di zhes bstan par ni //
NK102(ne)001:12609: rdo rje sems dpa' mtshon du med //
NK102(ne)001:12612: ma skyes don la reg 'gyur na //
NK102(ne)001:12613: rang gi kho na tsam du zad //
NK102(ne)001:12614: rang rig de yang 'di snyam zhes //
NK102(ne)001:12615: gzhan la bstan cing brjod du med //
NK102(ne)001:12616: tshig gi mtshon du de la med //
NK102(ne)001:12620: ji tsam rtag tu med pa'i zab mo zhig /
NK102(ne)001:12621: blo'i ngang du gsal bar de zhen na //
NK102(ne)001:12622: gang la mi rtog zab mo'i don myong ba //
NK102(ne)001:12623: myong ba yin phyir de ni rtog pa yin //
NK102(ne)001:12625: cir yang ma myong ba'i don gdengs chud pa nyid la tha snyad du myong zhes kyang bya ste /
NK102(ne)001:12635: de yang a tsar rnam gsum gyi man ngag las /
NK102(ne)001:12636: sems dang por tshor ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:12638: sems bar ma'i tshor ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:12639: 'du shes skye ba las sgyu ma yin pa la sgyu mar rtog pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:12640: de la mi 'gog mi 'brang bar bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:12641: mthar phyin pa'i tshor ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:12642: skye 'gag med pa'i dbyings nyid rnam par mi rtog pa'i dbyings nyid de /
NK102(ne)001:12643: de la yang mi gnas par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:12644: bsgom chags rnam gsum yod do //
NK102(ne)001:12645: de la nyams dang po ni 'du shes byung tshor nas zhi ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:12651: mthar phyin pa'i tshor ba ni /
NK102(ne)001:12652: dbyings mnyams pa nyid la'ang mi gnas pa'i tshor ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:12655: tshig gi don ma yin pa'i don blos gshis su phebs pa'i dus na /
NK102(ne)001:12656: drod chen po gsum zhig 'byung ste /
NK102(ne)001:12661: dbugs phyi nang du rgyu ba yang mi tshor ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:12663: mnyam pa nyid mngon sum du snang tsam na /
NK102(ne)001:12664: gzugs kyi phung po shing bal gyi 'dab ma rlung
NK102(ne)001:12665: gis g.yengs pa ltar phung po yod par mi mthong
NK102(ne)001:12667: yum kun tu bzang mo yum gyi mkha' gsal bar gyur pa'i dus na /
NK102(ne)001:12668: chos nyid kyi ro bde ba chen po nyams su myong ste /
NK102(ne)001:12670: bdag nyid gcig pu la bde ba 'byung ba lta bu ma yin gyi /
NK102(ne)001:12671: kun gzhis ma khyab pa'i chos med pas /
NK102(ne)001:12672: thams cad nas thams cad du bde ba chen po'i ro 'da' bar 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:12675: de la thog tu phebs pa'i drod gsum zhig yod de /
NK102(ne)001:12676: mtshan mar snang ba'i bag chags rgyu ba chad nas /
NK102(ne)001:12677: blo dwangs ma yi nam mkha' ltar gnas te /
NK102(ne)001:12678: mtshan ma g.yo ba med par bde ba zhig byung na /
NK102(ne)001:12681: phyi nang srid pa'i chos thams cad mngon sum du snang zhing nyam nga ba med par rig na /
NK102(ne)001:12682: 'di ni snang ba mi skyen pa zhes bya ste /
NK102(ne)001:12685: ci la ma spyad par yongs su khyab pa chen por btang bas /
NK102(ne)001:12686: chos ji bzhin pa la rig pa de bzhin spyi
NK102(ne)001:12687: blugs su gyur pas rgyud zhib mos ma bkrol bzhin
NK102(ne)001:12688: du sems dang chos thugs phrad du gyur pas /
NK102(ne)001:12689: chu dang 'o ma 'dres pa bzhin du blo bde ba chen po zhig tu gyur nas /
NK102(ne)001:12690: sngar 'di lta bu blo la byung ma myong ste /
NK102(ne)001:12691: yid g.yang za ba phyad chad pa zhig byung ba des /
NK102(ne)001:12692: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa thams cad dus gcig tu phyags mas btab nas so //
NK102(ne)001:12695: de lta'i don la ring zhig nas //
NK102(ne)001:12696: shes shing 'dris par gyur pa na //
NK102(ne)001:12697: des don mthong ba'i nyams drod ni //
NK102(ne)001:12698: don dang mjal ba'i rtags chen yang //
NK102(ne)001:12699: man ngag lung gis brgyad 'char te //
NK102(ne)001:12700: nges par don gsum myong bar 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:12701: de dag thog tu phebs pa'i drod //
NK102(ne)001:12702: drod chen rtags su brtan pa yin //
NK102(ne)001:12703: de yi zhar las 'byung ba'i drod //
NK102(ne)001:12704: 'khor ba'i chos la snying rje ba'i //
NK102(ne)001:12705: byang chub sems kyang skye bar 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:12706: mtshan mar rtog pa'i chos rnams la //
NK102(ne)001:12708: chos rnams 'di ltar yin pa la //
NK102(ne)001:12712: rtsol sgrub dka' ba'i thabs chen gyis //
NK102(ne)001:12713: yang dag don chen lam re ring //
NK102(ne)001:12714: bsags pa'i 'bras bu yod gyur kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12715: don de mthong bar yong mi 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:12717: de ltar shes pa'i nyams drod ni //
NK102(ne)001:12718: skal dang ldan pa'i skyes bu gang //
NK102(ne)001:12719: rgyud 'gros tshig gis ma bkrol bar //
NK102(ne)001:12721: smra ba'i sgo mor thams cad gsal //
NK102(ne)001:12722: don la nges pa'i gtan tshigs dag /
NK102(ne)001:12723: tshig gis mtshon te 'byin par nus //
NK102(ne)001:12726: blo rtsal las kyi khyad par gyis //
NK102(ne)001:12728: yang dag bden pa'i don bstan na //
NK102(ne)001:12729: mi skrag mi dngangs dga' ba skye //
NK102(ne)001:12730: yang dag don la nges bltas na //
NK102(ne)001:12731: 'khor ba'i chos la skyo ba skye //
NK102(ne)001:12732: yang dag don la 'dris pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12733: rnam grangs chos la dad mi 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:12734: yang dag don nyid mthong ba na //
NK102(ne)001:12735: tshogs la dga' ba mi skye zhing //
NK102(ne)001:12736: don nyid nye bar 'dzin par byed //
NK102(ne)001:12737: don mthong ba dang ye shes skye //
NK102(ne)001:12738: ye shes skyes par gyur pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12739: dngos po snang ba thams cad kun //
NK102(ne)001:12740: sgyu ma bzhin du shes par 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:12741: sgyu ma tsam du shes pa la //
NK102(ne)001:12742: brten nas chos nyid don bltas na //
NK102(ne)001:12743: snang ba med pa'i don nyid ni //
NK102(ne)001:12744: snang ba med par mthong bar 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:12745: snang med srid pa mthong ba'i tshe //
NK102(ne)001:12747: de ni bden pa'i snga ltas so //
NK102(ne)001:12748: de nas nyi ma'i 'od zer gyis //
NK102(ne)001:12750: 'di ni g.yo ba'i snga ltas so //
NK102(ne)001:12751: de nas smig rgyu lta bu 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:12752: dang po'i drod ces bya bar bshad //
NK102(ne)001:12754: bar gyi drod ces bya bar bshad //
NK102(ne)001:12755: de nas rlung chen lta bu yang //
NK102(ne)001:12757: tha ma'i drod ces bya bar bshad //
NK102(ne)001:12758: de nas yig 'bru'i drod spros pas //
NK102(ne)001:12760: de ni thob pa'i drod ces bshad //
NK102(ne)001:12761: de ni mkha' la sprin bzhin lding //
NK102(ne)001:12763: de ni shin tu brtan pa'i drod //
NK102(ne)001:12764: de nas ta la gcig tsam du //
NK102(ne)001:12765: bdag gi lus ni dbang med par //
NK102(ne)001:12767: 'di ni shin tu gsal ba'i drod //
NK102(ne)001:12772: dang po mi dga' ba'i shas 'byung /
NK102(ne)001:12773: de nas gzhig cing bag tsha ba 'byung /
NK102(ne)001:12774: de nas thams cad sgyid lug pa 'byung /
NK102(ne)001:12775: de nas bdag nyid chung zhing dul ba snyam byed /
NK102(ne)001:12776: de nas 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad brdzun nam /
NK102(ne)001:12779: de nas 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad la dngos po dang /
NK102(ne)001:12781: phyogs ris su 'dzin pa la snying rje bskyed de /
NK102(ne)001:12782: col med re gol snyam byed /
NK102(ne)001:12783: de nas ci la yang ma chags pa snyam byed la /
NK102(ne)001:12784: 'jigs shing dogs pa'i rnam pa til tsam yang med par /
NK102(ne)001:12785: lus shing bal gyi 'dab ma ltar yangs shing yod pa snyam yang mi byed la /
NK102(ne)001:12786: yid kyi rnam par shes pa dar lo lce'i me tog lha mo bskyed mas btegs pa bzhin /
NK102(ne)001:12787: nyams la teg teg la thams cad 'dus pa'i tshe /
NK102(ne)001:12788: rab yeng yeng po cir snang tsam la /
NK102(ne)001:12789: chos thams cad rnam par ci yang ma grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsal /
NK102(ne)001:12790: gang ltar 'dod pa ltar bsgom zhing /
NK102(ne)001:12791: bsgyur du 'dod pa zhig 'byung phan chad /
NK102(ne)001:12792: byang chub sems bsgom pa'i drod phebs pas /
NK102(ne)001:12793: kun tu bzang po bde ba chen po nyid yin no //
NK102(ne)001:12794: de ltar drod ma shar kyang khad kyis cig pa chung yang de ltar bsgoms na /
NK102(ne)001:12795: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin du gyur nas /
NK102(ne)001:12796: de las yang kun tu bzang por de nyid 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:12799: yang dag pa'i don las 'pho 'gyur med pa lhang
NK102(ne)001:12800: nger gnas pa ni chos kyi gzhung gi drod thob
NK102(ne)001:12803: lus kyi drod 'og na med shig mi tshor ba yan chad /
NK102(ne)001:12805: gnyid kyi rtogs pa choms pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12806: lus kyi bzod pa thob pa ni //
NK102(ne)001:12807: 'di ni dang po'i drod yin no //
NK102(ne)001:12808: khams kyi zas dang bral ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12809: mdangs dang dbang po gsal bar 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:12810: 'di ni gnyis pa'i drod ces bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:12811: shing bal lta bur yang ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12812: khams bde mi bde mi 'byung zhing //
NK102(ne)001:12813: nad kyi tshogs dang bral gyur pa //
NK102(ne)001:12814: 'di ni drod chen brtan pa yin //
NK102(ne)001:12816: de dag gsal bas dgrol bshad mi bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:12817: de dag gi drod snga phyi la gnas pa'i dus su /
NK102(ne)001:12818: rmis ltas rnams ni mtshan ma la brtag cing 'byung yang /
NK102(ne)001:12820: mtshan ma pra'i rmi ltas kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12821: shin tu rgya cher 'byung ba ste //
NK102(ne)001:12822: rnal 'byor can gyis shes par gyis //
NK102(ne)001:12823: bag chags 'byang ba'i snga ltas kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12824: rtag par gcer bur phyung ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12825: khrus chen rtag tu byed pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12826: dri ma'i tshogs rnams dag pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12827: chu bo dag la rkyal pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12828: mtsho chu dag la rkyal ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12829: char gyi rgyun gyis 'khru ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12830: gzhan gyis bum pa gang ba'i chus //
NK102(ne)001:12831: bdag gi lus la ldugs pa yang //
NK102(ne)001:12832: me dpung chen pos sreg pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12833: shin tu mthon po'i rtse dag la //
NK102(ne)001:12834: rlung gis shin tu g.yengs shing 'thor //
NK102(ne)001:12836: 'jigs dang bral ba'i snga ltas ni //
NK102(ne)001:12837: g.yul 'gyed pa las log pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12838: nad las thar te gsos pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12839: btson ra dag las thar ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12840: gshed ma'i lag las shor ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12841: gcan gzan nang nas bros pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12842: dug nad dag las sos pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12843: bcings pa dag las grol ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12844: thag pa bcad par gyur pa dag /
NK102(ne)001:12845: mtshan ma bzang po'i ltas chen yin //
NK102(ne)001:12846: sa rnams thob pa'i snga ltas ni //
NK102(ne)001:12847: khri rkang dag la 'dzeg pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12848: phal pa'i skas la 'dzeg pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12849: ljon shing dag la 'dzeg pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12850: gyen du shin tu 'gro ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12851: ri bo'i rtse la 'dzeg pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12852: rin chen skas la 'dzeg pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12853: mchod rten dag la 'dzeg pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12854: nam mkha'i skas la 'dzeg pa rnams //
NK102(ne)001:12855: 'di dag don gyi snga ltas yin //
NK102(ne)001:12856: sa rnams non pa'i snga ltas kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12857: khri mthon steng na 'dug pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12858: glang po che la zhon pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12859: seng ge dag la zhon pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12860: khyung chen lding la zhon pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12861: mchod rten kha la phyin pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12862: ri bo'i rtse la 'dug pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12863: nam mkha'i dbyings na 'dug pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12864: lus la sprin phung 'byung ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12865: nyi ma'i dkyil na 'dug pa rnams //
NK102(ne)001:12866: rnal 'byor sa la gnas pa'i rtags //
NK102(ne)001:12867: sangs rgyas sras kyi snga ltas ni //
NK102(ne)001:12868: rgyal po'i bka' la btags pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12869: bka'i dbang por bskos pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12870: gzhan la dbang ni byed pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12872: gzhan gyi sde ba dbang sdud dang //
NK102(ne)001:12873: g.yul chen dag las rgyal ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12874: bdag nyid rgyal por gyur pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12875: mgo la me tog skyes pa rnams //
NK102(ne)001:12876: rgyal ba'i sras su gyur pa'i ltas //
NK102(ne)001:12877: chos la dbang thob snga ltas kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12878: glegs bam zab mo rnyed pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12879: de bzhin dri ba mang po dang //
NK102(ne)001:12880: de dag la ni spyod pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12881: gzhan la 'chad cing ston pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12882: don nyid gtan la 'bebs pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12883: me long dag la blta ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12884: shel gyi bum pa gang ba la //
NK102(ne)001:12887: rin chen nor bu 'thu ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12888: 'khor lo lag tu phebs pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12889: nyi zla lag pas zin pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12890: ri rab klad la bskor ba rnams //
NK102(ne)001:12891: chos la dbang thob snga ltas yin //
NK102(ne)001:12892: bden pa mthong ba'i snga ltas kyang //
NK102(ne)001:12893: sngon ma mthong ba'i yul mthong dang //
NK102(ne)001:12894: stong gsum rgya cher mthong ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12895: gling grangs gzhal du phyin pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12896: ri rab kha la phyin pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12897: nam mkha' rgya cher mthong ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12898: rgya mtsho'i gting du phyin pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12899: lag na sgron me thogs pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12900: nyi ma'i snying po blta ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:12901: snang srid spyod pa byed pa rnams //
NK102(ne)001:12902: bden pa mthong ba'i ltas chen yin //
NK102(ne)001:12903: lung chen thob pa'i snga ltas ni //
NK102(ne)001:12904: rol mo'i sgra rnams thos pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12905: 'brug gi sgra ni grags pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12906: seng ge'i nga ro grags pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12907: chos kyi 'gro ba'i gtam thos dang //
NK102(ne)001:12908: gzugs brnyan zhal ni 'dzum pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12909: sangs rgyas gsung thos sku mi mthong //
NK102(ne)001:12910: lha mos glu dbyangs sgrogs pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:12911: gzhal yas dag las sgra byung dang //
NK102(ne)001:12912: grogs po grogs po zhes brjod cing //
NK102(ne)001:12913: chos kyi bgro ba byed pa rnams //
NK102(ne)001:12914: lung bstan 'byung ba'i snga ltas so //
NK102(ne)001:12916: de ltar drod rtags 'byung ba'i ltas dag bstan pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12918: rtsol ba yid la mi byed cis kyang mi 'khrugs mnyam par shes pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12919: gang la'ang lha'i bu mo la ma /
NK102(ne)001:12920: chags pa dang yul gyi myos gti mug med srin mo 'bar ba mthong yang mi sdug /
NK102(ne)001:12921: skrag med de mi 'bral mi gnas shing /
NK102(ne)001:12922: mi 'grogs mnyam shes bzhi po phyogs dang pha rol phyin rnams der shes te /
NK102(ne)001:12923: zhes pas rtags de lta bu 'byung bar gsungs /
NK102(ne)001:12925: phyi nang gi chos rnams ris su mi 'dzin pa ni rtogs pa'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12926: thams cad la khongs yangs shing 'phral spong len med pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12928: ci lta'ang skyon mi blta gang la'ang dngos por mi rtog pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:12931: yon tan la chags pa med pa ni bsgom pa'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12932: 'khor ba'i chos mi spong la mya ngan las 'das
NK102(ne)001:12933: pa'i chos la mi 'dzin pa nyams su myong ba'i
NK102(ne)001:12934: rtags so // bde ba la 'dod pa ma skyes
NK102(ne)001:12935: sdug bsngal la skyon du mi 'dzin pa grub pa'i
NK102(ne)001:12936: rtags so // rtags so // nyin mtshan du yengs
NK102(ne)001:12937: pa med cing snga phyiir gyur pa med pa klong
NK102(ne)001:12939: rtag chad kyi mtshan ma las 'das pas /
NK102(ne)001:12940: skye shi med par yid ches par klong du gyur pa'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12941: rang bzhin med pa chos nyid klong na /
NK102(ne)001:12942: 'dzin rtog med pa'i ye shes rol pas /
NK102(ne)001:12943: rtsol sgrub kyis blo ma bsgyur /
NK102(ne)001:12944: rgyu 'bras kyis kun gzhi ma bslad par /
NK102(ne)001:12945: lham me lhang nger gsal te /
NK102(ne)001:12946: sang nge sa ler rtogs pa mthar phyin pa'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12949: 'di ltar dus gsum rnam pa thams cad du //
NK102(ne)001:12950: nyid las ma yengs pa ni chos nyid kyi //
NK102(ne)001:12951: stobs su gyur nas 'jig rten rang bzhin med //
NK102(ne)001:12953: yun ring na 'di lta bu dag 'byung ste /
NK102(ne)001:12954: chos gang la yang phyogs ris su mi 'dzin na chos kyi sku'i dgongs pa myong ba'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12955: phan gnod ci byas kyang phan byed la dga' ba med la /
NK102(ne)001:12956: gnod byed na zhe mi sdang na gnyis med kyi dgongs pa nyams su myong ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:12957: sangs rgyas 'od ka re mthong yang bzang bar mi 'dzin la /
NK102(ne)001:12958: sems can 'dre mo lung mthong yang ngan sems ma skyes na /
NK102(ne)001:12959: mnyam pa nyid kyi dgongs pa myong ba'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12960: mtho dman bzang ngan ci la yang blang dor med na /
NK102(ne)001:12961: phyogs ris med pa'i dgongs pa myong ba'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12962: bde sdug bzang ngan ci byung yang sems ma g.yos
NK102(ne)001:12963: na bde ba chen po'i dgongs pa nyams su myong
NK102(ne)001:12964: ba'i rtags so // ci byed ci spyod kyang 'dzin chags med na /
NK102(ne)001:12965: kun tu bzang po'i dgongs pa nyams su myong ba'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12966: nad dang mi mthun pa'i dgra bgegs ci byung yang /
NK102(ne)001:12967: de las ma gtogs bde ba'i 'bras bu mi tshol
NK102(ne)001:12968: bas de la mi dga' ba med na dngos grub
NK102(ne)001:12969: btsal mi dgos pa nyams su myong ba'i rtags so
NK102(ne)001:12971: 'chi ba la sdug bsngal du 'du shes pa mi 'byung bas /
NK102(ne)001:12972: g.yung drung tshe'i dgongs pa nyams su myong ba'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12973: ji ltar snang srid kyang bdag las mi gzhan par rig na /
NK102(ne)001:12974: bdag nyid chen po'i dgongs pa nyams su myong ba'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12975: lha'i bu mo mthong yang 'dod chags ma skyes /
NK102(ne)001:12976: srin po 'bar ba mthong yang 'jigs sems ma g.yos
NK102(ne)001:12977: na ji bzhin pa'i dgongs pa nyams su myong ba'i
NK102(ne)001:12978: rtags so // lus ngag gis ci byed kyang khur
NK102(ne)001:12979: bor 'du shes med de byas pa mi 'dzin na
NK102(ne)001:12980: rtags so // / bya rtsol dang bral ba'i dgongs pa nyams su myong ba'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12981: 'khor ba'i gnas su bskal bar gnas kyang skyo ba snyam mi byed na /
NK102(ne)001:12982: thugs rje chen po mi nyams pa'i dgongs pa nyams su myong ba'i rtags so //
NK102(ne)001:12984: ci spyad kyang ting nge 'dzin las mi nyams pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12985: 'bras bu la re ba med pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12986: dmyal ba'i 'jig rten mthong yang lhung du dogs pa med pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12987: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams mthong yang dwangs pa mi skye /
NK102(ne)001:12988: bdud dang srin po mthong yang 'jigs sems mi g.yo ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:12989: lha'i bu mo mthong yang ma chags pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12990: ci byas tshogs su ma gyur pa med pas dge ba rgyun mi 'chad pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12991: las legs nyes kyi rnam pa la spong len med pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:12992: brdeg brtsog dang spyod pa ci byed kyang sems 'khrugs pa med pa dang dgu 'byung ste /
NK102(ne)001:12994: bsam gtan chen por nges snang ba //
NK102(ne)001:12995: kun tu mi nyams re dogs med //
NK102(ne)001:12996: dwangs ba mi skye mi g.yo dang //
NK102(ne)001:12997: ma chags mi 'chad len pa med //
NK102(ne)001:12998: 'khrul pa med na rang bzhin nyid //
NK102(ne)001:13000: der ma zad bdud kyi spyod yul bco brgyad yang 'byung ste /
NK102(ne)001:13001: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' mang po bdag gi spyad na 'dug pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:13002: de dag la bdag snang mdzad du gyur nas byang chub sems dpa' la /
NK102(ne)001:13004: bdag gi sems kyi skad cig la sprul pa mang po 'gyed nus pa mthong ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:13005: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i chos kun gsal bar mthong ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:13006: dus tshes snga phyi kun gsal bar shes pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:13007: rgyud drug gi lam la gnas pa kun yid la sa le bar /
NK102(ne)001:13009: de la snying rje chen po rang dbang med par skye ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:13010: nyin mtshan med par sa le 'od chen por /
NK102(ne)001:13013: dang ri dang chu la thogs pa med par 'gro ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:13014: nam mkha' dang sa la bya bzhin 'gro zhing 'dug nus mthu /
NK102(ne)001:13018: ste bdag gi spyi bor bzhag nas lung ston pa nus snyam /
NK102(ne)001:13020: 'gro ba kun gyi skad du chos ston shes pa
NK102(ne)001:13021: dang snod bcud kyi 'jig rten las bdag mchod pa'i
NK102(ne)001:13022: rim gro bkur sti byed pa'i /
NK102(ne)001:13024: stong gsum lag mthil ltar mnyam par mthong ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:13025: snod 'od phyogs bcur gsal bar 'byung ba /
NK102(ne)001:13026: bcud sa ler mthong ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:13027: ci la'ang res nges par mngon du gyur pas 'gro
NK102(ne)001:13028: ba thams cad kyi don thogs pa med par nus
NK102(ne)001:13029: snyams / thogs pa med par 'gro ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:13030: lha srin dang rig 'dzin kun gyis chos kyi ston pa gyis shig par bsgo ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:13032: brgya byin la sogs pa rnams mchod pa byed du 'ong ba dang bco brgyad 'byung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:13033: de yang rnal 'byor bdud kyi spyod yul ni /
NK102(ne)001:13034: dam par 'dun mthong dam par smra //
NK102(ne)001:13035: sprul pa grangs med par mthong ba //
NK102(ne)001:13036: dam pas smras kun gsal mthong dang //
NK102(ne)001:13037: dus kun shes gsal mthong ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:13038: rgyud drug lam gnas kun snang dang //
NK102(ne)001:13039: de la gdung ba'i shugs 'byung dang //
NK102(ne)001:13040: kun snang gsal bar mthong ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:13041: ci la'ang thogs med 'gro ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:13042: mkha' la sa bzhin 'dug pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:13043: dam pa'i phyag brkyang lung ston dang //
NK102(ne)001:13044: kun gyi skad du chos smra dang //
NK102(ne)001:13045: dngos po brtan g.yo bsti gnas mthong //
NK102(ne)001:13046: thams cad mnyam par bkod pa dang //
NK102(ne)001:13047: de nyid rang bzhin gsal snang dang //
NK102(ne)001:13048: las su rung bas thogs med dang //
NK102(ne)001:13049: dam pa'i don la bsgo ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:13050: 'jig rten gtso bos mchod pa dag /
NK102(ne)001:13051: rang bzhin shes na dam pa'i rtags //
NK102(ne)001:13052: gang ma rtog pa log pa'i bdud //
NK102(ne)001:13056: nyes dang legs pa gang la yang //
NK102(ne)001:13057: dga' dang 'gyod pa'i rtog pa med //
NK102(ne)001:13058: rang byung rang zhi de nyid yin //
NK102(ne)001:13061: byang chub sems kyi man ngag las //
NK102(ne)001:13062: sems dang snang ba'i mtshan ma ste //
NK102(ne)001:13063: nga bdag gnyis po'i mtha' med pas //
NK102(ne)001:13064: snang ba thams cad yon tan yin //
NK102(ne)001:13065: de bas dga' spro 'du shes med //
NK102(ne)001:13066: yon tan bsnyems pa'i nga rgyal gyis //
NK102(ne)001:13067: dregs khengs mtho dman sems skyes na //
NK102(ne)001:13068: nges par bden pa ma mthong bas //
NK102(ne)001:13069: des na bdud kyi spyod yul gsungs //
NK102(ne)001:13070: de bas sgyu mar rab shes na //
NK102(ne)001:13071: rlom sems bral ba sangs rgyas yin //
NK102(ne)001:13073: de dag la'ang chags 'dzin mi bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:13075: snang ba lus kyi snga ltas dang //
NK102(ne)001:13076: ngo mtshar rdzas rnyed tshul rtags dang //
NK102(ne)001:13077: mtshan ma pra'i rmi ltas dang //
NK102(ne)001:13078: 'dun pa mang po'i snga ltas dang //
NK102(ne)001:13079: blo rtsal las kyi khyad par dang //
NK102(ne)001:13081: rtsi 'tshal lo ma gar byung ba //
NK102(ne)001:13082: zes nas gser khung yod pa ltar //
NK102(ne)001:13083: sngar ltas mtshan ma 'di dag gis //
NK102(ne)001:13084: 'bras bu mtho dman gang gyur pa //
NK102(ne)001:13085: sgyu ma mkhas par byas nas ni //
NK102(ne)001:13086: mtshan ma ci byung de la sbyar //
NK102(ne)001:13089: de nas sa chen g.yo ba ltar //
NK102(ne)001:13090: shin tu yal yol mar mer 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:13091: 'di ni dang po'i rtags zhes bya //
NK102(ne)001:13092: de nas ting 'dzin rtsal sbyangs na //
NK102(ne)001:13093: ji ltar dmigs pa de 'grub ste //
NK102(ne)001:13094: me yi skye mched der bsgom na //
NK102(ne)001:13095: me yi skye mched nyid du 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:13096: zhes pa dag gi rjes la /
NK102(ne)001:13097: de ltar rdzas kyi skye mched du //
NK102(ne)001:13098: gang ltar bsgom pa de ltar 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:13099: de ni rtags chen thob pa yin //
NK102(ne)001:13100: ngag gis bden pa'i rtsal 'byung ste //
NK102(ne)001:13101: srid pa'i skye mched mthong ba na //
NK102(ne)001:13102: zhi bar gyur cig brjod pa yis //
NK102(ne)001:13103: de nyid du ni zhi bar 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:13104: chu klung gnod pa'i rgyun byung na //
NK102(ne)001:13105: chad par gyur cig brjod pa yis //
NK102(ne)001:13106: de nyid du ni chad par 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:13109: nad ga na na bar se gol gtogs pas zhi ba dang /
NK102(ne)001:13110: ji skad brjod pa ltar 'gyur ro //
NK102(ne)001:13111: khams kyi zas la ma brten yang //
NK102(ne)001:13112: dbang po zhi mdangs rab tu gsal //
NK102(ne)001:13114: gzhan yang lus kyi snga ltas ni //
NK102(ne)001:13115: mnyam pa'i skyil krung bcas nas ni //
NK102(ne)001:13116: khru gang tsam du 'phar nas ni //
NK102(ne)001:13117: t+aa la gang tsam bar du 'gro //
NK102(ne)001:13118: 'di yang rtags chen ltas yin no //
NK102(ne)001:13119: gzhan yang snang ba nam mkha' la //
NK102(ne)001:13120: gom pas bgrod de 'gro ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:13121: chu la mi byings sa la 'dzul //
NK102(ne)001:13122: me yis mi 'tshig rlung bcings ba //
NK102(ne)001:13123: 'di yang snga ltas chen po yin //
NK102(ne)001:13124: lus kyi bden pa'i rtsal rdzogs nas //
NK102(ne)001:13125: mthu yi rtsal yang 'byung ba ste //
NK102(ne)001:13126: mthu ni byin rlabs bsam mi khyab //
NK102(ne)001:13127: gal te 'dod dam dgos pa na //
NK102(ne)001:13129: gser dang dngul la sogs par 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:13130: skam sa dag las chu 'byin cing //
NK102(ne)001:13131: sol ba dag las ljon shing 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:13132: de la sogs pa'i dgos pa rnams //
NK102(ne)001:13134: spyod pa'i mthu dang rtsal rdzogs na //
NK102(ne)001:13138: rdzas kyi mchog tu gyur pa yi //
NK102(ne)001:13139: ngo mtshar can yang rnyed par 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:13140: de dag las su rung ba'i snga ltas su //
NK102(ne)001:13142: kun gyis bkur zhing dga' ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:13144: thams cad 'dul zhing thams cad la //
NK102(ne)001:13145: dbang bsgyur byed pa'i mchog tu 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:13146: de dag snga ltas chen po yin //
NK102(ne)001:13147: nyi zla zhon nas 'gro ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:13148: ri rab snyegs nas gsor ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:13150: sreg pa'i skal pa gzhil ba dang //
NK102(ne)001:13151: rdzogs pa'i cho 'phrul thams cad kun //
NK102(ne)001:13153: rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul ni //
NK102(ne)001:13155: so so'i skad du chos mthun par //
NK102(ne)001:13156: 'dul ba sgo ni sna tshogs su //
NK102(ne)001:13157: so so'i skad du ston par nus //
NK102(ne)001:13158: chos kyi sgo rnams snang ba ni //
NK102(ne)001:13159: ting 'dzin rtsal gyi khyad par gyis //
NK102(ne)001:13160: 'jig rten khams rnams g.yo nas kyang //
NK102(ne)001:13161: thams cad ngo mtshar skyes 'gyur te //
NK102(ne)001:13162: sems kyi bsam par rang byas nas //
NK102(ne)001:13163: so sor dga' ba'i ro myong 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:13164: kun tu kun tu brjod pa yi //
NK102(ne)001:13165: gsang ba'i yi ge 'phreng ba las //
NK102(ne)001:13166: rdzu 'phrul chos kyi sgra bsgrags pas //
NK102(ne)001:13167: yod mthong snang grags chos rnams kun //
NK102(ne)001:13168: sngags su ma gyur gang yang med //
NK102(ne)001:13171: 'o na a ti yo ga ci la yang rag ma lus pa /
NK102(ne)001:13173: rtags dang mtshan ma 'byung bar mi bzhed do //
NK102(ne)001:13177: spyir rtags de dag rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo ga pa la 'byung na /
NK102(ne)001:13178: 'dir ji bzhin pa byang chub kyi sems ni 'khor
NK102(ne)001:13179: ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i mtshan ma gang
NK102(ne)001:13181: ya mtshan snang ba thams cad kyi 'byung gnas yin pas /
NK102(ne)001:13182: dpe rgya mtsho dang rlabs kyi tshul du /
NK102(ne)001:13183: mi skye ba'i chos nyid kyi ngo bo nyid /
NK102(ne)001:13184: rtags mtshan skye ba'i cho 'phrul rang shar ba la 'gogs pa med de /
NK102(ne)001:13185: de yang nam mkha' che las /
NK102(ne)001:13186: de ni snying po de bas na //
NK102(ne)001:13187: de las de 'byung ngo mtshar che //
NK102(ne)001:13189: ngo mtshar rmad byung rol pa 'di //
NK102(ne)001:13190: bya bral nam mkha' ji bzhin te //
NK102(ne)001:13191: cir yang mi dmigs gti mug las //
NK102(ne)001:13192: de ma thag tu rang las 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:13195: skye med dbyings nas skye ba'i cho 'phrul rnams //
NK102(ne)001:13196: rnam dag byang chub sems kyi dbyings nas 'phro //
NK102(ne)001:13199: chos rnams sgyu mar mngon sum bsal ba'i phyir //
NK102(ne)001:13200: ting 'dzin sgyu ma'i cho 'phrul sna tshogs rnams //
NK102(ne)001:13201: cir yang mi dmigs gar yang nges pa med //
NK102(ne)001:13204: cho 'phrul rmad du byung ba bstan nas /
NK102(ne)001:13205: rtags mtshan 'byung ba la the tshom zar med par la rbad kyis bcad do //
NK102(ne)001:13207: de dag la chags par byar med de /
NK102(ne)001:13208: dper nam mkhar mtshan ma 'ja' tshon glog la sogs
NK102(ne)001:13209: pa snang ba gzhi ma cir yang snang la ma
NK102(ne)001:13210: dmigs so // de lta bu'i rtags shar nas /
NK102(ne)001:13212: 'bras bu thob pa'i tha snyad de tshul ji lta bu zhe na /
NK102(ne)001:13213: lhun grub rang bzhin nam mkha' 'dra /
NK102(ne)001:13214: zhes pa'i don gyis lung dang sbyar te /
NK102(ne)001:13220: pa grub zin don gyi che ba /
NK102(ne)001:13222: de bzhin dngos grub grub zin pas //
NK102(ne)001:13223: de nyid rnyed pa nyid las byung //
NK102(ne)001:13224: zhes pa'i don sbyar na grub zin pa drug ste zhib tu sngar bshad do //
NK102(ne)001:13226: sgrib pa sbyangs zin pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:13227: rnal 'byor ma h+aa yo ga pa ni dug sman du gyur pa ltar /
NK102(ne)001:13228: mi spong ched du 'joms par byed la /
NK102(ne)001:13230: thams cad ji bzhin pa'i de kho na nyid kyi
NK102(ne)001:13231: ngang la 'khor ba mya ngan las 'das par ye
NK102(ne)001:13233: phyin ci log byang chub lam du gtod /
NK102(ne)001:13234: sdug bsngal chos nyid du yo lang skye /
NK102(ne)001:13235: nyon mong bde chen du shar /
NK102(ne)001:13236: sgrib pa ye shes chen por rang gsal /
NK102(ne)001:13237: ngan song gsum mtho ris kyi gnas dam pa ye ma bcom ma bsgyur ba sangs rgyas pa la /
NK102(ne)001:13238: da 'phral du gser 'gyur rtsi ltar sgrib pa ye shes su gyur par bya yang med de /
NK102(ne)001:13239: ka nas ngang gis dag par shes pa nyid la sgrib byed ming med de /
NK102(ne)001:13240: rgya mtsho dwangs pa ltar gnas pa nyid la bag
NK102(ne)001:13241: la nyal gyi sa bon thams cad dang bral ba'o
NK102(ne)001:13243: bskal par bsags pa'i mun nag thibs po dag /
NK102(ne)001:13244: rig pa'i rgyal po ye shes nyi zer gyis //
NK102(ne)001:13245: skad cig yud tsam nyid la gsal bar 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:13247: lam pas ngo bgrod du med pa nyid la bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:13248: don rig pa nyid la bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:13250: ye shes rlung du shar ba'i rnal 'byor gyis //
NK102(ne)001:13251: sa mchog 'di na ma bsgrubs lhun gyis grub //
NK102(ne)001:13252: bag la nyal ba'i skyon rnams ma lus kun //
NK102(ne)001:13253: ye shes 'od gsal chen pos rab bsal nas //
NK102(ne)001:13254: theg chen 'di yi mkha' la nyi shar bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:13255: mtha' yi mun pa ye nas med ces gsungs //
NK102(ne)001:13258: ri rab sum cu phrag dgu yang //
NK102(ne)001:13259: rmad byung byang chub sems 'di yis //
NK102(ne)001:13260: sgom pas rdo rje phye mar brlagsa //
NK102(ne)001:13263: las dang nyon mongs sdug bsngal rgya mtsho ni //
NK102(ne)001:13264: gsang nyid skad cig snang bas thams cad med //
NK102(ne)001:13267: gsang ba'i don mthong skad cig gis //
NK102(ne)001:13268: thams cad snang ba'i rnam par 'gyur //
NK102(ne)001:13271: byang chub sems ni spu gri'i so //
NK102(ne)001:13272: til mar ngar btags ral gri bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:13273: byang chub sems ni yongs kyi lam //
NK102(ne)001:13274: skyon gyis ma gos pad+ma bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:13275: bskal pa 'bar ba'i me bzhin du //
NK102(ne)001:13276: sdug bsngal sdig pa ci spyad kyang //
NK102(ne)001:13279: de lta bas na skabs 'dir ci la'ang zin chags med pas las dang rnam par smin pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:13280: skye gnas kyi sgrib pa ye dag go //
NK102(ne)001:13281: bdag 'dzin dus gsum bral bas nyon mongs pa ngang gis skye ba med do //
NK102(ne)001:13282: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dag go //
NK102(ne)001:13283: ye brdal khyab gnyis su med pas ji bzhin pas
NK102(ne)001:13284: de kho na nyid tsam du yang mi 'dzin pa
NK102(ne)001:13285: gdod nas bral ba'i shes bya'i sgrib pa dag go
NK102(ne)001:13286: // 'on tang ye dag pa la gnyen po'i rtsol
NK102(ne)001:13287: ba mi dgos par dag pa nyid kyis zin pa'i
NK102(ne)001:13288: don dang mjal ba med par mjal ba la /
NK102(ne)001:13289: tha snyad du sgrib pa dag ces btags so //
NK102(ne)001:13290: de la tshogs bsags pa dang bral te bshad zin to //
NK102(ne)001:13291: dngos grub ye nas grub zin pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:13292: thob bya ril gyi bdag nyid du rang rig pa bzhugs pa'i phyir /
NK102(ne)001:13293: bsal thob med kyang thob pa med pa'i don ma btsal bar mjal ba la /
NK102(ne)001:13294: tha snyad du thob shar zhes btags su zad kyi /
NK102(ne)001:13295: ngo bo la dngos grub rang las shar ma shar gyi tha snyad kyang med de /
NK102(ne)001:13296: de yang brod pa bskyed pa'i ngor /
NK102(ne)001:13298: rnam dag byang chub sems kyi ngang tshul sgom dang yon tan khyad par ni /
NK102(ne)001:13299: blo ldan nam zhig sems kyi dam pa mngon du gyur pa na //
NK102(ne)001:13300: de la sku gsum mchog tu gyur pa chos kyi sku zhes rgyal bas gsungs //
NK102(ne)001:13301: shes byed dam par gyur par shes rab can zhes kyang ni de la bya //
NK102(ne)001:13302: rdo rje rtse mo mchog nyid mi rtog ye shes de yang de nyid do //
NK102(ne)001:13305: nam mkha'i ngang la rang bzhin med //
NK102(ne)001:13306: rtag tu med pas dngos dang bral //
NK102(ne)001:13307: snying po nyid pas gzhan pa med //
NK102(ne)001:13308: sna tshogs dag gis rgyun du 'char //
NK102(ne)001:13309: sgron mar snang bas mun pa sel //
NK102(ne)001:13310: yid bzhin nor bu nyid las 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:13312: cir yang ma nges nyams mi nga //
NK102(ne)001:13313: chub na bya rtsol kun dang bral //
NK102(ne)001:13314: go ba'i yul na bgrod pa med //
NK102(ne)001:13315: gzhan du rtsa ba gsum bcad kyang //
NK102(ne)001:13316: gsang ba'i don nyid rang las 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:13319: yon tan kun dang stobs kyi rnams //
NK102(ne)001:13320: ji bzhin rtogs pa phra ba las //
NK102(ne)001:13321: de ma thag tu rang las 'byung //
NK102(ne)001:13323: lta ba'i skabs su zhib tu brjod zin to //
NK102(ne)001:13324: de lta bas na dngos grub dang 'bras bu gzhan
NK102(ne)001:13325: nas thob tu med pa tsam la rang las byung
NK102(ne)001:13326: zhes bya ba'i / thob pa dang ma thob pa med par gdengs chud pa nyid thob pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:13328: theg pa gsum gyis nges 'byung la //
NK102(ne)001:13329: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK102(ne)001:13331: mi rtog pa rim pa gsum po ni nges par 'byung byed yin /
NK102(ne)001:13332: de ril gyi grub mtha' ni lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i theg pa 'di yin te /
NK102(ne)001:13333: 'di ma rtogs par gzhan gyis sangs rgya ba'i thabs med par zhib tu brjod pa'i phyir na /
NK102(ne)001:13334: khyad par chen po mtshan brjod pa yang nges so //
NK102(ne)001:13335: 'di ni ril grub zin pa dpe nam mkha' dang 'dra bar yang bzhed do //
NK102(ne)001:13336: theg pa'i khyad par bshad pa ni /
NK102(ne)001:13337: khong gis khrel bar yod de zin pa'i don nyi shu kho nas chog /
NK102(ne)001:13338: de la man ngag dang lung gi gtan tshigs rgyab tu bzhag la /
NK102(ne)001:13339: phyir rgol ba po'i blo la gtan tshigs grub par gyis shig /
NK102(ne)001:13341: mdor na go bde bar rtsa bar dril te gsol /
NK102(ne)001:13342: ston mun ni rdzogs chen dang skad mthun /
NK102(ne)001:13343: bya ba med bsgrub pa med par ston yang /
NK102(ne)001:13344: gzhi mi 'byung ba yongs su grub pa la dgongs nas /
NK102(ne)001:13345: don dam pa'i bden pa ma skyes stong pa'i gzhi la smra ste /
NK102(ne)001:13346: de la ni brtags na da dung bden pa re mos pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:13347: stong pa'i ngang la 'dris par byed pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:13349: bden pa gnyis med pa la spyod kyang ma myong ste /
NK102(ne)001:13350: rang gi lta bas bsgribs te gnyis med la bzod 'jug dgos so //
NK102(ne)001:13351: ma h+aa yo ga a ti yo ga dang don
NK102(ne)001:13352: phyogs gnyis su med par don yang bdag nyid du
NK102(ne)001:13353: ma shes te / de la goms rtsol cher byed pa dang ma bral lo //
NK102(ne)001:13354: a nu yo ga ma h+aa yo ga la bltos na khyad par che yang /
NK102(ne)001:13355: rtsol ba mi byed par 'jog tshul byed kyang mi rtsol ba'i btang snyoms la ched du byed do //
NK102(ne)001:13356: yang ma h+aa yo ga de bzhin nyid las /
NK102(ne)001:13357: rim pas lhar bskyed cing 'gro don byed /
NK102(ne)001:13358: a nu yo ga skad cig mar bskyed nas don
NK102(ne)001:13359: byed pa nyid kyis rang byung ye shes bya ba
NK102(ne)001:13360: med pa'i mdzad spyod chen po ma mthong ste /
NK102(ne)001:13361: mi rtog pa la bzhag pas bdag gzhan gyi don
NK102(ne)001:13362: rdzogs pa las gol te don gyis gong ma la
NK102(ne)001:13363: ltos na / bden pa re mos kyang 'dug go //
NK102(ne)001:13364: rnam gcig tu don gyi ngo bo la yang khyad par yod de /
NK102(ne)001:13365: sngags kyi de bzhin nyid ni /
NK102(ne)001:13366: rang rig gnyis med kun tu 'od gsal ba yin la /
NK102(ne)001:13367: rdzogs chen ni lhun rdzogs de bzhin nyid mthar thug pa nyid pas /
NK102(ne)001:13368: gnyis med chen po dbye ba med pas /
NK102(ne)001:13369: ye shes bla ma'i sa yin pas khyad par shin tu che'o //
NK102(ne)001:13370: yang rnam gcig tu rnal 'byor spyod pa'i dbu ma pas a ti yo ga la /
NK102(ne)001:13372: chos thams cad rang gi sems kun rdzob tu rang rig gnyis med ye shes skad cig ma /
NK102(ne)001:13375: mtha' bzhi dang bral bar yang 'dod /
NK102(ne)001:13376: de las de lhag pa'i lta ba ci mchis /
NK102(ne)001:13377: mdo sde dbu ma pas a ti yo ga la /
NK102(ne)001:13383: ngo bo ma don dam par /
NK102(ne)001:13384: skyes dben pa chen po la rtag chad dang bral
NK102(ne)001:13385: ba las 'phags pa'i don las lhag pa ci mchis
NK102(ne)001:13386: / ston mun cig char 'jug pas gsol a ti la /
NK102(ne)001:13388: chos thams cad ye nas ma skyes stong pa'i ngang
NK102(ne)001:13389: la bdan pa gnyis don dam pa gcig med pas
NK102(ne)001:13391: re dogs med pa'i don nga yang 'dod de /
NK102(ne)001:13392: de las 'phags pa'i don ga la yod /
NK102(ne)001:13394: rang rig pa gnyis su med pa de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du gsal ba la /
NK102(ne)001:13395: snang na snang kun rdzob tu /
NK102(ne)001:13396: du zad de phung po khams skye mched lha'i dkyil
NK102(ne)001:13397: 'khor lags pa'i don de las lhag pa ci 'tshal
NK102(ne)001:13398: / a nu yo ga pas gsol pa /
NK102(ne)001:13399: chos thams cad gnyis su med pa'i sras byang chub
NK102(ne)001:13400: sems bde ba chen po'i ngang las skad cig gi
NK102(ne)001:13401: ngang gis kyang sku dang dkyil 'khor sprul pas /
NK102(ne)001:13402: don gnyis grub pa las lhag pa ci mchis gsol pa dang /
NK102(ne)001:13403: a ti yo ga'i rnal 'byor sems pa la lan btab pa /
NK102(ne)001:13404: chos rnams thams cad sems su 'dus pa la //
NK102(ne)001:13405: sems kyi rang bzhin skad cig lta bas nor //
NK102(ne)001:13406: don dam par ma skyes stong par lta bas 'khrul //
NK102(ne)001:13407: skad cig stong las 'das pas de nyid 'phags //
NK102(ne)001:13408: mdo sde pa la lan btab pa /
NK102(ne)001:13409: chos thams cad thig le chen po'i rang bzhin la //
NK102(ne)001:13410: bden pa gnyis su lta ba khyod nyid 'khrul //
NK102(ne)001:13411: gnyis med gnyis su'ang nga ni 'dzin mi byed //
NK102(ne)001:13412: des na brdal khyab 'ub chub nga nyid che //
NK102(ne)001:13413: ston mun pa la lan btab pa /
NK102(ne)001:13414: stong dang ma skyes gnyis med bya bral yang //
NK102(ne)001:13415: gnyis med bya bral ma mthong thos pa'ang med //
NK102(ne)001:13417: mo bya bral nga la a ti /
NK102(ne)001:13419: bcos nas mthong dgos phyir na 'phags pas nga nyid che //
NK102(ne)001:13420: sngags nang pa la lan btab pa /
NK102(ne)001:13421: de bzhin nyid du gnyis su med pa la //
NK102(ne)001:13422: skur bskyed don byed rtsol ba bcug pas nor //
NK102(ne)001:13423: byar med ting 'dzin don la nam yang re mi nus //
NK102(ne)001:13424: de phyir lhun grub rgyal por nga nyid gcig pur byung //
NK102(ne)001:13425: a nu yo ga pa la lan btab pa /
NK102(ne)001:13426: ji bzhin ma bslad btsal rgyu med pa la //
NK102(ne)001:13427: sgo phugs dkyil 'khor bskyed dang ma bral nor //
NK102(ne)001:13428: 'jug skyes ye bral ngang nyid khyod kyis kyang //
NK102(ne)001:13429: phyogs tsam ma shes rang 'byung nga nyid 'phags //
NK102(ne)001:13431: theg pa so so'i lta ba shan phyed de /
NK102(ne)001:13432: rang rang gi lta ba la kho thag chod par gyur to //
NK102(ne)001:13433: 'di ni man ngag rna brgyud dang /
NK102(ne)001:13434: lta ba la shan las kyang 'byung ngo //
NK102(ne)001:13435: rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan zhes bya ba rgya cher 'grel ba las /
NK102(ne)001:13436: rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhung rgyas par bkod pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o////bdag dang gzhan ma dmigs la /
NK102(ne)001:13437: ma 'gags pas dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo ste /
NK102(ne)001:13438: dus lan gcig mtha' 'khob kyi rgyal khams /
NK102(ne)001:13439: bod srin po gdong dmar gyi yul 'di dag tu /
NK102(ne)001:13440: gsang sngags theg pa chen po dar zhing rgyas pa'i rkyen dang stobs kyis /
NK102(ne)001:13441: dgon par gnas pa'i gang zag byang chub don du gnyer ba yang mang du 'byung ba'i dus su /
NK102(ne)001:13442: nga'i bka' rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan rgya cher 'grel pa 'di /
NK102(ne)001:13443: dar zhing ches pa'i nus mthu dang byin rlobs kyis /
NK102(ne)001:13444: rnal 'byor spyod pa'i skal pa dang ldan pa 'di
NK102(ne)001:13445: la yang cing 'jug pa'i skyes mchog rnal 'byor pa
NK102(ne)001:13446: kun kyang dra ba gcig pa dbu ma pa /
NK102(ne)001:13448: phyed pa nyan thos rang rgyal /
NK102(ne)001:13450: chen po so so'i skye bo /
NK102(ne)001:13452: dra ba dang bzhi mu stegs /
NK102(ne)001:13454: sgrib pa dag kyang byang zhing bor te rgyud shin
NK102(ne)001:13455: tu dwangs bas shes rab kyi mig rnyed pa'i don
NK102(ne)001:13456: la bsgoms pas ye shes mchog gi sa thob ste
NK102(ne)001:13457: / de ltar 'bras bu thob nas 'gro ba mtha'
NK102(ne)001:13458: yas pa rnams byang chub tu 'dren cing don byed
NK102(ne)001:13460: bka' phyi nang dang khyad par nga'i bstan pa rnal
NK102(ne)001:13461: 'byor gyi bsam gtan 'di dus kun tu brtan cing
NK102(ne)001:13463: ces dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo ba'o //
NK102(ne)001:13464: 'o na 'di phyi nas ji lta bu'i lag tu
NK102(ne)001:13465: gtad pa'i gang zag gi snod skyon bstan pa ni
NK102(ne)001:13466: / pho dregs phyi lang rang phyogs can //
NK102(ne)001:13467: lce mkhas snying ring nga che 'byin //
NK102(ne)001:13468: gdung bral chags che sgyu 'bru dang //
NK102(ne)001:13469: mi chos ngor blta chos mi nyan //
NK102(ne)001:13470: chung ma bu dang ngan skyong 'khor //
NK102(ne)001:13471: 'dod smra dam med de dag la //
NK102(ne)001:13473: nam yang bstan par mi bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:13474: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir mi spel te /
NK102(ne)001:13475: spyir thams cad rang byung mchog gi sangs rgyas la /
NK102(ne)001:13476: snod bzang ngan ma dmigs kyang /
NK102(ne)001:13477: mdzub mo'i rtse mo bzhin rang gi mtshan nyid ma
NK102(ne)001:13478: rig pa'i gang zag bsam gyis mi khyab pa yang
NK102(ne)001:13480: de dag la bstan na skran can la bcud can byin pa dang 'dra ste /
NK102(ne)001:13482: pho dregs nga bo rang 'gying can //
NK102(ne)001:13483: phyi lang spyod daka'i tshig mi btsan //
NK102(ne)001:13484: rang phyogs gzungs 'dzin shin tu che //
NK102(ne)001:13485: de dag bstan pa'i snod ma yin //
NK102(ne)001:13486: lce mkhas ro dang bslu 'brid can //
NK102(ne)001:13487: snying ring gdung ba'i sems dang bral //
NK102(ne)001:13488: nga che dpon bas mtho bar sems //
NK102(ne)001:13489: gdung bral snying ring gdong 'das can //
NK102(ne)001:13490: rlung phyogs tsam du'ang bsnyen pa min //
NK102(ne)001:13491: chags pas ser snas bcings pa yis //
NK102(ne)001:13492: man ngag sgo gsum g.yo sgyus 'bru //
NK102(ne)001:13493: gzol pa rgyal po'i dkor khang dgu //
NK102(ne)001:13494: shes nas gtan du spangs pa'i rigs //
NK102(ne)001:13495: chos phyir mi 'breng gang zag rnams //
NK102(ne)001:13496: mi chos 'brel dang gnyen ngor blta //
NK102(ne)001:13497: de ltos mnyes pa 'bul mi byed //
NK102(ne)001:13498: bka'i zur yang nyan mi byed //
NK102(ne)001:13499: mi bzad srin mo chung ma dang //
NK102(ne)001:13500: rim pa med pa lus kyi bu //
NK102(ne)001:13501: brtsams yang snying ring ngan gyong 'khor //
NK102(ne)001:13502: man ngag 'dod pa dam pa med //
NK102(ne)001:13503: phyi nang med par kha smra zhing //
NK102(ne)001:13504: man ngag thob nas phyi thag med //
NK102(ne)001:13505: khungs sub rang che 'byin byed la //
NK102(ne)001:13506: rgyal khams 'dus na srog gcod kyang //
NK102(ne)001:13507: gtan du bstan par mi bya ste //
NK102(ne)001:13508: bstan na rdo rje dmyal bar ltung //
NK102(ne)001:13511: ltogs la ngan pa'i slob bu ni //
NK102(ne)001:13512: dar ma shog shog 'phrag la khyer //
NK102(ne)001:13514: zab mo man te gnas mtshon nas //
NK102(ne)001:13515: zang zing ngor lta snang 'tshor byed //
NK102(ne)001:13516: ched du re ba'i slob bu ni //
NK102(ne)001:13517: nga rgyal dregs pas khengs pa yis //
NK102(ne)001:13518: gus pas mi zhu thabs kyis 'dod //
NK102(ne)001:13519: thob nas dpon pas mkhas par smra //
NK102(ne)001:13520: drin las sems kyi bsam thag chod //
NK102(ne)001:13521: yon gyi skyen pa 'tshol rings pas //
NK102(ne)001:13522: gtugs pas dar ma 'dod spel la //
NK102(ne)001:13523: nam bzhar bstan par ma byed cig /
NK102(ne)001:13524: be'u sbrel g.yang du bskyur ba bzhin //
NK102(ne)001:13525: gnyis ka sreg dang sgrib gnas su //
NK102(ne)001:13526: lhungs nas thar ba'i skabs mi srid //
NK102(ne)001:13528: ban chung gnubs ban sangs rgyas kyis //
NK102(ne)001:13529: rgya bal bod dang bru sha sogs //
NK102(ne)001:13530: mkhas pa'i kha brgyud mnyes phul bas //
NK102(ne)001:13532: yang rtse lung gi man ngag thob //
NK102(ne)001:13534: bdag sprang po gnubs ban sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches /
NK102(ne)001:13535: rgya gar gyi mkhas pa pan+di ta mang po dang /
NK102(ne)001:13536: bal po'i rgyal po ba su d+ha ra dang /
NK102(ne)001:13537: bru sha'i yul gyi lo ts+aa ba che btsan skyes
NK102(ne)001:13538: la sogs pa rgyal khams so so'i mkhas pa mang
NK102(ne)001:13540: mnyes pa phul bas pan+di ta rnams dgyes pa skyes te gnang ba thob pas /
NK102(ne)001:13541: thugs kyi mdzod sgo phye nas /
NK102(ne)001:13542: man ngag gi rgyal po dgongs don mthar gtugs pa bdag gis thob ste /
NK102(ne)001:13543: bdag man ngag gi rgyal por gyur to //
NK102(ne)001:13545: bdag la lha srin rnams kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK102(ne)001:13546: rang nyams goms pa'i yi ge bris //
NK102(ne)001:13548: bdag ni nam zhig shel brag 'od na nyal ba'i tshe //
NK102(ne)001:13549: 'dzab grangs yid la bzlas pa'i tshe //
NK102(ne)001:13550: chos nyid blo la gsal ba'i tshe //
NK102(ne)001:13551: lha srin sde brgyad kyis bdag la dbang bskur ro //
NK102(ne)001:13553: de ltar mngon shes can rnams kyis bdag la bsgo bas /
NK102(ne)001:13554: bdag gi dpa' bor blon chen 'phags pa la sogs pa'i bu /
NK102(ne)001:13555: gdung brgyud khu lung yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK102(ne)001:13559: bka' brgyud spyod pa bu tsho'i don du brtsams so //
NK102(ne)001:13560: rgyal ba'i gdung 'dzin skyes mchog bu //
NK102(ne)001:13561: gtan du sgom byed 'du spong gis //
NK102(ne)001:13562: nyams su longs shig pha yi sras //
NK102(ne)001:13563: bus kyang rigs 'tshob gcig la gtod //
NK102(ne)001:13564: mang na rdo rje dmyal bar skye //
NK102(ne)001:13567: re re nas re re brgyud la /
NK102(ne)001:13568: mang na dmyal bar skye zhing gsang sgo yang 'chal te /
NK102(ne)001:13569: mi nag yongs la cha yod dang /
NK102(ne)001:13577: lung dang man ngag gzhan gyi 'og bskal gyi mig /'dir bsdus rnal 'byor can mchog ste /
NK102(ne)001:13578: 'di la su zhig dad mos pas //
NK102(ne)001:13579: thos pa tsam gyis 'khor ba stong //
NK102(ne)001:13580: mos pa tsam gyi chos nyid rtogs //
NK102(ne)001:13581: go ba tsam gyis sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:13582: kun kyang 'di'i rjes su spyod pa yis //
NK102(ne)001:13583: dbye ba med pa'i sa la gnas par shog /
NK102(ne)001:13584: rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan zhes bya ba /
NK102(ne)001:13586: dge rtsa bsngo zhing snod bstan pa'i le'u ste brgyad
NK102(ne)001:13587: pa'o////dang po gnas dang skyon yon dam bcas las brtsams
NK102(ne)001:13588: pa'ang / sngon 'gro'i las brtsoms de dgos nor gnyen yid chags spangs //
NK102(ne)001:13589: dgon pas skyo na'ang grong dang 'du 'dzi'i skyon bsam dang //
NK102(ne)001:13590: rang bzhin dben don dgon pa'i yon tan dran pas bsangs //
NK102(ne)001:13591: don la 'jug tshe thabs dang thabs chen thob bya dang //
NK102(ne)001:13592: mthun bstan rkyen bzlog yo byad lus kyi gru gzugs phyir //
NK102(ne)001:13593: rim gro cher bya de la'ang mi chags ma bsgom skyon //
NK102(ne)001:13594: yon tan rgyas shes dkar phyogs btang snyoms bzhag par bya //
NK102(ne)001:13595: don bzhin thag chod rang bzhin rtogs pas gcan gzan rgyal //
NK102(ne)001:13596: ji bzhin gnas pas bsam pa'ang g.yang sa shes phyir gzhi //
NK102(ne)001:13597: tsen ston mi dmigs nang pa'i mi rtog de bzhin nyid //
NK102(ne)001:13598: lhun rdzogs mi rtog khyad par skas bzhin chud par bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:13599: mdo sde stong sgom dang po tshad med bzhi la rab bsgom nas //
NK102(ne)001:13600: kun rdzob sgyu mar bltas 'jog don dam mi dmigs 'jog pa ga nga //
NK102(ne)001:13601: kha cig zhi gnas goms nas lhag skyed byed cing dmigs gtad nas //
NK102(ne)001:13602: skyon bcos zhi bas zung 'brel rim bgrod sgrib sbyangs tshogs btang 'gro //
NK102(ne)001:13603: ston mun ri rgyal rtser phyin kun mthong tshul gyis thag bcad nas //
NK102(ne)001:13604: 'jug pa'ang cig car zung 'brel gyi nar ma skyes rang gsal ba'ang //
NK102(ne)001:13605: don dam ngang la skyon skyes mi spang rang byung rang zhir 'dod //
NK102(ne)001:13606: de ltas pa las bgrod med mi sbyong grub non khyung chen 'dra'o //
NK102(ne)001:13607: nang pa la dmigs thag chod sgom pa'ang rim 'jug sems 'chos byed //
NK102(ne)001:13608: cig car 'jug la bcos skyon nyams drod rtags mtshan 'byung 'gyur yang //
NK102(ne)001:13609: de la'ang mi chags rmi ltas sogs spyod ci la'ang ma chags spyad //
NK102(ne)001:13610: tshogs la re med gcig pas 'gyur rtsi bzhin 'grub rang 'char nyi ma 'dra'o //
NK102(ne)001:13611: rdzogs chen ngang nyid mngon chud bzhag med don chen rang gsal ba'ang //
NK102(ne)001:13612: gzhal med rtogs chen 'jug bral sgom med skyon byung yang //
NK102(ne)001:13613: sgo gsum bcos med de nyid rang lugs 'chos 'dzin phur sgrib yin //
NK102(ne)001:13614: thun mtshams bral bas mi g.yo mi ldang ngang chen thig le bas //
NK102(ne)001:13615: re mos ldang 'jug spyod lam med de kun kyang bde gshegs mdzad //
NK102(ne)001:13616: spong len ngang bral bri tar dran tsam mi 'gog dran med cing //
NK102(ne)001:13617: re dogs bral yang nyams drod rmis ltas rtags 'char chags med pa'ang //
NK102(ne)001:13618: nam mkha' mtshan snang bzhin pas lhun grub rang bzhin nam mkha' 'dra'o //
NK102(ne)001:13620: theg chen dar ba'i rkyen stobs kyis //
NK102(ne)001:13621: dgon par gnas pa mang 'byung dus //
NK102(ne)001:13623: kun kyang d+r+wa ba bzhi bor nas //
NK102(ne)001:13624: mig rnyed mchog gi sa thob ste //
NK102(ne)001:13625: mtha' yas sems can 'dren par shog /
NK102(ne)001:13626: bstan pa yun du btsan gyur cig /
NK102(ne)001:13627: pho dregs phyi lang rang phyogs can //
NK102(ne)001:13628: lce mkhas snying ring kha che 'byin //
NK102(ne)001:13629: gdung bral chags che sgyus 'bru dang //
NK102(ne)001:13630: mi chos ngor lta bka' mi nyan //
NK102(ne)001:13631: chung ma bu dang ngan gyong 'khor //
NK102(ne)001:13632: 'dod smra dam med de dag la //
NK102(ne)001:13634: nam zhar bstan par mi bya'o //
NK102(ne)001:13635: ban chung gnubs ban sangs rgyas kyis //
NK102(ne)001:13636: rgya bal bod dang bru sha sogs //
NK102(ne)001:13637: mkhas pa'i kha brgyud mnyes phul bas //
NK102(ne)001:13638: pan+di ta yi thug sgo phye //
NK102(ne)001:13639: yang rtse lung gi man ngag thob //
NK102(ne)001:13640: lha srin rnams kyis dbang bskur bas //
NK102(ne)001:13641: rang nyams bsgoms pa'i yi ge bris //
NK102(ne)001:13642: rgyal ba'i gdung 'dzin skyes mchog bus //
NK102(ne)001:13643: gtan du sgom byed 'du spong gis //
NK102(ne)001:13644: nyams su longs shig pha'i btsas //
NK102(ne)001:13645: bus kyang rigs 'tshob gcig la gtod //
NK102(ne)001:13646: mang na rdo rje dmyal bar skye //
NK102(ne)001:13648: gcig gnyis kyi rna bar zungs ya //
NK102(ne)001:13652: mang+ga lam////smin gling mkhan chen d+harma sh+r+ai'i phyag dpe las bshus shing /
NK102(ne)001:13653: des kyang jo nang rje btsun kun dga' snying po'i phyag dpe la ma phyi mdzad pa'o //
NK102(ne)001:13654: sarba dz+ny+aa nan+da gar+b+ha s+ya le kham /
NK102(ne)001:13655: gnubs chen po sangs rgyas ye shes kyis mdzad pa'i rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan zhes kyang zer /
NK102(ne)001:13656: bsam gtan mig sgron zhes kyang grags pa 'di /
NK102(ne)001:13657: shog bu brgya pa de grangs yig ma tshang 'dug kyang don la tshang yod lags /
NK102(ne)001:13659: ka m+aa la shi la'i lugs dang /
NK102(ne)001:13660: lnga pa nas ho shang ma h+aa ya na'i lugs de gsal bar bstan /
NK102(ne)001:13661: bod kyi phyag chen dang po'i tsho /
